\id EXO
\h Uffuɣ 
\toc1 Uffuɣ 
\toc2 Uffuɣ 
\toc3 Uf. 
\mt1 Uffuɣ  
\c 1
\s1 Beddu n tesmuɣi n Israil  
\m
\v 1 Ina d ismawen n ayt n Israil i dd-yiwḍen ak-d Yaɛqub ɣar Miṣra. Yusa-dd kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add* ak-d \add aytbab\add* n taddart nnes: \f ◼ \fr 1:1 \ft \+fk Israil\ft  - wanita d isem n jdid i Yaɛqub. Xzar Amz. 32:29.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Amz. 46:8; Uf. 6:14. \x*  
\v 2 Rubin, Cimɛun, Lawi d Yahuda, \f ◼ \fr 1:2 \fq afessar n řmeɛna n ismawen n ayt n Israil\ft  - xzar Amz. 49.\f*  
\v 3 Issakar, Zabulun d Binyamin,  
\v 4 Dan d Naftali, Jad d Acir.  
\v 5 Marra řeɛmur nni dd-iffɣen zi tmeṣṣaḍt n Yaɛqub, \add tuɣa aten\add* di sebɛin. Yusuf tuɣa-t di Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Amz. 46:27; Aɛwd. 10:22; Řex. 7:14. \x*  
\v 6 Immut Yusuf d marra aytmas, d jjiř nni marra.  
\v 7 Mmarenyen ayt n Israil u jjin-dd řɣiǧet \add ařami\add* zzaysen tesfuffi \add temmurt\add* uca ttwaktaren uca dewřen jehden aṭṭas, \add minzi\add* teccur zzaysen temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Aɛwd. 26:5; Řex. 7:17\x*   
\m
\v 8 Iffeɣ-dd xenni ijj n ujeǧid d jdid \add iḥekkem\add* x Miṣra, wenni tuɣa war issin Yusuf. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Řex. 7:18\x*  
\v 9 Inna i řgens nnes: “Xzar, řgens n ayt n Israil imɣar u ijhed xaneɣ.  
\v 10 Řexxu, aqa ad xas neḥkem s řeɛqeř, ḥima war ittmarni \add řgens ktar,\add* uca, mařa imsar ikkar ca n řbaruḍ, ad idweř ak-d řɛedyan nneɣ, ad yegg řḥarb akidneɣ uca \add xenni\add* ad iffeɣ zi temmurt.” \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Řex. 7:19\x*  
\v 11 Nitni ggin xasen imeḥḍayen x warbar n tesmuɣi, ḥima ad ssdeǧen řgens s ddquřat i xasen ssarebbun. Bnan i firɛun, \add ajeǧid\add*, tineddam n řexzen: Fitum d Raɛamsis.  
\v 12 \add Maca\add* mecḥař ma deǧen nitni řgens, amenni i igma u ibezzeɛ \add řgens\add*, ařami iwḍen nitni ad carhen ayt n Israil aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 1:12 \xt Izhd. 105:24\x*  
\v 13 Uca arrin Imiṣriyyen ayt n Israil d isemɣan s uɣiř  
\v 14 uca ssarezgen tudart nsen s tesmuɣi iqesḥen deg ubeǧaɛ d llajur uřa di marra tesmuɣi deg iyyaren. Marra tasmuɣi i ggin nitni di \add řwest\add* nsen, tuɣa tt s uɣiř. \f ◼ \fr 1:14 \ft \+fk tasmuɣi\ft  - ‘řxedmet n isemɣan’.\f*   
\m
\v 15 Issiweř ujeǧiḍ n Miṣra ak-d řqabřat tiɛibraniyyin, icten zzaysent qqaren as Sifra, u tenneɣni qqaren as Fuɛat.  
\v 16 Inna: “Xmi ɣa tɛawnent timɣarin tiɛibraniyyin ad arwent, uca ad texzarent xmi ttɣimant x iẓra \add maḥend ad arwent\add*, ittxeṣṣa kennint ad nɣent \add aḥenjir\add* mařa d mmis, \add maca\add* mařa d yeǧis, jjent tt ad teddar!”  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* řqabřat tuɣa tteggʷedent AREBBI, war ggint muxas tent yumur ujeǧid n Miṣra, \add maca\add* ḥḍant tudart n iḥenjiren.  
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa ujeǧid n Miṣra i řqabřat, inna asent: “Maɣar teggint aya, aqa teḥḍant tudart n iḥenjiren?”  
\v 19 Řqabřat arrint x firɛun: “Tiɛibraniyyin war ǧint am Timiṣriyyin, minzi nitenti jehdent, ttarwent qbeř ma ad ɣarsent dd-tas řqabřa.”  
\v 20 Uca AREBBI igga mliḥ i řqabřat uca immarni řgens, dewřen jehden s waṭṭas.  
\v 21 Minzi řqabřat ggʷedent AREBBI, imsar, aqa yarzeq i-tent-i-dd s tudrin \add ak-d řwacun\add*. \f ◼ \fr 1:21 \ft \+fk yarzeq\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘yegga’.\f*   
\m
\v 22 \add Řexdenni\add* yumur firɛun marra řgens nnes, inna: “Kuř aḥenjir i dd ɣa ixeřqen ad t tenḍarem deg iɣzar u marra taḥenjirt \add i dd ɣa ixeřqen\add* ad tt tejjem ad teddar.” \x ◘ \xo 1:22 \xt Řex. 7:19\x*  *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Axřaq n Musa d tarewřa nnes  
\m
\v 1 Uca iffeɣ ijj n weryaz zi \add raǧ n\add* taddart n Lawi, yiwi ict n tḥenjirt n Lawi \add d tamɣart\add*. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Uf. 6:20; Řxř. 26:59\x*  
\v 2 Teksi temɣart s ddeyset uca turuw-dd aḥenjir. \add Umi\add* teẓra belli iṣbeḥ \add uḥenjir\add*, teffar i-t třata n iyuren. \f ◼ \fr 2:2 \ft \+fk iyuren\ft  - niɣ ‘cchur’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt 1 Im. 23:13; Řex. 7:20; Ɛbr. 11:23\x*  
\v 3 \add Umi\add* war tezmar ɛad ad t teffar, teksi as-dd ict n tsenduqt n uɣanim, tebra i-tt s ucarmuḍ d tizeft uca tessars dayes aḥenjir, tegga \add tasenduqt nni\add* jar uɣanim x tma n iɣzar.  
\v 4 Tbedd wučmas ɣar řaggʷaj, maḥend ad tẓar min zzayes ɣa ggen.   
\m
\v 5 U \add xzar\add*, tehwa yeǧis n firɛun, maḥend ad tessird ixef nnes deg iɣzar. Tuɣa timsexxarin tibřiɣin nnes ggurent x tma n iɣzar. Nettat teẓra tasenduqt deg uɣanim uca tessekk tismeɣt nnes uca teksi tt-i-dd. \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Řex. 7:21; Ɛbr. 11:23\x*  
\v 6 Ařami tt tarzem, teẓra aḥenjir nni, uca xzar, aḥenjir tuɣa ittru. Yudef i-tt uziǧez, tenna: “Wa d \add ijj\add* zeg iḥenjiren n Iɛibraniyyen!”  
\v 7 \add Řexdenni\add* tenna učmas i yeǧis n firɛun: “Ma ad raḥeɣ ad řaɣiɣ x ict n temsuḍeḍt zi Tɛibraniyyin maḥend ad am tessuṭṭeḍ aḥenjir?”  
\v 8 Tenna as yeǧis n firɛun: “Ruḥ!” Truḥ teɛzarect, třaɣa i yemmas n uḥenjir.  
\v 9 \add Řexdenni\add* tenna as yeǧis n firɛun: “Awi-dd aḥenjir-a, tessuṭṭeḍ i-t i necc u necc ad cem xeǧṣeɣ.” Teksi temɣart aḥenjir uca tessuṭṭeḍ i-t.  
\v 10 \add Umi\add* igma uḥenjir, tiwyi i-t ɣar yeǧis n firɛun, idweř as am mmis uca tegga as Musa, tenna: “Aqa jebdeɣ t-i-dd zeg waman.”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Deg wussan nni imsar, umi igma Musa, aqa iffeɣ-dd ɣar aytmas, uca iẓra ddquřat i xasen \add ssarebbun\add*. Iẓra ijj n Umiṣri iccat ijj n Uɛibrani, \add ijjen\add* zeg aytmas. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Řex. 7:23; Ɛbr. 11:24, 25\x*  
\v 12 Ixzar da d diha, iẓra belli war din ḥed, \add xenni\add* inɣa Amiṣri nni uca issnuffar i-t deg ijdi.  
\v 13 Umi dd-iffeɣ tiwecca nnes, iẓra tnayen n yeryazen Iɛibraniyyen ttmenɣan. Inna \add Musa\add* i uɛeffan nni ittɛeddan: “Maɣar teccated jjar nnec?”  
\v 14 Inna netta: “Wi i cek iggin d řḥakem d řqaḍi xaneɣ? Ma cek teqqared aya umi cek tenwid ad ayi tenɣed am mammec tenɣid Amiṣri?” \add Řexdenni\add* iggʷed Musa, inna: “S tidett tamesřact tᵉttwassen!” \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Řex. 7:27\x*   
\m
\v 15 Umi isřa firɛun man aya, yarzu ad ineɣ Musa. \add Maca\add* Musa yarweř zi firɛun uca izdeɣ di temmurt n Midyan uca iqqim \add din\add* ɣar ijj n wanu. \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Řex. 7:29\x*   
\m
\v 16 Akehhan n Midyan tuɣa ɣares sebɛa n yessis, tinni i dd-yusin ad ayment aman \add din\add* uca ccurent sswarej, ḥima ad wardent uǧi n babatsent.  
\v 17 Usin-dd imeksawen uca uẓẓřen xasent. Ikkar Musa \add řexdenni\add*, ifekk i-tent, iward uǧi nsent. \f ◼ \fr 2:17 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  
\v 18 \add Umi\add* dewřent ɣar babatsent \add umi qqaren\add* Raɛuyil, inna \add asent\add*: “Mayemmi dd-ttɛeqbent ass-a deɣya?” \f ◼ \fr 2:18 \ft \+fk Raɛuyil\ft  - ɣares uřa d isem nneɣni, aqa-t Yitru. Xzar Ufuɣ 3:1. Isem-a ixs ad yini ‘ameddukkař n Arebbi’.\f*  
\v 19 Nitenti arrint-i-dd xas: “Ijj n weryaz d Amiṣri ifekk aneɣ zeg ifassen n imeksawen uca \add ɛawed\add* yuyem aneɣ-dd aṭṭas n waman uca iward uǧi.” \f ◼ \fr 2:19 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  
\v 20 Inna i yessis: “I mani yeǧa? Mayemmi tejjint aryaz \add nni din\add*? Ruḥent řaɣant-i-dd xas ḥima ad icc aɣrum!”  
\v 21 Uca iqbeř Musa ad izdeɣ ak-d weryaz nni uca netta iwca as i Musa yeǧis Ṣaffura \add d tamɣart\add*.  
\v 22 Tejja as-dd aḥenjir, igga as Jarcum, minzi inna: “Necc tuɣa ayi d aɣrib deg ict n temmurt d taɣribt xafi.” \f ◼ \fr 2:22 \ft \+fk Jarcum\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘ijj n ubarrani (ǧiɣ) danita’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Uf. 18:2, 3\x*   
\m
\v 23 Řami teɛdu waṭṭas n řweqt, immut ujeǧid n Miṣra uca weḥweḥen ayt n Israil di tesmuɣi \add i di tuɣa ddaren\add*, ssɣuyen uca iɣuyyan nsen geɛɛden ɣar AREBBI zi tesmuɣi \add nsen\add*.  
\v 24 Uca issḥess AREBBI i tɣuyyit nsen uca ixarreṣ AREBBI di Řɛahd nnes ak-d Ibrahim u ak-d Isḥaq u ak-d Yaɛqub. \x ◘ \xo 2:24 \xt Amz. 15:14\x*  
\v 25 Ixzar AREBBI ɣar ayt n Israil uca yargeb AREBBI \add x řeɣben nsen\add*.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Tařaɣit n Arebbi x Musa  
\m
\v 1 Yarwes Musa uǧi n Yitru, aḍeggʷař nnes, akehhan n Midyan. Indeh uǧi awarni i řexřa uca yiwiḍ-dd ɣar wedrar n AREBBI, ɣar Ḥurib.  
\v 2 Iban as-dd lmalak n SIDI deg ijj n uceɛɛuř di řwesṭ n ijj n cbarq ak-d isennanen, u xzar, netta iẓra belli cbarq ak-d isennanen tuɣa tekkar dayes tmessi, \add maca\add* cbarq war ittwacmeḍ ca.  
\v 3 Inna Musa: “Ejj ayi ad qewseɣ \add cwayt\add*, maḥend ad ẓareɣ tameẓriwt nni tameqqrant, mayemmi cbarq ak-d isennanen war icemmeḍ ca.”  
\v 4 \add Řami\add* iẓra AREBBI belli ijja abrid, maḥend ad iẓar \add man aya\add*, iřaɣa-dd xas AREBBI zi řwesṭ n cbarq ak-d isennanen, inna: “Musa, Musa!” Netta yarra: “Aqa ayi da!”  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* inna Netta: “War dd-ttqarrab ca danita! Kkes tisiřa nnec zeg iḍaren nnec, minzi amcan i xef tbedded, aqa-t d tammurt tqeddes.” \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Yac. 5:15\x*  
\v 6 Inna \add ɛawed:\add* “Necc d AREBBI n babac, AREBBI n Ibrahim, AREBBI n Isḥaq d AREBBI n Yaɛqub.” \add Řexdenni\add* issduriy Musa aɣembub nnes, minzi iggʷed ad isweḍ di AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Mt. 22:32; Mk. 12:26; Lk. 20:37; Řex. 7:32\x*   
\m
\v 7 Inna SIDI: “Aqa ẓriɣ řmeḥnet \add i di iddar\add* řgens inu i iǧan di Miṣra uca sřiɣ iɣuyyan nsen zzat i imzeyyaren nsen, aqa ssneɣ tamara nsen. \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt Řex. 7:34\x*  
\v 8 Hwiɣ-dd ḥima ad fekkeɣ \add řgens\add* zeg ifassen n Imiṣriyyen, ad t ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt nni ɣar ict n temmurt teṣbeḥ d tmiriwt, ɣar ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment, ɣar wemcan n ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥittiyyen d Imuriyyen d Ifiriziyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyibusiyyen.  
\v 9 Xzar řexxu, aqa tiweḍ-dd ɣari tɣuyyit n ayt n Israil uca ɛawed ẓriɣ ddeǧ nsen i zi ten deǧen Imiṣriyyen.  
\v 10 Řexxu \add xenni\add*, ruḥ, Necc ad cek ssekkeɣ ɣar firɛun u cek ad tsuffɣed řgens inu, ayt n Israil, zi Miṣra.” \x ◘ \xo 3:10 \xt Izhd. 105:26; Ḥuc. 12:14; Mixa 6:4; Řex. 7:35\x*   
\m
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa i AREBBI: “Min ɛniɣ necc ařami ɣa raḥeɣ ɣar firɛun, ad ssuffɣeɣ ayt n Israil zi Misra?”  
\v 12 Netta inna as: “Necc ad kik iřiɣ u tanita ad ac tiři d řeɛřamet, belli Necc ssekkeɣ-dd cek: x minni i ɣa tessuffɣed řgens-a zi Miṣra, ad tɛebdem AREBBI x wedrar-a.” \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Yac. 1:5\x*  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa i AREBBI: “Xzar, xmi dd ɣa awḍeɣ necc ɣar ayt n Israil, ad asen iniɣ: ‘AREBBI n řejdud nwem issekk ayi-dd ɣarwem!’, \add uca\add* nitni ad ayi sseqsan: ‘Mammec d as qqaren?’, min d asen ɣa iniɣ \add xenni\add*?”  
\v 14 Inna AREBBI i Musa: \bd “NECC d NECC i ǧiɣ”\bd*. Uca inna \add ɛawed\add*: “Ammu i ɣa tinid i ayt n Israil: \bd NECC d NECC \+bdit i ǧiɣ\+bdit*!\bd* aqa Netta d Wenni d ayi dd-issekken ɣarwem.”  
\v 15 Inna AREBBI ɛawed i Musa: “Ammu i ɣa tinid i ayt n Israil: ‘SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, AREBBI n Ibrahim d AREBBI n Isḥaq d AREBBI n Yaɛqub, issekk ayi-dd ɣarwem. D wa d Isem inu i řebda u \add Yisem\add* wanita \add ad yiři\add* i řidaret dayi zi jjiř ař jjiř.’  
\v 16 Ruḥ, tessmuned imɣaren n Israil, ini asen: ‘SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, AREBBI n Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub iban ayi-dd, inna: ‘Aqa xawem ḥinneɣ uca \add ẓriɣ\add* min xawem sseɛdun di Miṣra.  
\v 17 Nniɣ: Necc ad kenniw ssuffɣeɣ zi řmeḥnet di Miṣra ɣar temmurt n ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥittiyyen d Imuriyyen d Ifiriziyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyibusiyyen, ɣar ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment.’  
\v 18 Ad sřen i tmijja nnec, uca ad traḥed, cek d imɣaren n Israil, ɣar ujeǧid n Miṣra, ad as tinim: ‘SIDI, AREBBI n Iɛibraniyyen, imsagar akidneɣ. Xenni řexxu, ejj aneɣ ad neṭṭef abrid ticři n třata n wussan di řexřa, ḥima ad nqeddem tiɣarṣa i SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.’ \f ◼ \fr 3:18 \ft \+fk taɣarṣt - tiɣarṣa\ft  - niɣ ‘ddebiḥet’, ‘ddbayeḥ’.\f*  
\v 19 \add Maca\add* Necc ssneɣ belli ajeǧid n Miṣra war kenniw ittejji ad traḥem uřa s ufus ijehden.  
\v 20 Xenni ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu, ad wteɣ Miṣra s marra lmuɛjizat inu i dayes i ɣa ggeɣ di řwesṭ nnes, uca awarni i man aya, netta ad kenniw yejj ad traḥem.  
\v 21 Ad ḥinneɣ x řgens-a zzat i tiṭṭawin n Imiṣriyyen uca ad imsar, xmi ɣa traḥem, war tᵉtteffɣem ca s ifassen xwan.  
\v 22 Ad tᵉttar kuř tamɣart zi tajjart nnes u zi tbarranit nni akides izeddɣen di taddart, řeqcuɛ n nnuqart d wureɣ d warruḍ, uca kenniw ad ten teggem x iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin nwem, uca \add ammu i\add* ɣa tkeccḍem Miṣra.” \x ◘ \xo 3:22 \xt Uf. 11:2; 12:35; Ḥiz. 39:10\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Arebbi issekk Musa ɣar Miṣra  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd Musa, inna: “Xzar, nitni war dayi ttimnen ca uca war ttesřin ca i wawař inu, minzi ad inin: ‘SIDI war d ac dd-iban ca!’” \f ◼ \fr 4:1 \ft \+fk i wawař inu\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘i tmijja inu’.\f*  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna as SIDI: “Min ɣarek deg ufus nnec?” Uca yarra-dd: “D taɣɣarct.”  
\v 3 Inna: “Nḍar i-tt x temmurt!” Inḍar i-tt x temmurt, tedweř d ijj ufiɣar uca yarweř Musa zzayes.  
\v 4 \add Řexdenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec, ṭṭef i-tt zeg unewwar nnes ...” - uca isswiẓẓeḍ \add Musa\add* afus nnes, iṭṭef i-tt uca tedweř \add ɛawed\add* d taɣɣarct deg ufus nnes -  
\v 5 “... ḥima ad amnen belli aqa iban ac-dd SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen, AREBBI n Ibrahim, AREBBI n Isḥaq d AREBBI n Yaɛqub.”   
\m
\v 6 Inna as SIDI ɛawed: “Sidef afus nnec deg weḥsin nnec.” Uca issidef afus nnes deg weḥsin uca umi t-i-dd-ikkes, xzar, afus nnes ibarṣ am wedfeř. \f ◼ \fr 4:6 \ft \+fk aḥsin\ft  - niɣ ‘abeḥrur’.\f*  
\v 7 Uca inna: “Arr afus nnec \add ɛawed\add* deg weḥsin!” Yarra afus nnes deg weḥsin uca iɛqeb issuffeɣ i-t-i-dd \add ɛawed\add* zeg weḥsin, uca xzar, idweř \add ɛawed\add* am \add min iqqimen n\add* arrimet nnes.  
\v 8 “Mařa war zzayek uminen ca u war ɣarek dd-ttesřin i min d asen i ɣa tini řeɛřamet tamezwarut, \add xenni\add* ad amnen di min d asen ɣa tini řeɛřamet taneggarut.  
\v 9 Mařa nitni war uminen ca di tnayen n řeɛřamat-a u war d ac sřin ca, xenni ksi aman n iɣzar uca farreɣ i-ten x řaẓaɣ u aman nni teksid zeg iɣzar ad dewřen d idammen x řaẓaɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Uf. 7:19\x*   
\m
\v 10 \add Řexdenni\add* inna Musa i SIDI: “A Sidi inu!, necc war \add ǧiɣ ca\add* d aryaz n bu-tawařin, iḍennaḍ lla, \add uřa d\add* fariḍennaḍ lla u zeg wami tebdid ad tessiwřed ak-d umsexxar nnec lla, minzi necc ɣari aqemmum ideqřen d iřes ideqřen.”  
\v 11 Inna as SIDI: “Wi iwcin aqemmum i bnadem? Niɣ wi iggin ḥed d aziynun niɣ d adehcur niɣ d wenni ittwařan niɣ d adarɣař? Ma war \add iǧi\add* d Necc, SIDI?  
\v 12 Řexxu, ruḥ \add din\add*, ad iřiɣ ak-d uqemmum nnec, ad ac ssecneɣ mliḥ min ɣa tinid.” \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Mt. 10:19; Mk. 13:11; Lk. 12:12\x*  
\v 13 \add Maca\add* netta inna: “A Sidi inu, sekk s ufus nnec \add man wen i texsed\add* ad tessekked.”  
\v 14 \add Řexdenni\add* ittwassarɣ weɣḍab n SIDI x Musa, inna: “Ma war iǧi Harun, Alawi, d umac? Necc ssneɣ, aqa netta issen ad issiweř. Xzar, aqa ad kic imsagar u xmi cek ɣa iẓar, ad ifarḥ wuř nnes.  
\v 15 Uca cek ad kis tessiwřed, ad as tegged awařen deg uqemmum \add nnes\add*. Ggur ad iřiɣ ak-d uqemmum nnec d uqemmum nnes, ad awem ssɣareɣ min ɣa tinim. \x ◘ \xo 4:15 \xt Uf. 7:2\x*  
\v 16 Netta ad issiweř ak-d řgens deg wemcan nnec. Ad imsar ammu: netta ad ac yiři \add amecnaw\add* aqemmum nnec u cek ad tiřid i netta \add amecnaw\add* AREBBI.  
\v 17 Ad teksid taɣɣarct-a i zi ɣa tegged řeɛřamat deg ufus nnec.”   
\m
\v 18 Iruḥ Musa uca idweř ɣar uḍeggʷař nnes Yitru, inna as: “Ejj ayi ad raḥeɣ, ad ɛeqbeɣ ɣar aytma nni iǧan di Miṣra, ḥima ad ẓareɣ, ma ɛad ddaren.” Inna Yitru i Musa: “Ruḥ di řehna.”  
\v 19 Inna SIDI ɛawed i Musa di Midyan: “Řuḥ, tdewřed ɣar Miṣra, minzi aqa mmuten marra inni tuɣa yarezzun řmewt nnec.”   
\m
\v 20 Iksi Musa tamɣart nnes d iḥenjiren nnes uca issenya i-ten x weɣyuř, idweř-dd ɣar temmurt n Miṣra uca iksi Musa taɣɣarct n AREBBI deg ufus nnes.  
\v 21 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Xmi ɣa traḥed, ad dd-tdewřed ɛawed ɣar Miṣra, xzar ad tegged i firɛun marra lmuɛjizat nni d ac ggiɣ deg ufus nnec. \add Maca\add* Necc ad ssqesḥeɣ uř nnes, řami war ixs ad iḍřeq i řgens.  
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* ad tinid i firɛun: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Israil d mmi d amenzu inu. \x ◘ \xo 4:22 \xt Ḥuc. 11:1; Mt. 2:15\x*  
\v 23 Aqa nniɣ ac: Ejj ad iffeɣ mmi ad ayi iɛbed! \add Maca\add* cek tugid ad t tejjed. Xzar, Necc ad nɣeɣ mmic, amenzu nnec.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 24 Imsar deg webrid, deg ijj n wemcan mani ɣa ssensen, immeřqa SIDI akides u Netta tuɣa ixs ad t ineɣ.  
\v 25 \add Řexdenni\add* teksi Ṣaffura ict n txedmect n weẓru, texten řeɛdařyet n mmis uca teřqef as iḍaren nnes, tenna: “S tidett cek \add teǧid\add* am yijj n yesři n idammen i necc”  
\v 26 Ijja i-t xenni. Řexḍenni tenna: \bd “\+bdit Cek\+bdit* d isři n idammen \+bdit i teǧid\+bdit*!”\bd*, di ssibbet n ixtanen.   
\m
\v 27 Inna SIDI i Harun: “Ruḥ ad teřqid Musa di řexřa!” Uca iruḥ, imsagar akides ɣar wedrar n AREBBI, issudem i-t.  
\v 28 Ixebbar Musa Harun x marra awařen \add i d as inna\add* SIDI wenni i-t-i-dd-issekken uřa x marra řeɛřamat i d as yumur \add ad igg\add*.   
\m
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* iruḥ Musa d Harun, ssmunen marra imɣaren n ayt n Israil,  
\v 30 uca issiweř Harun s marra awařen i tuɣa inna SIDI i Musa uca igga řeɛřamat qibač i tiṭṭawin n řgens.  
\v 31 Uca yumen zzaysen řgens, sřin belli SIDI izziǧez as ayt n Israil umi iẓra řmeḥnet \add i di ǧan\add*, uḍaren uca bendqen \add as\add*.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Musa d Harun zzat i firɛun  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya yudef Musa d Harun ɣar Firɛun, nnan as: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Ejj ad iraḥ řgens inu, ḥima ad ayi iɛeyyed di řexřa!’”  
\v 2 \add Maca\add* firɛun inna: “Min iɛna SIDI umi ɣa sřeɣ i wawař nnes uca ad jjeɣ Israil ad iffeɣ. Necc war ssineɣ SIDI u war ttejjiɣ ad iraḥ Israil.” \f ◼ \fr 5:2 \ft \+fk i wawař nnes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘i tmijja nnes’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:2 \xt Uf. 3:19; Ayub 21:15\x*  
\v 3 Nitni nnan: “AREBBI n Iɛibraniyyen imsagar akidneɣ, ejj aneɣ xenni ad nraḥ ticři n třata n wussan di řexřa, ad nqeddem taɣarṣt i SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, ḥima war d aneɣ iřeqqef s ṭṭaɛun niɣ s ssif.” \x ◘ \xo 5:3 \xt Uf. 3:18\x*  
\v 4 \add Řexdenni\add* inna asen ujeǧid n Miṣra: “Mayemmi, \add a kenniw,\add* Musa d Harun, tessbeddem řgens x řxedmet nnes? Ruḥem kenniw, dewřem ɣar ddquřat i xawem iǧan!”  
\v 5 Inna firɛun: “Xzar, aqa řexxu řgens n temmurt d aṭṭas u kenniw texsem ad ten tessbeddem x warbar n ddquřat i xasen ttwaggent.”   
\m
\v 6 Yumur firɛun deg wass nni i imzeyyaren n řgens u i iweqqafen nsen, inna:  
\v 7 “Zi ssa d tsawent war tticem ɛad řum i řgens maḥend ad zzayes ggen llajur am yiḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ. Jjem ten ad raḥen nitni, ad yrun řum i yixef nsen.  
\v 8 Řqedd n llajur i ggin iḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ ad xasen t teggem \add ɛawed\add*, war zzayes tessneqqisem walu, minzi nitni d ifinyanen. X uya sɣuyyun \add ammu\add*, qqaren: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad nraḥ ad nqeddem taɣarṣt i AREBBI nneɣ.’  
\v 9 Ittxeṣṣa řxedmet ad tiři tedqeř x iryazen-a, ḥima ad dayes řhan ammu uca war tticen \add ɛad\add* taynit i wawařen ixarriqen.”   
\m
\v 10 \add Řexdenni\add* ruḥen imzeyyaren n řgens d iweqqafen nsen \add ggʷejen x Firɛun\add* uca ssiwřen ak-d řgens, nnan: “Ammu i iqqar firɛun: ‘Necc war d awem tticeɣ ca ɛad řum.’  
\v 11 Ruḥem kenniw ad tyarwem řum mani t ɣa tafem, maɣar war xawem tᵉttwakkes walu zi řxedmet nwem.”  
\v 12 \add Řexdenni\add* imbezzeɛ řgens x marra tammurt n Miṣra, ḥima ad yrun iɣeǧ deg wemcan n uřum.  
\v 13 Imzeyyaren ziyyaren xasen, nnan: “Kemmřem řxedmet nwem, kuř ass min dd-ittasen i kuř ass, am mammec tuɣa din řexdenni řum.”  
\v 14 Ttwafarcen iweqqafen n ayt n Israil, inni xasen ggin imzeyyaren n firɛun, nnan \add asen\add*: “Mayemmi war tkemmřem tasɣart nwem n llajur am řebda, iḍennaḍ lla u ɛawed ass-a lla?”  
\v 15 \add Řexdenni\add* usin-dd iweqqafen n ayt n Israil, sɣuyen ɣar firɛun, nnan: “Mayemmi tᵉttegged ammu ak-d isemɣan nnec?  
\v 16 War ittmewci bu uřum i isemɣan nnec, \add waxxa\add* qqaren aneɣ: ‘Ggem llajur!’ U xzar, aqa isemɣan nnec ttᵉtten aɛmud, waxxa řɛib aqa-t di řgens nnec!”  
\v 17 Netta yarra-dd: “Kenniw d ifinyanen, d ifinyanen \add aṭṭas\add*. X uya teqqarem: ‘Jjem aneɣ ad nraḥ maḥend ad nqeddem taɣarṣt i SIDI.’  
\v 18 Ruḥem řexxu ad txedmem. War d awem tticen ɛad \add a\add*řum, \add waxxa\add* ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad teqqimem tsebbřem řeɛbar n llajur!”   
\m
\v 19 \add Řexdenni\add* ẓrin iweqqafen n ayt n Israil, aqa-ten ḥařa, minzi ittwanna: “Kenniw war ssneqṣem walu zi llajur i dd-ittasen i kuř ass.”   
\m
\v 20 \add Umi\add* dd-ffɣen x firɛun, mmṣadafen ak-d Musa d Harun, inni tuɣa din ibedden ḥima ad ten rajan.  
\v 21 Nnan asen: “D SIDI, d wenni kenniw ittwařan, d wenni xawem i ɣa iḥekmen, minzi kenniw aqa tessarzgem aneɣ ɣar firɛun d imsexxaren nnes umi d asen teggim ssif deg ifassen nsen maḥend ad aneɣ nɣen.”   
\m
\v 22 \add Řexdenni\add* idweř Musa ɣar SIDI, inna: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, mayemmi tegged řɣar di řgens-a, mayemmi d ayi tessqaded xenni?  
\v 23 Zeg wami udfeɣ ɣar firɛun ḥima ad ssiwřeɣ s Yisem nnec, ideǧ \add firɛun\add* řgens-a u Cek qaɛ war tfekkid ca řgens nnec.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 SIDI issiweř ak-d Musa  
\m
\v 1 \add Řexdenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Řexxu ad tẓared min ɣa ggeɣ i firɛun, minzi s ufus ijehden ad ten yejj ad raḥen, \add wah,\add* s ufus ijehden ad xasen yaẓẓeř zi temmurt nnes.”  
\v 2 Issiweř AREBBI ɣar Musa, inna as: “Necc d SIDI,  
\v 3 Necc baneɣ-dd i Ibrahim, d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub am Arebbi, Amzemmar x kuřci, \add maca\add* s Yisem inu ‘SIDI’, tuɣa war ɣarsen ttwassneɣ ca.  
\v 4 Ɛawed ssgeɛɛdeɣ Řɛahd inu akidsen aqa ad asen wceɣ tammurt n Kenɛan, tammurt n unewji nsen mani ten tuɣa am yibarraniyyen.  
\v 5 Ɛawed Necc sřiɣ anixses n ayt n Israil, inni ittwaggen d isemɣan zeg Imiṣriyyen, aqa xarrṣeɣ di Řɛahd inu.  
\v 6 S uya ad tinid i ayt n Israil: Necc aqa ayi d SIDI u Necc ad kenniw ssuffɣeɣ zi sadu zayřu n Imiṣriyyen. Necc ad kenniw fekkeɣ zi tesmuɣi nsen, ad kenniw fdiɣ s uɣiř isswiẓẓḍen d řeḥkamat imɣaren.  
\v 7 Ad kenniw qebřeɣ d řgens inu uca ad awem iřiɣ d AREBBI u kenniw ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d wenni tuɣa kenniw issuffuɣen zi sadu zayřu n Imiṣriyyen.  
\v 8 Ad kenniw ssidfeɣ ɣar temmurt mixef ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu maḥend ad tt wceɣ i Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub u Necc ad awem tt wceɣ d řwart, Necc d SIDI!” \f ◼ \fr 6:8 \ft \+fk ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini belli Arebbi tuɣa ijjuǧ ad asen iwc tammurt. Xzar ɛawed Ɛbr. 6:13-18.\f*  
\v 9 Ammu i issiweř Musa ak-d ayt n Israil, maca nitni war sřin ca ɣar Musa zi ssibbet n řeḥṣaret n tnefsect d tasmuɣi iqesḥen.   
\m
\v 10 Uca issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:  
\v 11 “Adef ɣar firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, tinid as ad iḍřeq i ayt n Israil maḥend ad ffɣen zi temmurt nnes.”  
\v 12 \add Maca\add* Musa issiweř zzat i SIDI, inna: “Xzar, ayt n Israil war ɣari dd-sřin, mammec i d ayi ɣa iseř firɛun u necc \add aqa\add* ɣari iyencicen war ittwaxetnen.” \f ◼ \fr 6:12 \ft \+fk necc ... ɣari iyencicen war ittwaxetnen\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini: necc war zemmareɣ x wawař deg wemcan n Arebbi zzat i firɛun.\f*  
\v 13 \add Řexdenni\add* issiweř SIDI ɣar Musa d Harun uca yumur i-ten ad uyuren ɣar ayt n Israil d firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, ḥima ad issuffeɣ ayt n Israil zi temmurt n Miṣra.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tarwa n Rubin, Cimɛun d Lawi  
\m
\v 14 \bd Ina d izeǧifen \+bdit x řaǧat\+bdit* zi tudrin n ibabaten nsen.\bd*  
\m \bd Ayt n Rubin\bd*, amenzu n Israil, \add nitni d\add* Hanuk d Fallu, Ḥaṣrun d Karmi. D yina d řaǧat n Rubin. \x ◘ \xo 6:14 \xt Amz. 46:9; Řxř. 26:5; 1 Im. 5:3\x*   
\m
\v 15 \bd Ayt n Cimɛun\bd* tuɣa aten d Yamuyil d Yamin d Uhad d Yakin d Ṣuḥar d Cawul, mmi n ict n temɣart Takenɛanit. Ina d řaǧat n Cimɛun. \x ◘ \xo 6:15 \xt Amz. 46:10; Řxř. 26:12; 1 Im. 4:24\x*   
\m
\v 16 Ina d ismawen n \bd ayt n Lawi\bd* ɛlaḥsab asettef n wexřaq nsen: Jarcum d Qahat d Marari. Tuɣa \add řmijař n\add* tudart n Lawi mya u-sebɛa u-třatin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt Amz. 46:11; Řxř. 3:17; 26:57; 1 Im. 5:25, 1; 23:6\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 17 \bd Ayt n Jarcum\bd* tuɣa aten d Libna d Cimɛi ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen. \x ◘ \xo 6:17 \xt 1 Im. 6:2; 23:7\x*   
\m
\v 18 \bd Ayt n Qahat\bd* tuɣa aten d Ɛamram d Yiṣhar d Ḥabrun d Ɛuzziyil. Tuɣa \add řmijař n\add* tudart n Qahat mya u-třata u-třatin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 6:18 \xt 1 Im. 6:3; 23:12\x*   
\m
\v 19 \bd Ayt n Marari\bd* tuɣa aten d Maḥli d Muci. Ina d řaǧat n Lawi ɛlaḥsab \add asettef n\add* wexřaq nsen. \x ◘ \xo 6:19 \xt 1 Im. 6:4; 23:21\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Uca \bd Ɛamram\bd* iksi Yukabad, ɛentis, d tamɣart i yixef nnes u nettat turuw as-dd Harun d Musa. Tuɣa \add řmijař\add* n tudart n Ɛamram mya u-sebɛa u-třatin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 6:20 \xt Uf. 2:1; Řxř. 26:59\x*   
\m
\v 21 \bd Ayt n Yiṣhar\bd* tuɣa aten d Quraḥ d Nafaj d Dikri.   
\m
\v 22 \bd Ayt n Ɛuzziyil\bd* tuɣa aten d Micayil d Alṣafan d Sitri.   
\m
\v 23 Uca iksi \bd Harun\bd* Ilicabaɛ, yeǧis n Ɛamminadab, učmas n Naḥcun, d tamɣart i yixef nnes u nettat turuw as-dd Nadab d Abihu d Aliɛazar d Itamar. \x ◘ \xo 6:23 \xt Řxř. 3:2; 26:60; 1 Im. 5:29; 24:1\x*   
\m
\v 24 \bd Ayt n Quraḥ\bd* \add tuɣa aten d\add* Assir d Alqana d Abiyasaf. Ina d řaǧat n Iquraḥiyyen.   
\b  
\m
\v 25 Uca \bd Aliɛazar\bd*, mmis n Harun, iksi icten zeg yessis n Futiyil d tamɣart i yixef nnes uca nettat turuw as-dd \bd Finaḥas\bd*. Ina d izeǧifen \add n tudrin\add* n ibabaten n Ilawiyyen ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.   
\b  
\m
\v 26 Aqa wa d Harun d Musa i umi inna SIDI: “Suffɣem ayt n Israil zi temmurt n Miṣra \add am ttwasettfen nitni\add* ɛlaḥsab iseddiyyen n řɛeskar nsen.”  
\v 27 Ina d inni issiwřen ak-d firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, ḥima ad ssuffɣen ayt n Israil zi Miṣra, Musa d Harun, \add nitni\add* d ina.  
\v 28 Imsar deg wass i issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa di temmurt n Miṣra,  
\v 29 aqa issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna: “Necc d SIDI i ǧiɣ! Marra min d ac qqareɣ, ini t i firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra.”  
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa zzat i SIDI: “Aqa ɣari necc iyencicen war ittwaxetnen, mammec ɣa yegg \add xenni\add* ad ɣari iseǧ firɛun?” \f ◼ \fr 6:30 \ft \+fk Aqa ɣari iyencicen war ittwaxetnen\ft  - xzar afessar ɣar Uf. 6:12.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:30 \xt Uf. 6:12; Uf. 4:10\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Musa d Harun ruḥen ɣar firɛun twařa nneɣni  
\m
\v 1 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Xzar, Necc aqa ggiɣ cek d AREBBI i firɛun d umac Harun ad ac yiři d anabi i cek.  
\v 2 Cek ad tinid marra min zi cek ɣa umureɣ uca Harun, umac, ad issiweř ak-d firɛun, ḥima ad yejj ad ffɣen ayt n Israil zi temmurt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:2 \xt Uf. 4:14\x*  
\v 3 \add Maca\add* Necc ad ssqesḥeɣ uř n firɛun uca ad kettareɣ řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat inu di temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 4 \add Maca\add* firɛun war ɣarwem-dd issḥessi u Necc ad ggeɣ afus inu x Miṣra uca ad ssuffɣeɣ řɛeskarat inu, řgens inu, ayt n Israil, zi temmurt n Miṣra s řeḥkamat imɣaren.  
\v 5 \add Řexdenni\add* ad ssnen Imiṣriyyen belli Necc d SIDI i ǧiɣ xmi ɣa sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu x Miṣra uca ad ssuffɣeɣ ayt n Israil zi řwesṭ nsen.”   
\m
\v 6 Uca ggin Musa d Harun am mammec ten yumur SIDI, \add wah,\add* amenni i ggin.  
\v 7 Tuɣa Musa d ijj n bnadem n tmenyin n iseggʷusa u tuɣa Harun \add d ijj n bnadem\add* n třata u-tmenyin n iseggʷusa, řami ssiwřen ak-d firɛun.   
\m
\v 8 Uca issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa d Harun, inna:  
\v 9 “Mařa issiweř akidwem firɛun, ad yini: ‘Secnem, aqa kenniw tzemmarem ad teggem ict n lmuɛjiza!’, xenni ad tinid i Harun: ‘Ṭṭef taɣɣarct nnec uca nḍar i-tt zzat i firɛun!’, \add xenni\add* ad tedweř d ict n řhaycet.”  
\v 10 Udfen \add xenni\add* Musa d Harun ɣar firɛun uca ggin mammec \add i d asen\add* yumur SIDI. Inḍar Harun taɣɣarct nnes zzat i firɛun d imsexxaren nnes uca tedweř d ict n řhaycet.  
\v 11 \add Řexdenni\add* iřaɣa-dd ɛawed firɛun x imiɣisen d iseḥḥaren, uca tarwa n tseḥḥart n Miṣra ggin ɛawed amenni s tmegga nsen n swadday swadday d ict.  
\v 12 Inḍar kuř ijjen taɣɣarct nnes uca dewřent \add tiɣɣaryen nni\add* d řhaycat. \add Maca\add* taɣɣarct n Harun tsarḍ tiɣɣaryen nsen.  
\v 13 Uř n firɛun idweř iqseḥ uca war ɣarsen isři ca, am mammec tuɣa i d asen inna SIDI \add qbeř\add*.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tesɛa n jjrayeḥ timezwura  
\m
\v 14 \add Řexdenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Uř n firɛun idweř iqseḥ. War ixs ad yejj ad iffeɣ řgens.  
\v 15 Ruḥ tiwecca ɣar ṣṣbeḥ ɣar firɛun. Xzar, netta ad iffeɣ ɣar waman. Cek raja din ɣar tma n yiɣzar uca ksi-dd taɣɣarct nni idewřen d afiɣar deg ufus nnec.  
\v 16 Ad as tinid: ‘SIDI, AREBBI n Iɛibraniyyen issekk ayi-dd ɣarek, inna: Ejj ad iraḥ řgens inu, ḥima ad ayi iɛbed di řexřa! Xzar, ař řexxu war texsed ad tseǧed.  
\v 17 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘S man aya ad tessned belli Necc d SIDI!’ Xzar, Necc ad wteɣ aman i iǧan deg iɣzar s teɣɣarct i ɣari deg ufus inu uca ad dewřen d idammen.  
\v 18 Iseřman i iǧan deg iɣzar ad mmten \add ař ɣa\add* yurṣuḍ iɣzar \add n Nil\add*, ad ɛiffen Imiṣriyyen ad swen aman n iɣzar \add n Nil\add*.’”  
\v 19 Inna SIDI \add ɛawed\add* i Musa: “Ini i Harun: ‘Ksi taɣɣarct nnec, swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec x waman n Miṣra, x iɣezran nsen, x tɣezratin nsen, x iyeřmamen nsen x marra imucan manis ttmunan waman uca ad dewřen d idammen. Ad dewřen d idammen x marra tammurt n Miṣra, \add uřa\add* di \add řeqcuɛ\add* n ukeccuḍ d weẓru.’”   
\m
\v 20 Musa d Harun ggin am mammec \add i d asen\add* yumur SIDI. Issgeɛɛed Harun taɣɣarct, iwta aman nni tuɣa deg iɣzar qibač i tiṭṭawin n firɛun d imsexxaren nnes uca \bd marra aman nni tuɣa deg iɣzar dewřen d idammen.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 7:20 \xt Uf. 17:5; Izhd. 78:44; 105:29\x*  
\v 21 Mmuten iseřman inni tuɣa deg iɣzar uca yurṣuḍ yeɣzar ařami dewřen Imiṣriyyen war zemmaren ad zzayes swen aman uca dewřen \add waman\add* d idammen di marra tammurt n Miṣra.  
\v 22 \add Maca\add* tarwa n tseḥḥart n Miṣra ggin amenni s tmegga nsen n swadday swadday \add ařami\add* uř n firɛun idweř iqseḥ, u netta war ɣarsen issḥess ca, am mammec d asen tuɣa inna SIDI.  
\v 23 Inneqřeb firɛun uca yudef ɣar taddart nnes uca war iggi uř nnes ɛad di man aya.   
\m
\v 24 Marra Imiṣriyyen ɣzan x tma n iɣzar \add n Nil\add* maḥend ad afen aman n tessit, minzi war zemmaren ad swen aman n iɣzar \add n Nil\add*.  
\v 25 \add Ammu i\add* ɛdun sebɛa ussan awarni řami iwta SIDI iɣzar \add n Nil\add*.   
\m
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Adef ɣar firɛun, ini as: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Ejj ad iffeɣ řgens inu ḥima ad ayi iɛbed.  
\v 27 Mařa tugid ad \add ten\add* tejjed ad raḥen, aqa ad wteɣ marra tammurt nnec s iqarqriwen  
\v 28 uca iɣzar \add n Nil\add* ad dd-iseffiy x iqarqriwen, ad \add zzayes-dd\add* geɛɛden, ad adfen ɣar taddart nnec u ɣar wexxam nnec n yiḍeṣ, \add ad dd-asen\add* x qama nnec uřa di taddart n imsexxaren nnec u jar řgens nnec, u \add ɛad\add* deg ifarranen nnec u di tbeqyin nnec.  
\v 29 Ad xak dd-geɛɛden iqarqriwen uřa x řgens nnec u x marra imsexxaren nnec.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\m
\v 1 Inna SIDI \add ɛawed\add* i Musa: “Ini i Harun: ‘Swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec s teɣɣarct nnec x iɣezran, x tɣezratin uřa x iyeřmamen, sgeɛɛed \bd iqarqriwen\bd* x temmurt n Miṣra.’”  
\v 2 Uca isswiẓẓeḍ Harun afus nnes x waman n Miṣra uca geɛɛden-dd iqarqriwen uca dřin tammurt n Miṣra.  
\v 3 Uca uřa d tarwa n tseḥḥart ggin amenni s tmegga nsen n swadday swadday d ict, uca ssgeɛɛden-dd \add ɛawed\add* iqarqriwen x temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 4 Iřaɣa-dd firɛun x Musa d Harun, inna asen: “Ẓaǧem s řaǧaɣ i SIDI ḥima ad xafi iksi iqarqriwen u x řgens inu, uca xenni ad jjeɣ ad iffeɣ řgens, maḥend ad qeddmen tiɣarṣa i SIDI.”  
\v 5 Inna Musa i firɛun: “Ṭṭef xafi řḥurmet meřmi d ayi ɣa tinid ad xak ẓẓaǧeɣ u x imsexxaren nnec u x řgens nnec, maḥend ad xak qeḍɛeɣ iqarqriwen u x tudrin nnec, ad qqimen deg iɣzar waha.”  
\v 6 Yarra-dd xas: “Tiwecca!” Inna \add Musa\add*: “Ad yiři am mammec tennid ḥima ad tessned belli war \add din\add* iǧi ḥed am SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.  
\v 7 Uca iqarqriwen ad mmeksin xak u x tudrin nnec uřa x imsexxaren nnec u x řgens nnec, ad qqimen deg iɣzar waha.”  
\v 8 \add Řexdenni\add* iffeɣ Musa d Harun x firɛun uca iřaɣa Musa i SIDI di ssibbet \add n jjriḥect\add* n iqarqriwen nni tuɣa igga x firɛun.  
\v 9 Uca igga SIDI am mammec dd-ittas ak-d wawař n Musa uca mmuten iqarqriwen \add uca weddaren\add* zi tudrin, zi řemraḥat u zeg iyyaren.  
\v 10 Uca ssmunen ten d iɛurrac uca turṣuḍ \add zzaysen\add* temmurt.  
\v 11 \add Řami\add* iẓra firɛun belli aqa bnadem izemmar ad yarr nnefs, isseqseḥ uř nnes uca war ɣarsen issḥess, am mammec tuɣa inna SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 8:11 \xt Uf. 7:14\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 \add Řexdenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Ini i Harun: ‘Swiẓẓeḍ taɣɣarct nnec, tewted \add zzayes\add* acař n temmurt. \add Xenni\add* ad idweř d nnamus x marra tammurt n Miṣra.’”  
\v 13 Uca ammu i ggin nitni. Isswiẓẓeḍ Harun afus nnes s teɣɣarct nnes i dayes, iwta acař n temmurt. Uca yusa-dd nnamus am x iwdan am x řmař. \bd Marra acař n temmurt idweř d nnamus\bd* di marra tammurt n Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 8:13 \xt Izhd. 105:31\x*  
\v 14 Tarwa n tseḥḥart ggin tizemmar nsen amenni \add ɛawed\add* s tmegga nsen n swadday swadday, maḥend ad ssuffɣen nnamus, maca war zemmaren. Uca tuɣa nnamus x iwdan d řmař.  
\v 15 \add Řexdenni\add* nnan tarwa n tseḥḥart i firɛun: “Man aya d aḍaḍ n AREBBI!” \add Maca\add* isseqseḥ uř n firɛun uca war dd ɣarsen iseǧ ca, am mammec tuɣa inna SIDI.   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Uca inna SIDI i Musa: “Tiwecca kkar zic, ad tbedded zzat i firɛun. Xzar, netta ad iffeɣ ɣar tma n waman, ad as tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Ejj ad iraḥ řgens inu, ḥima ad ayi iɛbed!  
\v 17 Minzi mařa war tejjid řgens inu ad iraḥ, xzar, Necc ad xak ssekkeɣ \bd iyřafen n ibeɛɛac\bd*, x imsexxaren nnec, x řgens nnec, x tudrin nnec, ař ɣa ttwaccurent tudrin n Imiṣriyyen s iyřafen n ibeɛɛac uca amenni uřa d tammurt mani \add zeddɣen\add*.  
\v 18 Deg wass nni ad ssḥuzeɣ tammurt n Jucan mani izeddeɣ řgens inu, ḥima war din ttiřin weyřafen n ibeɛɛac ḥima ad tessned belli Necc d SIDI di řwesṭ n temmurt.  
\v 19 Uca ad ggeɣ \bd ijj n \+bdit ttaman n\+bdit* weṣřaḥ\bd* jar řgens inu d wenni nnec. Tiwecca ad tiři řeɛřamet-a.’”  
\v 20 Uca ammu i igga SIDI. Usin-dd iyřafen imeqqranen n ibeɛɛac x taddart n firɛun, x tudrin n imsexxaren nnes u x marra tammurt n Miṣra uca tᵉttwaxarreb temmurt s iyřafen n ibeɛɛac. \x ◘ \xo 8:20 \xt Izhd. 78:45; 105:31\x*  
\v 21 \add Řexdenni\add* iřaɣa firɛun i Musa d Harun, inna asen: “Ruḥem, tqeddmem taɣarṣt i AREBBI nwem di temmurt-a.”  
\v 22 Inna Musa: “War dd-yusi ad negg ammu, minzi ad nqeddem taɣarṣt i SIDI, AREBBi nneɣ, min iǧan d ict n jjɛifect ɣar Imiṣriyyen. Xzar, mařa nqeddem d taɣarṣt zzat i tiṭṭawin n Imiṣriyyen \add min d asen ittɣiř d\add* jjɛifect, ma war d aneɣ tarejjmen ca? \x ◘ \xo 8:22 \xt Amz. 43:32; 46:34\x*  
\v 23 Ejj aneɣ ad nraḥ ticři n třata n wussan di řexřa, ḥima ad nqeddem taɣarṣt i SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, am mammec d aneɣ yumur Netta.”  
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* inna firɛun: “Necc ad kenniw jjeɣ ad traḥem uca ad tqeddmem taɣarṣt i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, di řexřa, maca war iɛeddeř ad tiggʷijem aṭṭas. Ẓaǧem \add uřa\add* xafi.”  
\v 25 Musa inna: “Aqa ad xak ffɣeɣ, ad ẓẓaǧeɣ i SIDI, ḥima ad ikkes tiwecca iyřafen n ibeɛɛac x firɛun, x imsexxaren nnes uřa x řgens nnes. Maca ittxeṣṣa firɛun war ixeddeɛ twařa nneɣni, war ittejji ad iraḥ řgens, maḥend ad iqeddem taɣarṣt i SIDI.”  
\v 26 \add Řexdenni\add* iffeɣ Musa x firɛun uca iẓẓuǧ i SIDI.  
\v 27 Igga SIDI ɛlaḥsab awař \add i inna\add* Musa uca ikkes iyřafen n ibeɛɛac x firɛun, x imsexxaren nnes, uřa x řgens nnes. War iqqim uřa d ijj \add n ubeɛɛuc\add*.  
\v 28 \add Maca\add* firɛun isseqseḥ uř nnes twařa-ya ɛawed, war ijji ad iraḥ řgens. \x ◘ \xo 8:28 \xt Uf. 8:11\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\m
\v 1 \add Řexdenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Adef ɣar firɛun, ini as: ‘SIDI, AREBBI n Iɛibraniyyen iqqar ammu: Ejj ad iraḥ řgens inu, maḥend ad ayi iɛbed.  
\v 2 Minzi mařa tugid ad \add ten\add* tejjed ad raḥen uca ad ten tᵉṭṭfed ɛad ktar,  
\v 3 xzar, afus n SIDI ad yiři x řmař nnec nni iǧan deg iyyar, x iysan d yeɣyař d yiřeɣman d ifunasen d tfunasin uřa x wuǧi s yijj n \bd ṭṭaɛun iqesḥen aṭṭas\bd*.  
\v 4 Ad ifarz SIDI jar řebhayem n ayt n Israil d řebhayem n Imiṣriyyen, ḥima war ittmetti walu zi marra min iǧan n ayt n Israil.’”  
\v 5 Uca ineyyec SIDI ict n řweqt umi inna: “Tiwecca ad yegg SIDI man aya di temmurt.”  
\v 6 Tiwecca nnes igga SIDI ddeqq nni uca mmuten marra řebhayem n Miṣra, maca zi řebhayem n ayt n Israil war temmut uřa d ict \add zzaysent\add*.  
\v 7 Uca issekk firɛun \add ijjen\add*, uca aqa da, war temmut uřa d ict zi řebhayem n ayt n Israil. \add Maca\add* uř n firɛun idweř iqseḥ uca war yejji ad iffeɣ řgens.   
\b  
\m
\v 8 \add Řexdenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa d Harun: “Ɛemmar uru \add n ifassen\add* nwem s iɣɣeḍ zi tefqunt uca ejj Musa ad t izzuzar deg ujenna qibač i tiṭṭawin n firɛun.  
\v 9 Ad idweř \add iɣɣeḍ\add* d taɛejjajt ifsusen x marra tammurt n Miṣra uca \add taɛejjact\add* ad tedweř d tiḥebba s řewɛi x bnadem u x řmař di marra tammurt n Miṣra.”  
\v 10 Uca ksin iɣɣeḍ zi tefqunt \add am\add* tuɣa bedden zzat i firɛun uca izzuzar i-t Musa deg ujenna uca idweř d \bd tiḥebba s řewɛi\bd* am deg iwdan am di řmař,  
\v 11 \add ařami\add* tarwa n tseḥḥart war zemmaren ad qqimen bedden zzat i Musa di ssibbet n tḥebba, minzi \add tiḥebba\add* ḥekment iseḥḥaren d marra Imiṣriyyen.  
\v 12 \add Maca\add* SIDI isseqseḥ uř n firɛun, \add ařami\add* war d asen iseǧ ca, am mammec tuɣa inna SIDI i Musa.   
\b  
\m
\v 13 \add Řexdenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Tiwecca kkar zic, tbedded zzat i wudem n firɛun uca ini as: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Iɛibraniyyen: Ejj ad iraḥ řgens inu, maḥend ad ayi iɛbed.  
\v 14 Minzi twařa-ya Necc ad cek řeqfeɣ deg wuř s marra jjrayeḥ inu uca uřa d imsexxaren nnec d řgens nnec, ḥima ad tessned belli war iǧi ḥed am Necc di marra tammurt.  
\v 15 Minzi \add ɛad\add* řexxu tuɣa zemmareɣ ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu, ḥima ad cek wteɣ uřa d řgens nnec s ṭṭaɛun uca tuɣa izemmar ad tᵉttwateḥḥid zi temmurt.  
\v 16 \add Maca\add* s tidett Necc ssbeddeɣ cek ḥima ad ac ssecneɣ jjehd inu u ḥima ad ittwacenneɛ Isem inu di marra tammurt. \x ◘ \xo 9:16 \xt Rum. 9:17\x*  
\v 17 Ma tᵉttegged ɛad tiɛinkrifin ḍidd i řgens inu, ḥima war ten tejjid ad raḥen?  
\v 18 Xzar, tiwecca ɣar tsaɛɛet-a Necc ad arreɣ \bd tabrurri iddeqřen\bd* ad tewwet, \add tabrurri\add* i war tuɣi ɛemmarṣ di Miṣra zeg wass i di tᵉttwabna ař i řexxu. \f ◼ \fr 9:18 \ft \+fk ɣar tsaɛɛet-a\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar řweqt-a’.\f*  
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* sekk řexxu \add imsexxaren nnek\add*, maḥend ad ssidfen řebhayem d marra min ɣarek deg iyyar ɣar daxeř. Kuř bnadem niɣ d řmař nni i ɣa ittwafen deg iyyar, war t ssidfen ɣar \add daxeř n\add* taddart, ad xas dd-tewḍa tebrurri uca nitni ad mmten.’”  
\v 20 Wenni iggʷeden awař n SIDI zeg imsexxaren n firɛun, ijja imsexxaren nsen d řebhayem nsen arewřen ɣar daxeř di tudrin.  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* wenni war ittiqqen awař n SIDI s wuř nnes, aqa ijja imsexxaren nnes d řebhayem nnes deg iyyar.  
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec ɣar ujenna uca ad tiři tebrurri x marra tammurt n Miṣra, x iwdan, x řmař u x marra afsu deg iyyaren di temmurt n Miṣra.”  
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* isswiẓẓeḍ Musa taɣɣarct nnes ɣar ujenna uca SIDI igga ajjaj d tebrurri uca tesswiẓẓeḍ tmessi ɣar temmurt. \add Ammu\add* i igga SIDI maḥend ad tewwet tebrurri x temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 24 Tuɣa \add din\add* tabrurri d tmessi ixeǧḍen ak-d tebrurri. Tuɣa tejhed aṭṭas, war tt tuɣi ɛemmarṣ di marra tammurt n Miṣra zeg wami tuɣa tedweř d ijj n řgens. \x ◘ \xo 9:24 \xt Ḥiz. 1:4\x*  
\v 25 Uca tewta tebrurri x marra tammurt n Miṣra, x marra min tuɣa deg iyyar, x iwdan d řmař. Tewta tebrurri \add ɛawed\add* x marra afsu deg iyyar uca ttwarẓent marra tcejjura n řexřa.  
\v 26 Mɣir di tammurt n Jucan, mani ǧan ayt n Israil, war tewti tebrurri.   
\m
\v 27 \add Řexdenni\add* issekk firɛun ad řaɣan i Musa d Harun uca inna asen: “Necc xḍiɣ twařa-ya. SIDI, aqa-t d Amsegged uca necc d řgens inu d iɛeffanen!  
\v 28 Ẓaǧem s řaǧaɣ i SIDI, minzi cfa, aqa ajjajen n AREBBI d aṭṭas uřa d tabrurri. Necc ad kenniw jjeɣ ad traḥem, war kenniw ttᵉṭṭfeɣ ca ɛad \add danita\add*.”  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* inna as Musa: “Meřmi ɣa ffɣeɣ zi tendint ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ ifassen inu ɣar SIDI uca ad bedden wajjajen, war tᵉttiři ɛad tebrurri, maḥend ad tessned belli tammurt aqa-tt n SIDI.  
\v 30 \add Maca\add* xak d x imsexxaren nnec, aqa ssneɣ \add mazal\add* war teggʷedem ca zi SIDI AREBBI.”   
\m
\v 31 Tiffest d imendi tuɣa ttwařeqfen, minzi imendi tuɣa-t s tidrin d tiffest tnewwar.  
\v 32 \add Maca\add* irden d karṣana war ttwařeqfen ca, minzi tuɣa aten war dd-ffiɣen \add ɛad\add*. \f ◼ \fr 9:32 \ft \+fk karṣana\ft  - niɣ ‘dduxn’ niɣ ‘jawars’.\f*  
\v 33 \add Xenni\add* yuyur Musa zi firɛun, iffeɣ zi tendint uca iksi ifassen nnes ɣar SIDI. \add Řexdenni\add* bedden wajjajen d tebrurri uřa d ibuda n wenẓar x temmurt.  
\v 34 \add Umi\add* iẓra firɛun belli anẓar d tebrurri d wajjajen bedden, ixḍa ɛad ktar uca isseqseḥ uř nnes, netta d imsexxaren nnes.  
\v 35 Uř n firɛun yarni di řeqsaḥet, war ijji ad iraḥ ayt n Israil, am mammec tuɣa inna SIDI s tsexxart n Musa. \x ◘ \xo 9:35 \xt Uf. 4:21; 7:3\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Adef ɣar firɛun, minzi Necc ssqesḥeɣ uř nnes d wuř n imsexxaren nnes, ḥima ad ssecneɣ řeɛřamat \add inu\add* di řwesṭ \add n temmurt\add* nnes, \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt Uf. 4:21; 9:34\x*  
\v 2 u ḥima ad tɛawded deg imezzuɣen n mmic d mmis n mmic min ggiɣ ak-d Miṣra, u \add ad tɛawded x\add* řeɛřamat i ggiɣ jar asen, \add maḥend\add* ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI.”  
\v 3 \add Řexdenni\add* yudef Musa d Harun ɣar firɛun, nnan as: “SIDI, AREBBI n Iɛibraniyyen inna: ‘Mecḥař ɣa tekked tugid ad tehwid ɣar wudem inu? Ejj ad iraḥ řgens inu ḥima ad ayi iɛbed.  
\v 4 Minzi mařa tugid ad tejjed ad iraḥ řgens inu, aqa ad ssiwḍeɣ tiwecca \bd tmurɣi\bd* x temmurt nnec.  
\v 5 Ad dřen udem n temmurt ař war izemmar ḥed ad itwařa tammurt \add ɛad\add* uca ad ccen min iqqimen i ittwanejmen, min d awem iqqimen ɛad awarni i tebrurri. Ad tecc \add tmuɣri\add* \add ɛawed\add* marra ticejjura i d awem dd-iɣemmyen deg iyyar.  
\v 6 Uca ad ccurent tudrin nnec d tudrin n imsexxaren nnec d tudrin n marra Imiṣriyyen. Ammu war tt ẓrin ɛemmarṣ ibabaten nnec d řejdud n ibabaten nnec zeg wami ten tuɣa x temmurt ɣar wass-a.’” Uca idweř-dd netta, ismeḥ di firɛun.  
\v 7 Nnan as imsexxaren n firɛun: “Ař meřmi i d aneɣ ɣa yiři wanita d řfex? Ejj ad raḥen iryazen nni, maḥend ad ɛebden SIDI AREBBI nsen! Ma war tessined ɛad belli Miṣra aqa tᵉttwaxarreb?”  
\v 8 \add Řexdenni\add* ssiwḍen \add imsexxaren n firɛun\add* Musa d Harun ɛawed ɣar firɛun. Netta inna asen: “Ruḥem, ɛebdem SIDI, AREBBI nwem! \add Ini ayi\add*, min ɛnan inni ixsen ad raḥen?”  
\v 9 Inna Musa: “Ad nraḥ \add ak-d\add* iḥramen nneɣ d iwessura nneɣ, s iḥenjiren nneɣ d tḥenjirin nneɣ, s wuǧi nneɣ d ifunasen d tfunasin nneɣ, minzi ɣarneɣ ijj n Řɛid i SIDI.”  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd xasen: “\add Xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad yiři SIDI \add aṭṭaṣ\add* akidwem mařa ad jjeɣ ad traḥem kenniw d iḥenjiren imeẓyanen nwem. Xzarem, aqa kenniw tenwim řɣar!  
\v 11 War ittiři amenni. Jjem ad ɛebden iryazen ijehden i SIDI, minzi d man aya i tᵉttexsem.” Uca uẓẓřen xasen zi qibač n wudem n firɛun.   
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec x temmurt n Miṣra, ḥima tamurɣi ad tgeɛɛed x temmurt n Miṣra, maḥend ad tecc marra afsu \add aziza\add* n temmurt, marra min iceṭṭen x tebrurri.”   
\m
\v 13 Isswiẓẓeḍ Musa ɣar teɣɣarct nnes x temmurt n Miṣra uca igga SIDI ad dd-isuḍ ijj n usemmiḍ i dd-yusin zi ccarq x temmurt war iqeṭṭin marra ass nni d marra ǧiřet nni. Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ yiwi-dd usemmiḍ tamurɣi. \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt Izhd. 78:46; 105:34,35\x*  
\v 14 Tgeɛɛed-dd \bd tmurɣi\bd* x marra tammurt n Miṣra, tṣeyyeḥ x marra jjwayeh n Miṣra. Aqa tuɣa řḥař yewɛar aṭṭas. Tamurɣi am tanita war tt tuɣi qbeř uca war tᵉttiři ɛemmarṣ zi ssa ɣar zzat.  
\v 15 Aqa dřint udem n marra tammurt ařami tessutem temmurt. Nitenti ccint marra afsu n temmurt d marra řɣiǧet n tcejjura i tuɣa iqqimen zi tebrurri. Di marra tammurt n Miṣra war iqqim walu zi marra tuzzizewt di tcejjura niɣ deg wefsu n iyyar.  
\v 16 \add Řexdenni\add* iřaɣa firɛun deɣya i Musa d Harun, inna: “Aqa xḍiɣ ak-d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, uřa akidwem.  
\v 17 Ttzawgeɣ řexxu ad ayi tsamḥem x uxeṭṭu inu twařa-ya. Ẓaǧem s řaǧaɣ i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ḥima ad xafi ikkes řmewt-a waha.”  
\v 18 Uca iffeɣ x firɛun uca iẓẓuǧ s řaǧaɣ ɣar SIDI.  
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* ijja SIDI ad dd-iɛqeb usemmiḍ i dd-yusin zi ccarq ɣar řɣarb, \add issjehd i-t\add* aṭṭas, uca ikkes \add usemmiḍ\add* tamurɣi, inḍar i-tt di Řebḥar n Telga. War teqqim uřa d ict n tmurɣi di marra jjwayeh n Miṣra. \f ◼ \fr 10:19 \ft \+fk inḍar itt\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘iwwet i-tt’. \fk Řebḥar n Telga\ft  - niɣ ‘Řebḥar n Teřga’.\f*  
\v 20 \add Maca\add* isseqseḥ SIDI uř n firɛun \add umi\add* war ijji ayt n Israil ad raḥen.   
\b  
\m
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec ɣar ujenna, \add xenni\add* ad tiři \bd taǧest\bd* x temmurt n Miṣra ař ɣa tafed tzemmared ad tḥadid taǧest.”  
\v 22 Isswiẓẓeḍ Musa afus nnes ɣar ujenna uca tehwa-dd \bd taǧest tejhed x marra tammurt n Miṣra, třata n wussan\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 10:22 \ft \+fk třata n wussan\ft  - niɣ ‘teřtyam’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:22 \xt Řqḍ. 16:27; Izhd. 105:27, 28; Izhd. 115:7\x*  
\v 23 Uřa d ijj war itwiři wenneɣni. Uřa d ijj war ikkar zeg wemcan nnes třata n wussan. \add Maca\add* marra ayt n Israil tuɣa ɣarsen tafawt deg imucan mani tuɣa zeddɣen.  
\v 24 \add Řexdenni\add* iřaɣa firɛun i Musa, inna: “Ruḥem, tɛebdem SIDI! Jjem waha ad iqqim wuǧi nwem d ifunasen d tfunasin nwem. \add Maca\add* tzemmarem ad dd-tawyem iḥenjiren imeẓyanen akidwem.”  
\v 25 Yarra-dd \add xas\add* Musa: “Ittxeṣṣa cek ɛawed ad aneɣ tewced deg ufus tiɣarṣa uřa d tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ. Ad tent nessewjed \add d tɣarṣṭ\add* i SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.  
\v 26 Uřa d řebhayem nneɣ ittxeṣṣa ad kidneɣ raḥent, war ittɣimi uřa d ijj n ucekrud, minzi zzaysent i ɣa neksi, ḥima ad neɛbed SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, minzi war nessin s minzi ɣa neɛbed SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, ař din ɣa naweḍ.”  
\v 27 \add Maca\add* SIDI isseqseḥ uř n firɛun uca yugi ad ten yejj ad raḥen.  
\v 28 Inna as firɛun: “Aggʷej xafi! Ḥḍa, ḥima war tẓarred \add ɛad\add* udem inu, minzi ass i di ɣa tẓared udem inu, ad temmted!”  
\v 29 Inna Musa: “\add Ad yiři\add* am mammec i tennid: war ẓarreɣ ɛad udem nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 10:29 \xt Ɛbr. 11:27\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Abarreḥ s jjriḥect wiss ɛecra  
\m
\v 1 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Ad řeqfeɣ ɛad \add mɣir\add* s yicten jjriḥect x firɛun d Miṣra. Awarni ta ad kenniw issekk ssa. Ɣar uneggar xmi kenniw ɣa yejj ad truḥem marra, ad xawem yaẓẓeř ssa s tidett.  
\v 2 Siweř xenni deg imezzuɣen n řgens maḥend ad ittar kuř aryaz zeg wajjar nnes u kuř tamɣart zi tajjart nnes řeqcuɛ n nnuqart d wureɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 11:2 \xt Uf. 3:22; 12:35\x*  
\v 3 SIDI iwca as i řgens arḍa di tiṭṭawin n Imiṣriyyen. Ɛawed tuɣa Musa d ijj weryaz s ccan ameqqran di temmurt n Miṣra di tiṭṭawin n řgens u di tiṭṭawin n imsexxaren n firɛun. \x ◘ \xo 11:3 \xt Uf. 12:36\x*  
\v 4 Inna Musa: “Ammu i inna SIDI: ‘Ɣar wezyen n ǧiřet Necc ad ɛduɣ di řwesṭ n Miṣra \x ◘ \xo 11:4 \xt Uf. 12:29\x*  
\v 5 uca \bd ad immet kuř amenzu di temmurt n Miṣra\bd*, zeg umenzu n firɛun, wenni iqqimen x řɛarc n tgeldit, ař amenzu n tayya, tenni iqqimen awarni i tsirt \add tḥarri imendi\add*, uřa d kuř amenzu zi řebhayem. \x ◘ \xo 11:5 \xt Uf. 12:12\x*  
\v 6 Ad din tiři ict n tɣuyyit d tameqqrant x marra tammurt n Miṣra i war tuɣi ɛemmarṣ niɣ ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad tiři.  
\v 7 \add Maca\add* ɣar marra ayt n Israil, war ittẓu uřa d ijj n weqzin x iwdan uřa x řmař, maḥend ad tessnem, belli SIDI ittegg řfarz jar Imiṣriyyen d Israil.’  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* ad ɣari dd-hwan marra imsexxaren nnec, ad ayi bendqen, ad inin: ‘Ffeɣ cek d marra řgens i cek iḍeffaren deg iṣuraf nnec!’ Awarni man aya necc ad ffɣeɣ.’” Uca iffeɣ x firɛun, tekkar dayes tmessi s uxeyyeq. \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Uf. 12:30\x*   
\m
\v 9 \add Aqa\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Firɛun war d awem ittesři ca, ḥima ad mɣarent řeɛřamat inu di temmurt n Miṣra.”  
\v 10 Aqa Musa d Harun ggin marra řeɛřamat-a zzat i wudem n firɛun, maca SIDI tuɣa isseqseḥ uř n firɛun ařami war ijji ad ffɣen ayt n Israil zi temmurt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 11:10 \xt Uf. 9:16; Rum. 9:17\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Ařeqqem n Tɣarṣt n Useɛdu niɣ ‘Pasxa’  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa d Harun di temmurt n Miṣra, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Ayur-a ad awem yiři d azeǧif n iyuren. Ad awem yiři wa i kenniw d amezwaru n iyuren n useggʷas.  
\v 3 Siweř ɣar marra tamesmunt n Israil, ini: ‘Deg wass wiss ɛecra ad iksi kuř ijj i yixef nnes ijj n yezmar x \add marra\add* \add řaǧ n\add* taddart \add i dd-iqqarṣen zeg\add* ibabaten, \add ijj n\add* yezmar x \add ict n\add* taddart. \f ◼ \fr 12:3 \ft \+fk tamesmunt\ft  - niɣ ‘jmaɛet’. \fk izmar\ft  - niɣ ‘iɣiḍ’. \fk \+bdit řaǧ n\+bdit* taddart\ft  - aqa din nican di tira ’taddart n ibabaten’, aqa-t d ijj n wawař Aɛibrani nni ixs ad yini ‘řaǧ i iǧan ɣar wenni iǧan d babatsen’.\f*  
\v 4 \add Maca\add* mařa \add raǧ n\add* taddart tuɣa imẓi i yezmar, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad iksi ak-d wajjar nnes yudsen ɣar taddart nnes ɛlaḥsab \add řqedd n\add* iwdan. Zi jjihet n yezmar ad tewtem řeḥsab i min ɣa yecc kuř ijjen.  
\v 5 Ad yiři d izmar icnan qaɛ, awtem n ijj n useggʷas. Ad \add t\add* teksim zeg iḥuřiyyen niɣ zeg iɣayḍen. \x ◘ \xo 12:5 \xt Lawi 1:3; 22:21; Mal. 1:8; 1 Bṭ. 1:19\x*  
\v 6 Ad t txemmřem ař ass arbeɛṭac zeg uyur-a uca ad as iɣarṣ marra agraw n tmesmunt n Israil jar beddu n wezyen n wass ař dd-tewḍa tmeddit.  
\v 7 Ad ksin ca zeg idammen uca ad t ggen x tnayen n řeḍruf \add i iǧan ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart\add* u x tnebdat sennej \add i tewwart\add* n tudrin mani t ɣa ccen.  
\v 8 Ad ccen aysum di ǧiřet nni, \add aysum\add* icennfen ɣar tmessi ak-d weɣrum břa antun. Ad t ccen s řebzar \add yarzeg\add*. \x ◘ \xo 12:8 \xt Řxř. 9:11; 1 Kur. 5:8\x*  
\v 9 War t ttᵉttem ca d aziza niɣ yenwan deg waman, maca mɣir mařa ittwacennef di tmessi, ak-d uzeǧif nnes d iḍaren nnes d wadan nnes.  
\v 10 War zzayes ttejjim walu ɣar ṣṣbeḥ, maca min zzayes ɣa iqqimen ɣar ṣṣbeḥ, ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad t tcemḍem di tmessi.  
\v 11 Ammu i d awem ittxeṣṣa ad t teccem: tajɛinna nwem ad tiři tebyes, sandaliyat nwem deg iḍaren nwem u taɣɣarct nwem deg ufus nwem uca ad t teccem deɣya. Aqa-t d \bd \+bdit Taɣarṣt n\+bdit* Useɛdu n SIDI\bd*.  
\v 12 \add Minzi\add* di ǧiřet-a, Necc ad ɛduɣ x temmurt n Miṣra uca ad wteɣ kuř amenzu di temmurt n Miṣra, ammu deg iwdan uřa di řmař, uca ad ssiwḍeɣ řeḥkamat inu x marra irebbiten n Miṣra, Necc d SIDI!  
\v 13 Uca idammen ad awem iřin d ict n řeɛřamet x tudrin mani \add tzeddɣem\add* kenniw. \add Mařa\add* ẓriɣ idammen, \bd ad xawem ɛduɣ\bd*. War tᵉttiři jjriḥect ineqqen jar awem, xmi ɣa wteɣ tammurt n Miṣra.  
\v 14 Ass-a ad awem yiři d ijj n wass i řidaret uca ad zzayes tɛeyydem i SIDI. Aqa-tt d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem, ḥima ad zzayes tɛeyydem. \x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt Uf. 5:1\x*  
\v 15 Sebɛa n wussan ad teccem aɣrum břa antun. Nican deg wass amezwaru ad tessuffɣem antun zi tudrin nwem, minzi man wen i ɣa iccen ca s wentun, zeg wass amezwaru ař ass wiss sebɛa, bnadem nni ad ittwaqess zi Israil. \f ◼ \fr 12:15 \ft \+fk bnadem\ft  - di tira Tɛibranit nican ‘řeɛmar’.\f*  
\v 16 Deg wass amezwaru ad yiři ijj n umuni iqeddsen uca \add ɛawed\add* deg wass wiss sebɛa ad din yiři ijj n umuni iqeddsen. Uřa d ict n řxedmet war tᵉttwagg ca deg \add wussan\add* nni. Mɣir min ɣa yecc kuř ijj, d man aya waha iɛeddeř ad zzaywem ittwassewjed.  
\v 17 Ad teḥḍam \add Řɛid n\add* Weɣrum břa Antun, minzi deg wass nni aqa ssuffɣeɣ-dd kenniw zi temmurt n Miṣra. Ad teḥḍam ass-a di \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem, aqa-tt d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda.  
\v 18 Deg \add uyur\add* amezwaru, deg wass wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur, di ǧiřet, ad teccem aɣrum břa antun ař ǧiřet n wass waḥit u-ɛicrin zeg uyur. \x ◘ \xo 12:18 \xt Lawi 23:5; Řxř. 28:16\x*  
\v 19 Sebɛa n wussan war ittwiffi wentun di tudrin nwem, minzi man wen i ɣa iccen zi min iǧan s wentun, ma d abarrani niɣ d mmis n temmurt, bnadem nni ad ittwaqess zi tmesmunt n Israil.  
\v 20 War ttᵉttem walu zi min iǧan s wentun. Di marra tizeddaɣ nwem ad teccem aɣrum břa antun.’” \x ◘ \xo 12:20 \xt Aɛwd. 16:3\x*   
\m
\v 21 Iřaɣa Musa i marra imɣaren n Israil, inna asen: “Ṭṭfem, ksim \add ijjen zeg\add* wuǧi i yixef nwem, i řaǧat nwem u ɣarṣem t i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 12:21 \xt Ɛbr. 11:28\x*  
\v 22 Ṭṭfem ict n tqebbiḍt n tɛelǧet, sɣeḍsem \add tt\add* deg idammen nni iǧan di ṭṭebṣi, ɣemsen xenni zeg idammen i iǧan di ṭṭebṣi x tnebdat sennej \add i tewwart\add* u x tnayen n řeḍruf \add ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart\add*. Ař ṣṣbeḥ war itteffeɣ uřa d ijjen zzaywem zi tewwart n taddart nnes. \f ◼ \fr 12:22 \ft \+fk taɛelǧet\ft  - s Teɛrabt: زُوفَا.\f*  
\v 23 SIDI ad iẓwa \add x temmurt\add*, maḥend ad iwwet Imiṣriyyen, \add maca xmi\add* ɣa iẓar idammen x tnebdat n nnej u x tnayen n řeḍruf \add ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart\add*, xenni ad iɛdu SIDI tawwart nni, war ittejji amteḥḥay ad yadef ɣar tudrin nwem, ḥima ad iwwet. \x ◘ \xo 12:23 \xt Ɛbr. 11:28\x*  
\v 24 Ḥḍam awař-a \add i nniɣ\add*, aqa d tewṣeyyet i cek u i iḥenjiren nnec i řebda.  
\v 25 Ad yiři, xmi ɣa tadfem ɣar temmurt tenni d awem ɣa yewc SIDI, am mammec inna Netta, ad teḥḍam aɛbad-a \add n řidaret\add*.  
\v 26 Uca x minni d awem ɣa inin iḥenjiren nwem: ‘Min ixs ad yini weɛbad-a \add n řidaret\add* i kenniw?’, \x ◘ \xo 12:26 \xt Yac. 4:6\x*  
\v 27 \add xenni\add* ad tinim: ‘Aqa d Taɣarṣt n Useɛdu i SIDI wenni iɛdun x tudrin n ayt n Israil di Miṣra, umi iwta Imiṣriyyen uca ifekk tudrin nneɣ.’” Řexdenni yuḍar řgens uca bendqen nitni.  
\v 28 Ruḥen ayt n Israil uca ggin am mammec ten yumur SIDI i Musa d Harun u ammu i tt ggin. \x ◘ \xo 12:28 \xt Ɛbr. 11:28\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Jjriḥect wiss ɛecra  
\m
\v 29 \bd Tuɣa ɣar wezyen n ǧiřet \+bdit umi\+bdit* iwta SIDI marra imenza di temmurt n Miṣra \+bdit s řmewt\+bdit*,\bd* zeg umenzu n firɛun, wenni iqqimen x řɛarc nnes, ař amenzu n umeḥbus i iǧan di řeḥbes, uřa d marra imenza n řebhayem. \f ◼ \fr 12:29 \ft \+fk řeḥbes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘taddart n wanu’. Ad taɣ ḥebbsen Imiṣriyyen imeḥbas deg ijj n wanu ḥima war zemmaren ad arewřen.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:29 \xt Izhd. 78:51; 105:36; 135:8; 136:10\x*   
\m
\v 30 Ikkar firɛun di ǧiřet nni, netta d marra imsexxaren nnes d marra Imiṣriyyen uca tuɣa din ict n tɣuyyit temɣar minzi war tuɣi uřa d ict n taddart mani war iǧi umettin. \x ◘ \xo 12:30 \xt Izhd. 105:38\x*  
\v 31 Uca iřaɣa-dd i Musa d Harun s ǧiřet, inna: “Kkarem, teffɣem zi řwesṭ n řgens inu, kenniw \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ayt n Israil, ruḥem, tɛebdem SIDI, am mammec tennam kenniw.  
\v 32 Awyem uǧi nwem d ifunasen d tfunasin nwem, am mammec tennam. Ruḥem, \add maca ttzawgeɣ kenniw,\add* barkem ayi necc ɛawed!”  
\v 33 Zeyyaren Imiṣriyyen aṭṭas x řgens, maḥend nitni ad ffɣen s uqeǧeq zi temmurt, minzi \add Imiṣriyyen\add* nnan: “Aqa neccin marra d imettan!”  
\v 34 Uca yiwi řgens arecti nnes qbeř ma ɣa inḍu uca tibeqyin nnḍen tent jar warruḍ nsen x ṭɣarḍin nsen. \f ◼ \fr 12:34 \ft \+fk arecti nnes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘arecti nsen’.\f*  
\v 35 Ayt n Israil ggin ɛlaḥsab awař \add i d asen inna\add* Musa, ttaren řeqcuɛ n nnuqart d wureɣ d warruḍ zeg Imiṣriyyen. \x ◘ \xo 12:35 \xt Uf. 3:21; 11:2; Izhd. 105:37\x*  
\v 36 SIDI iwca řgens arḍa di tiṭṭawin n Imiṣriyyen, wcin asen min ttaren, u \add ammu i\add* keccḍen nitni Imiṣriyyen. \f ◼ \fr 12:36 \ft \+fk Imiṣriyyen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Miṣra’.\f*   
\m
\v 37 Fesyen ayt n Israil iqiḍan nsen, \add uyuren\add* zi Raɛamsis ɣar Sukkut, \add tuɣa aten\add* ɛřaḥař di setta-myat-ařef x iḍaren, ttwaḥesben iryazen waha, břa iḥenjiren.  
\v 38 Igeɛɛed akidsen ijj n ubarru d ameqqran n ɛřam kuř iwdan, \add xenni ɛawed\add* uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin, aqa-tt d ict n tḥimart temɣar aṭṭas.  
\v 39 S warecti i kidsen dd-iwyen zi Miṣra ggʷin tifḍirin břa antun, minzi tuɣa \add ɛad\add* war ismim, minzi uẓẓřen xasen-dd zi Miṣra u war zemmaren ad bedden maḥend ad areyyḥen u war sswejden macca i webrid i yixef nsen.   
\b  
\m
\v 40 Tuɣa \add řmijař n\add* tzeddiɣt n ayt n Israil di Miṣra, \add řmijar\add* i \add din\add* izedɣen, arebɛa-mya u-třatin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 12:40 \xt Amz. 15:13; Řex. 7:6; Gal. 3:17\x*  
\v 41 Ɣar uneggar n arebɛa-mya u-třatin n iseggʷusa, deg wass nni simant nnes, ffɣen marra řɛeskar n SIDI zi temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 42 Tanita aqa-tt d ict n ǧiret ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwaḥḍa \add i řewqar\add* i SIDI, maɣar Netta indeh i-ten zi temmurt n Miṣra. Ǧiřet-a tanita, aqa-tt i SIDI. Ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwaḥda zi marra ayt n Israil, di \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Taɣarṣt n Useɛdu d ubarrani  
\m
\v 43 Inna SIDI i Musa d Harun: “D ta d tawṣeyyet x \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu: war zzayes ittett mmis n ubarrani,  
\v 44 \add maca\add* kuř ismeɣ immesɣen zeg ijj n weryaz s nnuqart, izemmar ad zzayes yecc, mařa txetned as.  
\v 45 Amɛezzeb d ucewwař war zzayes ttᵉtten ca.  
\v 46 Ad ittwacc di taddart d ict u war itteffeɣ walu zeg weysum nni ɣar barra n taddart uca war zzayes ittareẓẓi uřa d ijj n yiɣes. \x ◘ \xo 12:46 \xt Řxř. 9:12; Yḥ. 19:36\x*  
\v 47 Marra tamesmunt n Israil ad tegg \add amenni\add*.  
\v 48 Mařa ca n ubarrani innewjew-dd ɣarek uca ixs ad issewjed \add Taɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i SIDI, ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaxten kuř aryaz nni ɣares iǧan. Řexdenni ad dd-iqarreb, ad tt issewjed, uca ad yiři am wenni dd-ixeřqen di temmurt. Maca uřa d ijj zeg inni war ixtinen war izemmar ad zzayes yecc. \x ◘ \xo 12:48 \xt Yac. 5:5\x*  
\v 49 Ad din yiři ijj n uzerf i wenni dd-ixeřqen \add di temmurt\add* u i ubarran i izeddɣen jar awem am ubarrani.”  
\v 50 Uca marra ayt n Israil ggin am mammec d asen yumur Musa d Harun, ammu i tt ggin.  
\v 51 Uca imsar deg wass nni simant nnes issuffuɣ SIDI ayt n Israil zi temmurt n Miṣra \add am ttwasettfen nitni\add* ɛlaḥsab \add iseddiyyen n\add* řɛeskar nsen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Azerf i imenza  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:  
\v 2 “Sqeddes ayi kuř amenzu, wenni zi jar ayt n Israil yarezmen řemřawet \add d amezwaru\add*, am zeg iwdan am zi řebhayem. Netta aqa inu.” \x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt Uf. 22:29; 34:19; Lawi 27:26; Řxř. 3:13; 8:17; Lk. 2:23\x*  
\v 3 Inna Musa i řgens: “Idarem ass-a min di teffɣem zi Miṣra, zi taddart n tesmuɣi, minzi SIDI issuffeɣ-dd kenniw zzayes s ufus ijehden. \add Deg wass-a\add* war tᵉttettem walu min di iǧa wentun. \f ◼ \fr 13:3 \ft \+fk tasmuɣi\ft  - aqa isemɣan ddaren di tesmuɣi minzi war ɣarsen bu tiřelli.\f*  
\v 4 Ass-a ad teffɣem, deg uyur n Abib. \x ◘ \xo 13:4 \xt Uf. 23:15\x*  
\v 5 Mařa SIDI issidef i cek ɣar temmurt n ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥittiyyen d Imuriyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen, x tenni ijjuǧ i řejdud nwem ad ac tt iwc, tammurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment, \add xenni\add* ad teḥḍam aɛbad-a \add n řidaret\add* deg uyur-a.  
\v 6 Sebɛa n wussan ad tecced aɣrum břa antun uca deg wass wiss sebɛa \add ad din yiři\add* ijj n Řɛid i SIDI.  
\v 7 Sebɛa n wussan ad ittwacc weɣrum břa antun uca war ɣarek ittwiffi min ixemmren. Di marra jjwayeh nnec war ittwifi wentun ɣarek.  
\v 8 Deg wass nni ad tḥajid i mmic, ad as tinid: Man aya di ṭṭweɛ n min d ayi igga SIDI umi dd-ffɣeɣ zi Miṣra.  
\v 9 Ad ac yiři am yijj n uceyyar x ufus nnec u i řidaret jar tiṭṭawin nnec, maḥend Ccariɛa n SIDI ad tiři deg uqemmum nnec, minzi s ufus ijehden issuffeɣ SIDI i kenniw zi Miṣra.  
\v 10 S uya i ɣa teḥḍid tawsiyyet-a di řweqt nnes i d as ittwaggen, zeg useggʷas ɣar useggʷas.   
\m
\v 11 Ad yiři xmi cek ɣa issidef SIDI di temmurt n ayt n Kenɛan, am mammec i d ac ijjuǧ uřa i řejdud nnec, uca iwca ac tt,  
\v 12 \add xenni\add* ad tesseɛdud ɣar SIDI kuř \add amenzu\add* i yarezmen řemřawet \add d amezwaru\add* uřa d kuř amenzu n řebhayem i yarezmen řemřawet \add d amezwaru\add*: iwetman ad iřin i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 13:12 \xt Uf. 22:30; 34:19; Lawi 27:26; Řxř. 8:17; Ḥiz. 44:30\x*  
\v 13 Maca kuř \add amenzu\add* i yarezmen řemřawřet n weɣyuř \add d amezwaru\add*, ad t tefdid s yijj zeg wuǧi. Mařa war t tefdid, ad as tarẓed iri. Kuř amenzu n bnadem zeg iḥenjiren nnec ad t tefdid.  
\v 14 Uca ad imsar, xmi cek ɣa isseqsa mmic tiwecca, ad yini: ‘Manawya?’, ad as tinid: ‘Aqa issuffuɣ aneɣ-dd SIDI zi Miṣra s ufus ijehden, zi taddart n tesmuɣi.  
\v 15 \add Řami\add* d aneɣ ibedd firɛun deg webrid i wuffuɣ nneɣ, imsar aqa SIDI inɣa marra imenza di temmurt n Miṣra, zeg umenzu n bnadem ař amenzu n řebhimet. X uya qeddmeɣ kuř amenzu i yarezmen řemřawet \add d amezwaru\add* d taɣraṣt i SIDI, \add maca\add* kuř amenzu jar iḥenjiren inu, ad t fdiɣ.  
\v 16 Ad yiři d aceyyar x ufus nnec d ijj n ufiřu n useggem jar tiṭṭawin nnec, minzi SIDI aqa issuffeɣ aneɣ-dd zi Miṣra s ufus ijehden.’” \x ◘ \xo 13:16 \xt Uf. 13:9, Aɛwd. 6:8, Awřn. 3:3 \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 17 \add Umi\add* ijja firɛun řgens ad iraḥ, war ten indih AREBBI ɣar webrid n temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen, waxxa nettat tudes, minzi AREBBI inna: “Maḥend war ittendemmi řgens xmi ɣa iẓar řbaruḍ uca ad dd-idweř ɣar Miṣra.”  
\v 18 Indeh AREBBI řgens, maḥend ad ikk x webrid n řexřa ɣar Řebḥar n Telga. Uca geɛɛden ayt n Israil zi Miṣra wejden i umenɣi.  
\v 19 Iksi Musa akides iɣsan n Yusuf, minzi netta issjuǧ ayt n Israil s ict n tẓaǧit, inna: “S tidett ad ɣarwem dd-yarzef AREBBI, uca ad tessgeɛɛdem iɣsan inu ssa akidwem!” \x ◘ \xo 13:19 \xt Amz. 50:25; Yac. 24:32\x*  
\v 20 Uca fesyen iqiḍan nsen, \add ggʷejen\add* x Sukkut uca wtin iqiḍan nsen di Itam, ɣar ṭṭarf n řexřa.  
\v 21 SIDI izwar i tiṭṭawin nsen deg uẓiř deg ijj n uqellij n useynu, maḥend ad ten igewwed deg webrid, u di ǧiřet deg ijj n uqellij n tmessi, ḥima ad ɣarsen igg tafawt, ḥima \add ad taf zemmaren\add* ad uyuren ass d ǧiřet.  
\v 22 Deg wass war dd-ikkis aqellij n useynu zzat i uɣembub n řgens uřa di ǧiřet \add war dd-ikkis\add* aqellij n tmessi.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Musa d řgens ẓwan Řebḥar n Telga  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:  
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, \add maḥend\add* ad dd-dewřen uca ad wten iqiḍan nsen zzat i Fi-Haxirut, jar Migdul d řebḥar, qibač i Baɛal-Ṣafun. Arendad nnes ad tewtem iqiḍan nwem x tma n řebḥar. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Řxř. 33:7\x*  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* ad yini firɛun x ayt n Israil: ‘Aqa nitni weddaren di temmurt, aqa řexřa iḥṣar i-ten.’  
\v 4 Uca Necc ad ssqesḥeɣ uř n firɛun, \add ḥima\add* ad ten iḍfar u Necc ad ttwassɛuǧiɣ x firɛun u x marra řɛeskar nnes uca ad ssnen Imiṣriyyen belli Necc d SIDI.” Uca ammu i tt ggin nitni. \x ◘ \xo 14:4 \xt Uf. 4:21; 10:20\x*   
\m
\v 5 Uca xebbaren i ujeǧiḍ n Miṣra belli řgens yarweř. \add Xenni\add* ibeddeř wuř n firɛun d imsexxaren nnes x řgens uca nnan: “Mammec i negga aya, nessekk Israil zi tesmuɣi i iggin i neccin?”  
\v 6 Uca iḥezzem \add Firɛun\add* akarru nnes, iksi akides řgens nnes.  
\v 7 Iksi akides setta-mya n ikarruten icewwaren d marra ikarruten n Miṣra uca \add igga\add* acewwar n ineɣrafen \add zi řɛeskar\add* nnes x kuř \add ijj zzaysen\add*.  
\v 8 Aqa isseqseḥ SIDI uř n firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, uca yardef netta ayt n Israil, maca ayt n Israil tuɣa ffɣen s yijj n ufus ittwassgeɛɛden.  
\v 9 Aredfen ten Imiṣriyyen uca iwḍen ɣarsen s marra iysan d ikarruten n firɛun d imnayen nnes d řɛeskar nnes, ɣar Fi-Haxarut, ɣar ujemmaḍ n Baɛal-Ṣafun, mani wtin iqiḍan nsen ɣar řebḥar. \x ◘ \xo 14:9 \xt Yac. 24:6\x*  
\v 10 \add Řami\add* ten dd-yudes firɛun, ssgeɛɛden ayt n Israil tamuɣři nsen, ẓrin belli Imiṣriyyen ḍfaren ten-dd uca nitni ggʷeden aṭṭas. \add Xenni\add* sɣuyen ayt n Israil ɣar SIDI.  
\v 11 Nnan i Musa: “Ma war ǧin \add ɛad\add* imeḍřan di Miṣra ař d aneɣ dd-tawyed, maḥend ad nemmet di řexřa-ya? Maɣar teggid ammu, tessuffɣed aneɣ-dd zi Miṣra?  
\v 12 Ma war kidek nessiweř marra awařen-a di Miṣra, nenna: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad nexdem i Imiṣriyyen’? Xar mařa \add tuɣa neqqim\add* nexdem i Imiṣriyyen x mařa nemmut di řexřa.” \x ◘ \xo 14:12 \xt Uf. 6:9\x*  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa i řgens: “War tteggʷedem, beddem, texzarem asenjem n SIDI i d awem ɣa yewc ass-a, minzi Imiṣriyyen nni tᵉttwařam ass-a, ɛemmarṣ ad ten tẓarem ɛad i řebda.  
\v 14 SIDI ad xawem immneɣ uca kenniw ad tseɣdem \add waha\add*.”   
\m
\v 15 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Mayemmi ɣari tᵉttřaɣid? Ini i ayt n Israil \add ḥima\add* ad fesyen iqiḍan nsen.  
\v 16 Sgeɛɛed taɣɣarct nnec, swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec x řebḥar uca farq i-t, ḥima ad iẓwa ayt n Israil x řbarr di řwesṭ n řebḥar.  
\v 17 Xzar, Necc ad ssqesḥeɣ uř n Imiṣriyyen, maḥend ad ten aredfen \add di řebḥar\add* u Necc ad ssɛuǧiɣ Ixef inu s firɛun u s marra řɛeskar nnes, ikarruten nnes d imnayen nnes \add n iysan\add*.  
\v 18 Ad ssnen Imiṣriyyen belli Necc d SIDI, xmi ɣa ttwassɛuǧiɣ s firɛun, s ikarruten nnes d imnayen nnes \add n iysan\add*.”   
\m
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* immuṭṭi lmalak n AREBBI nni yuyuren zzat i řɛeskar n Israil uca idweř ɣar ḍeffar \add nsen\add*: aqellij n useynu immuṭṭi zi zzat i wudem nsen uca ibedd ɣar ḍeffar nsen.  
\v 20 Yudef \add uqellij\add* jar řɛeskar n Imiṣriyyen d řɛeskar n Israil. Tuɣa aseynu d taǧest \add ɣar uɣezdis-a\add* u issiɣ \add i uɣezdis nneɣni\add* s ǧiřet u war dd-iqarreb ijjen ɣar wenneɣni ǧiřet tekmeř.  
\v 21 Uca isswiẓẓeḍ Musa afus nnes x řebḥar uca iɛarn SIDI xenni řebḥar ɣar uɣezdis s yijj n usemmiḍ d acarqi ijhed, marra ǧiřet \add nni\add*, uca yarra řebḥar ad ijeffef. \add Ammu\add* i ttwammsebḍan waman. \x ◘ \xo 14:21 \xt Yac. 4:23; Izhd. 78:13; 106:9; 114:3\x*  
\v 22 Uyuren ayt n Israil x min yuẓɣen di řwesṭ n řebḥar uca aman ggin amecnaw řḥiḍ x yefus nsen d uzeřmaḍ nsen. \x ◘ \xo 14:22 \xt 1 Kur. 10:1; Ɛbr. 11:29\x*  
\v 23 Aredfen ten Imiṣriyyen, ruḥen awarni asen di řwesṭ n řebḥar s marra iysan n firɛun d ikarruten nnes d imnayen nnes \add n yiysan\add*.  
\v 24 Řami d yeffu řḥař, imsar belli SIDI iṣweḍ ɣar řɛeskar n Imiṣriyyen zeg uqellij n tmessi d iseynuten uca issxarweḍ řɛeskar n Miṣra.  
\v 25 Ijja tijarrarin n ikarruten nsen ad fesxent, ařami idweř iwɛar xasen ad uyuren ɣar zzat. \add Řexdenni\add* nnan Imiṣriyyen, \add kuř ijjen zzaysen i yixef nnes\add*: “Ittxeṣṣa ayi ad arewřeɣ zi zzat n tiṭṭawin n Israil, minzi SIDI immneɣ di ṭṭweɛ nsen ḍidd i Imiṣriyyen.”  
\v 26 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec x řebḥar, ḥima ad dewřen waman x Imiṣriyyen, x ikarruten nsen u x imnayen nsen \add n iysan\add*.”  
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* isswiẓẓeḍ Musa afus nnes x řebḥar u ɣar řefjar n ṣṣbeḥ idweř řebḥar ɣar mani t tuɣa qbeř uca arewřen Imiṣriyyen nican ḍidd nnes uca iɣḍeř SIDI Imiṣriyyen di řwesṭ n řebḥar.  
\v 28 Dewřen-dd waman uca ttwaneḍřen ikarruten d imnayen \add n iysan\add* n marra řɛeskar n firɛun i tuɣa yudef awarni asen ɣar řebḥar. War zzaysen iqqim uřa d ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 14:28 \xt Izhd. 78:53; 106:11\x*  
\v 29 \add Maca\add* ayt n Israil uyuren x min yuẓɣen di řwesṭ n řebḥar u aman tuɣa ggin amecnaw řḥiḍ ɣar yefus nsen d uzeřmaḍ nsen. \x ◘ \xo 14:29 \xt Izhd. 77:20\x*  
\v 30 \add Ammu\add* i issenjem SIDI Israil deg wass nni zeg ufus n Imiṣriyyen uca Israil iẓra Imiṣriyyen i immuten x tma n řebḥar.  
\v 31 Iẓra Israil afus imɣaren i igga SIDI deg Imiṣriyyen uca iggʷed řgens zi SIDI, uca umnen nitni di SIDI u di Musa, amsexxar nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Izři n uɣelleb n Musa  
\m
\v 1 Řexdenni izehhed Musa jmiɛ ak-d ayt n Israil zhid-a i SIDI, nnan:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ad zehhdeɣ i SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi Netta yuɛřa di řuɛřa!\qt*  
\m \qt Ayis d wenni xas yenyin\qt*  
\m \qt inḍar i-ten di řebḥar.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt Izhd. 106:12; Asa. 15:3\x*   
\m
\v 2 \qt SIDi d jjehd inu d azehhed inu.\qt*  
\m \qt Netta idweř d asenjem inu.\qt*  
\m \qt Wa d Arebbi inu,\qt*  
\m \qt necc ad t ssemɣareɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt Netta d AREBBI n baba,\qt*  
\m \qt necc ad t ssɛuǧeɣ!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Izhd. 18:2; Izhd. 118:14; Ica. 12:2\x*   
\m
\v 3 \qt SIDI d aryaz n umenɣi,\qt*  
\m \qt SIDI d Isem nnes!\qt*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Ikarruten n firɛun d řɛeskar nnes\qt*  
\m \qt inḍar i-ten di řebḥar\qt*  
\m \qt u acewwar n ineɣrafen nnes \+tl n řɛeskar\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ɣarqen di Řebḥar n Telga.\qt*   
\m
\v 5 \qt \+tl Aman\+tl* ihewřen dřin i-ten.\qt*  
\m \qt Amecnaw aẓru, hwan ɣar řaǧaɣ.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:5 \xt Naḥ. 9:11\x*   
\m
\v 6 \qt \+tl A\+tl* SIDI, afus afusi nnec\qt*  
\m \qt ittwaɛezz s jjehd,\qt*  
\m \qt afus afusi nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a\+tl* SIDI, aqa iřbez řeɛdu.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:6 \xt Izhd. 118:15, 16\x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt S řemɣaret n uɛuǧi nnec tᵉteḥḥid\qt*  
\m \qt inni kik ittemɛařan.\qt*  
\m \qt Mařa tessekked řḥaduq \+tl n weɣḍab\+tl* nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt ad ten yecc wanita amecnaw iɣeǧ.\qt*   
\m
\v 8 \qt S usuḍi n wenzaren nnec\qt*  
\m \qt ɛurrcen waman,\qt*  
\m \qt ttwassbedden tseǧya am weɣbar,\qt*  
\m \qt aman ihewřen jemden\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ n řebḥar.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:8 \xt Ica. 63:12, 13; Ḥab. 3:10\x*   
\m
\v 9 \qt Inna řeɛdu: ‘Ad ten aredfeɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt ad \+tl ten\+tl* ɛduɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt ad bḍiɣ řmur,\qt*  
\m \qt řeɛmar inu ad zzaysen ijjiwen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad dd-jebdeɣ ssif inu,\qt*  
\m \qt afus inu ad zzaysen ikkes řwart nsen.’\qt*   
\m
\v 10 \qt Tsuḍed s nnefs nnec\qt*  
\m \qt uca ideř i-ten řebḥar.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni hwan-dd am řexfif\qt*  
\m \qt deg waman imɣaren.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt Izhd. 74:13; 106:11\x*   
\m
\v 11 \qt \+tl A\+tl* SIDI, man wen i iǧan\qt*  
\m \qt am Cek jar irebbiten?\qt*  
\m \qt Wi iǧan am Cek,\qt*  
\m \qt d wenni ittwassɛuǧen di tqeddast,\qt*  
\m \qt amweqqar deg izřan n uṣebbeḥ,\qt*  
\m \qt man wen itteggen řeɛjayeb \+tl am Cek\+tl*?\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Tesswiẓẓḍed afus afusi nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt tsarḍ i-ten temmurt.\qt*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Cek tgewwded řgens-a\qt*  
\m \qt s tmexsiwt nnec icuwwaren,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa tefdid \+tl t\+tl*\qt*,  
\m \qt s jjehd nnec tnedhed \+tl ten\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar Tzeddiɣt Iqeddsen nnec.\qt*   
\m
\v 14 \qt Řegnus sřin \+tl x uya\+tl* uca arjijen.\qt*  
\m \qt Teṭṭef teggʷudi deg imezdaɣ n Filicit.\qt*   
\m
\v 15 \qt Řexdenni imeqqranen n tqebbař\qt*  
\m \qt n Idum ttbehten,\qt*  
\m \qt inni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa di Mu’ab\qt*  
\m \qt ttarjijen,\qt*  
\m \qt u marra imezdaɣ n Kenɛan aqa fesyen!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:15 \xt Aɛwd. 2:4\x*   
\m
\v 16 \qt Tewḍa xasen řɛurret d tiggʷudi.\qt*  
\m \qt S řemɣaret n uɣiř nnec\qt*  
\m \qt seɣden am weẓru,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami iẓwa řgens nnec, \+tl a\+tl* SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt ařami iẓwa řgens-a\qt*  
\m \qt i tkesbed i Yixef nnec.\qt*\x ◘ \xo 15:16 \xt Aɛwd. 2:25; 11:25; Yac. 2:9\x*   
\m
\v 17 \qt Cek ad ten tnedhed\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ten teẓẓud\qt*  
\m \qt x wedrar n řwart nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt amcan i teggid d Tazeddiɣt nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a\+tl* SIDI, Zzawect Iqeddsen\qt*  
\m \qt i iggin ifassen nnec, \+tl a\+tl* Sidi inu.\qt*   
\m
\v 18 \qt SIDI ad iḥkem i řebda qaɛ!\qt*   
\m
\v 19 \qt Minzi ayis n firɛun yudef ɣar řebḥar\qt*  
\m \qt s ikarruten nnes d imnayen nnes\qt*  
\m \qt uca iqřeb xasen SIDI ɛawed\qt*  
\m \qt aman n řebḥar.\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl Maca\+tl* ayt n Israil ẓwan x řaẓaɣ\qt*  
\m \qt di řwesṭ n řebḥar.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 U Maryam, tanabit, učmas n Harun, teksi aǧun deg ufus nnes u marra timeṭṭa ffɣent awarni as s ibendiren d ccḍiḥ \add s nnubtat\add*. \x ◘ \xo 15:20 \xt 1 Ṣm. 18:6\x*  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* tarra-dd xasen Maryam snnubet nnes: “Ɣennjem i SIDI, minzi aqa Netta yuɛřan aṭṭas! Inḍar ayis ak-d wenni xas yenyin di řebḥar.”   
\b  
\m
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* ijja Musa \add řgens n\add* Israil ad ifsi iqiḍan nsen, inni iǧan x tma n Řebḥar n Telga, uca ruḥen di řexřa n Cur, uyuren třata n wussan di řexřa břa ad afen aman.  
\v 23 Uca iwḍen ɣar \bd Mara\bd*, \add maca\add* war zemmaren ad swen aman n Mara, minzi tuɣa aten d imerzagen. X uya ggin as i wemcan nni ‘Mara’. \x ◘ \xo 15:23 \xt Řxř. 33:8\x*  
\v 24 Innedqem řgens x Musa, inna: “Min ɣa nsu?” \f ◼ \fr 15:24 \ft \+fk Innedqem\ft  - niɣ ‘iɛekkes’.\f*  
\v 25 Netta iřaɣa i SIDI uca SIDI immeř as ijj n ukeccuḍ uca inḍar i-t daxeř deg waman uca dewřen waman d imiẓiden. Din i d as igga \add i řgens\add* ict n tewṣeyyet d ict n lfariḍa u dinni i-ten iqeǧeb.  
\v 26 Inna: “Mařa tesřid mliḥ i wawař n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, teggid min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin nnes, ad tesřed i řumarat nnes, ad teḥḍid marra tiweṣṣa nnes, \add xenni\add* Necc war d awem-dd ssekkiɣ řehřac i dd-ssekkeɣ x Miṣra, minzi Necc d SIDI, Amesgenfi nnec!”  
\v 27 \add Řexdenni\add* iwḍen ɣar \bd Ilim\bd*, mani tuɣa tenɛac n řɛunṣarat n waman, d sebɛin n tcejjura n tini uca wtin iqiḍan nsen dinni zzat i waman.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Aɣrum zeg ujenna  
\m
\v 1 Uca fesyen iqiḍan nsen, \add uyuren\add* zi Ilim, u marra tamesmunt n ayt n Israil tiweḍ ɣar řexřa n Sin i iǧan jar Ilim d Sina. Tuɣa \add man aya\add* deg wass xemmesṭac n uyur wiss tnayen awarni řami dd-ffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 16:1 \xt Řxř. 33:5-49\x*  
\v 2 Marra tamesmunt n ayt n Israil tennedqem zi Musa d Harun di řexřa.  
\v 3 Nnan asen ayt n Israil: “Mři nemmut s ufus n SIDI di temmurt n Miṣra umi tuɣa neqqim ɣar ṭṭbaṣi n weysum, necca aɣrum ařami nejjiwen! Minzi kenniw tessuffɣem aneɣ-dd ɣar řexřa-ya maḥend ad tenɣem marra agraw aya s řaẓ.” \x ◘ \xo 16:3 \xt Řxř. 11:4; 1 Kur. 10:10\x*  
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Xzar, ad jjeɣ aɣrum ad xawem dd-iwḍa zeg ujenna am wenẓar. \add Xenni\add* ad iffeɣ řgens, ad ksin min ḥdajen i wass deg wass nni, ḥima ad ten qeǧbeɣ, ma gguren di \add tɣuri n\add* Ccariɛa inu, niɣ lla. \x ◘ \xo 16:4 \xt Izhd. 78:24; 105:40\x*  
\v 5 Ad yiři deg wass wiss setta, ad sswejden min dd-iwyen ɣar daxeř. Man aya ad yiři d tnayen n tseqqar x min ɣa ssmunen kuř ass.”   
\m
\v 6 \add Řexdenni\add* inna Musa d Harun i marra ayt n Israil: “Ɣar uɛecci ad tessnem belli SIDI i kenniw dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra,  
\v 7 u ɣar ṣṣbeḥ ad tẓarem aɛuǧi n SIDI, minzi aqa Netta isřa anedqem nwem x SIDI. Ma neccin, \add min neɛna\add*, ḥima kenniw ad xaneɣ tenndeqmem?” \f ◼ \fr 16:7 \ft \+fk anedqem\ft  - niɣ ‘řeɛkaset’.\f*  
\v 8 Inna Musa: “Řami d awem iwca SIDI aysum i macca deg uɛecci u aɣrum di tyawant di ṣṣbeḥ, aqa isřa SIDI anedqem nwem i zi xas tᵉttnedqamem. I neccin, \add min neɛna\add*? Kenniw war xaneɣ tᵉttnedqamem, maca x SIDI.”  
\v 9 Inna Musa i Harun: “Ini i tmesmunt n ayt n Israil marra: ‘Reḥḥgem-dd ɣar zzat i wudem n SIDI, minzi aqa isřa i unedqem nwem.’”  
\v 10 \add Am\add* issiweř Harun ak-d tmesmunt n ayt n Israil marra, tuɣa xezzaren ɣar řexřa uca xzar, aɛuǧi n SIDI iḍhar-dd deg useynu. \x ◘ \xo 16:10 \xt Uf. 13:21\x*   
\m
\v 11 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 12 “Necc sřiɣ i unedqem n ayt n Israil. Siweř akidsen uca ini: Jar beddu n wezyen n wass ař dd-tewḍa tmeddit ad teccem \bd aysum\bd*, ɣar ṣṣbeḥ ad tejjiwnem s \bd weɣrum\bd* uca ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 16:12 \xt Yḥ. 6:49,58\x*   
\m
\v 13 Ɣar uɛecci uřyent i-dd ijḍaḍ qqaren as ‘tsalwa’ uca dřint řmargeḥ n řɛeskar u ɣar ṣṣbeḥ tuɣa nnda inneḍ-dd i řmargeḥ. \x ◘ \xo 16:13 \xt Řxř. 11:31; Izhd. 105:40\x*  
\v 14 Řami dd-igeɛɛed nnda, aqa da, ict n řḥajjet d tazdat am teqcurt, d tazdat am nnda igarsen, \add tᵉttwaf\add* x wudem n řexřa, x temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 16:14 \xt Řxř. 11:7; Naḥ. 9:15; Izhd. 78:24; 105:40\x*  
\v 15 Ẓrin tt ayt n Israil, nnan ijjen i wenneɣni: “Manawya?”, minzi war ssinen min iɛna. \add Řexdenni\add* inna asen Musa: “Wa d aɣrum nni d awem iwca SIDI, ḥima ad teccem. \x ◘ \xo 16:15 \xt Yḥ. 6:31; 1 Kur. 10:3\x*  
\v 16 Wa d awař i \add d awem\add* yumur SIDI: ‘Ejj ad zzayes iksi kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab min iḥdaj, \add řeqyas n\add* ijj n uɛumir, \add ɛřaḥař tnayen litru\add*, i \add ijjen\add* bnadem. \add Kuř\add* aryaz ad iksi ɛlaḥsab řqedd n iwdan i ɣares deg uqiḍun.’” \f ◼ \fr 16:16 \ft \+fk aɛumir\ft  - (řeqyas n) yijj n ‘uɛumir’ d taɛeccart n yijj n ‘ifa’. Xzar Uf. 16:36\f*  
\v 17 Uca ammu i ggin ayt n Israil. Yrun \add zzayes\add*, \add ijjen\add* aṭṭas, \add wenneɣni\add* drus.  
\v 18 Weznen aya s \add řeqyas n\add* uɛumir. Wenni yrun aṭṭas war ɣares zzyada d wenni yrun drus, war d as ittxeṣṣi ɛad. Kuř ijj iyru macca nnes ɛlaḥsab min iḥdaj. \x ◘ \xo 16:18 \xt 2 Kur. 8:15\x*  
\v 19 Inna asen Musa: “Uřa d ijj ad zzayes yejj ař ṣṣbeḥ.”  
\v 20 \add Maca\add* nitni war sřin ca i Musa u ca n yeryazen xemmřen \add ca\add* zzayes ař ṣṣbeḥ. \add Xenni\add* udfen dayes ikeccawen uca ibda ad igg ccum. Uca iffugem xasen Musa aṭṭas.   
\m
\v 21 Kuř ṣṣbeḥ yrun t, kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab izemmar ad icc netta, minzi mařa teḥma tfuct, tuɣa ittfessi.   
\m
\v 22 Deg wass wiss setta yrun tnayen n tseqqar n weɣrum, \add řeqyas n\add* tnayen n iɛumiren i kuř azeǧif. Uca usin-dd marra řḥukkam n tmesmunt uca xebbaren Musa.  
\v 23 Netta inna asen: “D man aya min xef issiweř SIDI: ‘Tiwecca d ijj n \add wass n\add* arraḥet, ijj \add n wass\add* n ssebt d amqeddas i SIDI. Sengʷem min texsem ad tᵉssengʷem, snennam min texsem ad tᵉssennam uca marra min ɣa iqqimen, xemmřem t ař ṣṣbeḥ.’”  
\v 24 Nitni xemmřen t ař ṣṣbeḥ am mammec ten yumur Musa uca war yarṣuḍ u war dayes tuɣi tkecca.  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa: “Ccem aya ass-a, minzi ass-a d ass n ssebt n SIDI. Ass-a war t tᵉttifem deg iyyar.  
\v 26 Setta n wussan ad teyrum, maca deg wass wiss sebɛa aqa d ssebt, war ittiři walu.”   
\m
\v 27 Deg wass wiss sebɛa imsar belli ffɣen ca zi řgens, maḥend ad yrun \add ca\add*, maca war ufin walu.  
\v 28 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Ař meřmi tugim ad teḥḍam řumurat inu d izerfan inu?  
\v 29 Xzarem, minzi SIDI iwca awem \add ass n\add* ssebt, x uya iwca awem deg wass wiss setta aɣrum i tnayen n wussan. Kuř ijj zzaywem ad iqqim deg wemcan nnes! Deg wass wiss sebɛa war dd-itteffiɣ uřa d ijj zeg wemcan nnes!”  
\v 30 Uca yareyyeḥ řgens deg wass n ssebt.   
\m
\v 31 Taddart n Israil třaɣa as ‘manna’. Tuɣa-tt d tacemřařt am zzariɛet n řqeṣbur uca aředdi nnes amecnaw tifḍirin n tamment. \x ◘ \xo 16:31 \xt Řxř. 11:7\x*  
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa: “Ddegga d awař i zi yumur SIDI: ‘Ccurem zzayes \add řeqyas n\add* yijj n uɛumir uca xemmeř i-t i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem \add i dd ɣa yasen\add*, ḥima ad ẓaren aɣrum min zi kenniw ssecceɣ di řexřa, umi kenniw ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra.”  
\v 33 Inna Musa i Harun: “Ksi ijj n uzenbiř uca ɛemmar i-t s yijj n uɛumir n ‘manna’ uca egg i-t zzat i wudem n SIDI, ḥima ad ittwaxemmeř i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 16:33 \xt Ɛbr. 9:4\x*  
\v 34 Uca igga i-tt Harun zzat i Cchadet, ḥima ad tᵉttwaxemmeř am mammec d as yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 35 Ammu i ccin ayt n Israil ‘manna’ arebɛin n iseggʷusa, ařami iwḍen ɣar temmurt mani ɣa raḥen ad zedɣen. Ccin manna ařami iwḍen ɣar weymir n temmurt n Kenɛan. \x ◘ \xo 16:35 \xt Yac. 5:12; Naḥ. 9:15\x*  
\v 36 Ijj n uɛumir d ɛecra di tesɣart n ijj n ifa. \f ◼ \fr 16:36 \ft \+fk ijj n uɛumir\ft  - xzar Ufuɣ 16:16. \fk ijj n ifa\ft  - ɛřayen 22 litru. Aqa-t d ijj n řeqyas n imendi d irden. Abatu uřa d ijj n řeqyas n 22 litru maca i waman d binu d zzect. Aqa din inni qqaren belli ijj n ifa ktar zi 22 litru, ad taɣ 35 litru niɣ ktar. Ijj n ifa d ɛecra di tesɣart n yijj n uhumir uca ahumir dayes 220 litru.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 17
\s1 Massa d Mariba  
\m
\v 1 Uca fesyen marra tamesmunt n ayt n Israil iqiḍan nsen, \add uyuren\add* zi řexřa n Sin, am mammec d asen yumur SIDI uca wtin iqiḍan nsen di Rafidim. War din tuɣi aman, ḥima ad issu řgens.  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* imcubbec řgens ak-d Musa, nitni nnan: “Ewc aneɣ aman, ḥima ad nsu!” Musa inna asen: “Mayemmi tᵉttexsem ad kidi temcubbucem? Mayemmi tᵉttqeǧabem SIDI?” \x ◘ \xo 17:2 \xt Řxř. 20:3, 4\x*  
\v 3 Tuɣa řgens iffud aṭṭas ɣar waman uca nndeqmen zi Musa, nnan: “Maɣar d aneɣ tessgeɛɛded zi Miṣra? Ma ḥima ad ayi thellked s ufadi uřa d tarwa inu d řebhayem inu?”  
\v 4 \add Řexdenni\add* isɣuy Musa ɣar SIDI, inna: “Min ɣa ggeɣ ak-d řgens-a? Mɣir cwayt uca ad ayi arejmen.”  
\v 5 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Ekk zzat i řgens uca ksi akidek ca zeg imɣaren n Israil uca ksi ɛawed deg ufus nnec taɣɣarct nni zi tewtid iɣzar uca ruḥ. \x ◘ \xo 17:5 \xt Uf. 7:20\x*  
\v 6 Xzar, Necc ad beddeɣ din zzatek x teṣḍart ɣar Ḥurib, ad tewted taṣḍart, ad zzayes dd-ffɣen waman uca ad issu řgens.” Igga Musa amenni zzat i tiṭṭawin n imɣaren n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Řxř. 20:9; Izhd. 78:15; 114:8; 1 Kur. 10:4\x*  
\v 7 Uca iřaɣa isem n wemcan nni Massa d Mariba, minzi ayt n Israil mmcubbcen \add din\add* u minzi nitni qeǧben SIDI, nnan: “Ma SIDI aqa-t řexxu di řwesṭ nneɣ niɣ lla?”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Amenɣi ak-d Amalik  
\m
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd Ɛamaliq uca immneɣ ak-d Israil di Rafidim. \x ◘ \xo 17:8 \xt Aɛwd. 25:17, 18\x*  
\v 9 Inna Musa i Yacuwa: “Ejj aneɣ ad nixḍar iryazen uca ad neffeɣ, maḥend ad nemmneɣ ak-d Ɛamaliq. Tiwecca ad beddeɣ sennej x tqiccat n tewrirt uca taɣɣarct n AREBBI ad tiři deg ufus inu.”  
\v 10 Igga Yacuwa am mammec d as inna Musa, immneɣ ak-d Ɛamaliq, maca Musa d Harun d Ḥur uřyen ɣar tqiccat n tewrirt.  
\v 11 Uca imsar řami issgeɛɛed Musa afus nnes, \add řexdenni\add* tuɣa Israil tɣeǧeb, maca xmi ittejja afus nnes ad ihwa, \add řexdenni\add* ɣeǧben \add ayt n\add* Ɛamaliq.  
\v 12 Ifassen n Musa dewřen ddeqřen. \add Xenni\add* ksin ijj n weẓru uca ggin t sadu Musa uca iqqim xas uca Harun d Ḥur sennden ifassen nnes, ijj zeg uɣezdis-a, wenneɣni zeg \add uɣezdis\add* nneɣni. Ammu i iqqimen ifassen nnes geɛɛden ařami teɣři tfuct.  
\v 13 Uca iɣřeb Yacuwa x Ɛamaliq d řgens nnes s řeqḍeɛ n ssif. \f ◼ \fr 17:13 \ft \+fk s řeqḍeɛ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s uqemmum’.\f*  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Musa: “Ari aya deg ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen i řidaret \add dayes\add* uca egg i-t deg imejjan n Yacuwa, belli aqa Necc ad mḥiɣ qaɛ řidaret di Ɛamaliq sadu ujenna.” \x ◘ \xo 17:14 \xt Řxř. 24:20; Aɛwd. 25:17, 18, 19; 1 Ṣm. 15:2, 3\x*  
\v 15 Ibna Musa ijj n uɛalṭar uca iřaɣa as s yisem: “SIDI d taɛeǧant inu!”  
\v 16 Uca inna: “Afus tuɣa x řɛarc n SIDi. SIDI ad yegg garra x Ɛamaliq zi jjiř ař jjiř.” \x ◘ \xo 17:16 \xt 1 Ṣm. 15:2\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 18
\s1 Arzef n Yitrun  
\m
\v 1 Isřa Yitrun, akehhan n Midyan, aḍeggʷař n Musa, marra min igga AREBBI ak-d Musa u ak-d řgens nnes Israil, aqa issuffeɣ-dd SIDI Israil zi Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 18:1 \xt Uf. 2:16; 3:1\x*  
\v 2 Iṭṭef Yitrun, aḍeggʷař n Musa, Ṣaffura, tamɣart n Musa, awarni řami d as iwca tirzifin nnes n tesřit,  
\v 3 uřa d tnayen n iḥenjiren nnes, ijjen qqaren as Jarcum, minzi tuɣa inna: “Tuɣa ayi d abarrani di temmurt d tabarranect!”, \x ◘ \xo 18:3 \xt Uf. 2:22\x*  
\v 4 u wenneɣni qqaren as Aliɛazir, \add minzi tuɣa inna:\add* “AREBBI n baba iɛawen ayi uca ifekk ayi zi ssif n firɛun.”  
\v 5 Yitrun aḍeggʷař n Musa, ak-d iḥenjiren nnes d tmeṭṭut nnes, iwḍen ɣar Musa di řexřa, ɣar mani iwta iqiḍan, ɣar wedrar n AREBBI.  
\v 6 Uca netta ijja ad inin i Musa: “Necc, aḍeggʷař nnec Yitrun, usiɣ-dd ɣarek s temɣart nnec d tnayen n iḥenjiren nnes akides.”  
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ Musa ad iřqa aḍeggʷař nnes, ibendeq uca issudem i-t. Ijjen isseqsa wenneɣni x umeddur nnes uca udfen ɣar uqiḍun.  
\v 8 Musa iḥaja i uḍeggʷař nnes marra min igga SIDI ak-d firɛun u ak-d Imiṣriyyen di ṭṭweɛ n Israil u x marra tamara nni xasen ikkin deg webrid d mammec ten ifekk SIDI.  
\v 9 Ifarḥ Yitrun zi marra řxir nni igga SIDI i Israil, umi t ifekk zeg ufus n Imiṣriyyen.  
\v 10 Inna Yitrun: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI d wenni kenniw ifekken zeg ufus n Imiṣriyyen u zeg ufus n firɛun, d wenni ifekken řgens zeg ufus n Imiṣriyyen!  
\v 11 Řexxu ssneɣ belli SIDI imɣar aṭṭas x marra irebbiten, aqa di tmesřact nni dessaren xasen.” \x ◘ \xo 18:11 \xt Uf. 1:10, 16, 22; 5:7; 14:18\x*  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* iksi Yitrun, aḍeggʷař n Musa, taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tiɣarṣa i AREBBI uca yusa-dd Harun jmiɛ ak-d marra imɣaren n ayt n Israil, maḥend ad yecc aɣrum \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d uḍeggʷař n Musa zzat i wudem n AREBBI.   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Tiwecca nnes tuɣa Musa ittɣima \add x řkursi\add*, maḥend ad iḥkem řgens. Tuɣa řgens ibedd zzat i Musa zi ṣṣbeḥ \add zic\add* ař ǧiřet.  
\v 14 Iẓra uḍeggʷař n Musa marra min tuɣa ittegg \add Musa\add* i řgens, inna: “Manawaya i teggid cek i řgens? Mayemmi tᵉttɣimid cek weḥḥdek u marra řgens ibedd zzatek zi ṣṣbeḥ \add zic\add* ař ǧiřet?”  
\v 15 Yarra-dd Musa x uḍeggʷař nnes: “Minzi řgens ittas-dd ɣari ḥima ad ittar \add ccwar\add* n AREBBI.  
\v 16 X minni ɣarsen tᵉttiři ca n tmesřact, ttasen-dd ɣari \add s man aya\add* uca necc ad carrɛeɣ jar ijj d wenneɣni, ssecaneɣ asen tiweṣṣa d izerfan n AREBBI.”  
\v 17 \add Řexdenni\add* inna as uḍeggʷař n Musa: “Min teggid war iǧi ca mliḥ.  
\v 18 Ammu i ɣa taḥřed aṭṭas, cek d řgens-a i kik iǧan, minzi man aya idqeř xak aṭṭas, war d as tzemmared ad t tegged weḥḥdek.  
\v 19 Seř řexxu i wawař inu, necc ad cek neṣḥeɣ uca AREBBI ad kik yiři. Iři cek d aweṣṣay x řgens zzat i AREBBI uca qeddem ddɛawi zzat i AREBBI.  
\v 20 Scen asen tiweṣṣa d izerfan uca scen asen abrid i ten ittxeṣṣan ad uyuren u řxedmet i d asen ittxeṣṣan ad tt ggen.  
\v 21 Ɛawed xzar cek, ad tarzud jar marra řgens x iryazen izeɛɛamen, inni itteggʷeden AREBBI, iryazen iṣdiqen, inni icarrhen tarezzut x arbeḥ. Egg i-ten d imeqqranen x wařef, d imeqqranen x mya, d imeqqranen x xemsin d imeqqranen x ɛecra.  
\v 22 Ejj i-ten ad carrɛen jar řgens řebda. Ejj i-ten ad qeddmen marra ddɛawi iwɛaren zzatek, \add maca\add* marra ddɛawi timeẓyanin ad xasent carrɛen s yixef nsen. Egg i-t tefsus x yixef nnec uca ejj i-ten ad tt arbun akidek.  
\v 23 Mařa teggid aya, u AREBBI i cek yumuren, tzemmared ad teqqimed tbedded uca marra řgens aya ad yaweḍ ɛawed di řehna ɣar wemcan i d asen ittwagg.”   
\m
\v 24 Isřa Musa ɣar wawař n uḍeggʷař nnes, igga marra min \add d as\add* inna. \x ◘ \xo 18:24 \xt Aɛwd. 1:9\x*  
\v 25 Ixḍar Musa iryazen izeɛɛamen zi marra Israil uca igga i-ten d izeǧifen x řgens: imeqqranen x wařef, imeqqranen x mya, imeqqranen x xemsin d imeqqranen x ɛecra.  
\v 26 Uca nitni tuɣa ttcarrɛen řgens řebda uca ddɛawi iwɛaren qedmen tent ɣar Musa, \add maca\add* marra ddɛawi timeẓyanin carrɛen tent s yixef nsen.  
\v 27 Iqebbeḍ Musa aḍeggʷař nnes uca iɛqeb netta ɣar temmurt nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 19
\s1 SIDI x wedrar n Sina  
\m
\v 1 Deg uyur wiss třata awarni i wuffuɣ n ayt n Israil zi temmurt n Miṣra, deg wass nni nnit, iwḍen-dd ɣar řexřa n Sina.  
\v 2 Aqa fesyen iqiḍan nsen, \add uyuren\add* zi Rafidim uca iwḍen ɣar řexřa n Sina uca wtin iqiḍan nsen di řexřa. Iwta Israil iqiḍan nnes qibač i wedrar.  
\v 3 Yuři Musa ɣar AREBBI uca iřaɣa as-dd SIDI zeg wedrar, inna as: “Ammu i ɣa tessiwřed ak-d taddart n Yaɛqub u \add ammu i\add* ɣa tinid i ayt n Israil: \x ◘ \xo 19:3 \xt Řex. 7:38\x*  
\v 4 ‘Kenniw teẓrim min ggiɣ ak-d Imiṣriyyen u \add mammec\add* kenniw ksiɣ x wafriwen n ugider uca iwyeɣ-dd kenniw ɣari. \f ◼ \fr 19:4 \ft \+fk agider\ft  - niɣ ‘asiwan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 19:4 \xt Aɛwd. 29:1; 32:11\x*  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, mařa tesřim mliḥ ɣar wawař inu u ad teḥḍam Řɛahd inu, ad ɣari tiřim kenniw tiɣřam x marra řegnus, minzi marra tammurt aqa-tt inu. \x ◘ \xo 19:5 \xt Aɛwd. 7:6; 10:14, 15; 14:2; 26:18; Izhd. 135:4; Ica. 41:8; Tit. 2:14\x*  
\v 6 Kenniw ad ayi tiřim d ict n tgeldit n ikehhanen d ijj n řgens amqeddas.’ Ina d awařen nni d ac ittxeṣṣan ad ten tinid i ayt n Israil.” \x ◘ \xo 19:6 \xt 1 Bṭ. 2:9\x*   
\m
\v 7 Ihwa-dd Musa uca iřaɣa-dd x imɣaren n řgens uca ibarreḥ asen marra awařen-a i d as yumur SIDI.  
\v 8 Uca yarra-dd marra řgens, nnan: “Marra min issiweř SIDI, ad t negg!” Uca issiweḍ Musa awařen n řgens ɛawed i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 19:8 \xt Uf. 24:3\x*   
\m
\v 9 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Xzar, Necc ad ɣarek dd-aseɣ deg ijj n useynu d abarcan, ḥima ad iseř řgens xmi Necc kik ɣa ssiwřeɣ uca ɛawed ad zzayek amnen i řebda.” \add Minzi\add* Musa ixebbar awařen n SIDI i řgens.  
\v 10 SIDI inna i Musa: “Ruḥ ɣar řgens uca sqeddes i-ten ass-a d tiwecca, ejj i-ten ad ssirden arruḍ nsen  
\v 11 uca ad iřin wejden i wass wiss třata, minzi deg wass wiss třata ad dd-ihwa SIDI ɣar wedrar n Sina zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra řgens.  
\v 12 Egg iymiren i řgens deg wenneḍ n wedrar, ini: ‘Ɣarwem, war tiřyem ɣar wedrar niɣ ad tḥadam ṭṭarf nnes. Man wen i ɣa iḥadan adrar, ad ittwaneɣ nican. \x ◘ \xo 19:12 \xt Ɛbr. 12:18\x*  
\v 13 War t ittḥidi \add ḥed s\add* ufus, minzi \add xenni\add* ad ittwarjem niɣ ad ittwawwet nican \add s fřitcat\add* min ma iɛna, řebhimet niɣ d bnadem, war ittɣimi iddar. Mařa ad din yiři ijj n usuḍi \add deg uyicc n usřiwřew\add* d azirar, zemmaren nitni ad ařyen adrar.’”   
\m
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ihwa-dd Musa zeg wedrar ɣar řgens, issqeddes řgens uca ssirden arruḍ nsen.  
\v 15 Inna i řgens: “Iřim ttwejdem i wass wiss třata, war dd-ttqarrabem ɣar temɣart.” \x ◘ \xo 19:15 \xt 1 Ṣm. 21:4; 1 Kur. 7:5\x*  
\v 16 Di ṣṣbeḥ n wass wiss třata usin-dd wajjajen d wassamen. Aqa yarsa ijj n useynu iddeqřen x wedrar u řḥess \add n usuḍi\add* deg uyicc n icarri idweř ijhed aṭṭas. Marra řgens di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar yarjij.\x ◘ \xo 19:16 \xt Uf. 20:18; Ɛbr. 12:18; Asa. 4:5\x*  
\v 17 Musa indeh řgens zi řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, maḥend ad iřqa AREBBI uca bedden nitni swadday i wedrar. \x ◘ \xo 19:17 \xt Aɛwd. 4:10, 11\x*  
\v 18 Marra adrar n Sina iddexxen, minzi SIDI tuɣa ihwa-dd xas di tmessi. Ddexxan nnes yuři-dd am ddexxan n ufarran uca marra adrar inhezz aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 19:18 \xt Řqḍ. 5:4; Izhd. 68:9; 114:4; Ḥab. 3:10\x*  
\v 19 Am idweř usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri ijhed \add aṭṭas\add*, issiweř Musa uca yarra-dd xas AREBBI s yijj n řḥess \add ijhed\add*.  
\v 20 Uca ihwa-dd SIDI x wedrar n Sina, x tqiccet n wedrar, uca iřaɣa SIDI i Musa ɣar tqiccet n wedrar. \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed Musa.  
\v 21 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Hwa-dd, ɛřem i řgens, maḥend war ttcuqin di SIDI, maḥend ad t ẓaren uca \add xenni\add* balak ad ttwahellken aṭṭas zzaysen.  
\v 22 Ejj ɛawed ikehhanen, inni i dd ɣa iqarrben ɣar SIDI, ad ssqeddsen ixef nsen, ḥima SIDI war xasen iseɛɛar ca.”  
\v 23 Inna Musa i SIDI: “Řgens war izemmar ad igeɛɛed adrar n Sina, minzi Cek tɛeřmed aneɣ tennid: ‘Egg iymiren x wedrar uca sqeddes i-t.’”  
\v 24 Inna as SIDI: “Ruḥ, hwa! Ad tgeɛɛded cek d Harun akidek, \add maca\add* ikehhanen d řgens war zemmaren ad cuqen, ḥima ad geɛɛden ɣar SIDI, ḥima Netta war xasen iseɛɛar ca.”  
\v 25 \add Řexdenni\add* ihwa-dd Musa ɣar řgens uca inna asen \add marra\add* aya.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 20
\s1 Ɛecra n tweṣṣa  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř AREBBI marra awařen-a, inna:   
\m
\v 2 \bd “Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nnec\bd*, wenni cek dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, zi taddart n tesmuɣi. \x ◘ \xo 20:2 \xt Uf. 13:3; Aɛwd. 5:6; Izhd. 81:11\x*   
\m
\v 3 \bd War ɣarek ttiřin irebbiten nneɣni\bd* zzat i wudem inu.   
\m
\v 4 \bd War ttegg i yixef nnec řexyař ineqcen\bd* niɣ ca n řḥajjet tarwes di min \add iǧan\add* sennej deg ujenna niɣ di ca \add da\add* swadday di temmurt niɣ di ca deg waman \add i iǧan\add* sadu temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 20:4 \xt Lawi 26:1; Izhd. 97:7\x*  
\v 5 War d asen ttbendiq uřa ad xasen tsexxared, minzi Necc, SIDI, AREBBI nnec, d ijj n Arebbi ittasmen, wenni dd-yarezfen řmuɛṣiyyet n ibabaten di tarwa ař \add jjiř\add* wiss třata d wiss arebɛa n yinni d ayi icarrhen,  
\v 6 d wenni isscanen tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren i řuřuf n yinni d ayi ittexsen u ḥeṭṭan řumurat inu.   
\m
\v 7 \bd War neṭṭeq s Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di řbaṭeř\bd*, minzi war ittbarri SIDI i wenni i ɣa ineṭqen s Yisem nnes di řbaṭeř. \x ◘ \xo 20:7 \xt Lawi 9:12; Izhd. 139:20; Mt. 5:33; \x*   
\m
\v 8 \bd Idar ass n ssebt, ḥima ad t tessqeddsed.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 20:8 \xt Ḥiz. 20:12\x*  
\v 9 Setta n wussan i ɣa txedmed, ad tegged marra řxedmet nnec. \x ◘ \xo 20:9 \xt Uf. 23:12; 34:21; Lk. 13:14\x*  
\v 10 Ass wiss sebɛa d wass n ssebt n SIDI, AREBBI nnec. War \add dayes\add* ttegg uřa d ict n řxedmet, cek lla, uřa d mmic lla, d yeǧic lla, d ismeɣ nnec lla, d tayya nnec lla, d řebhimet nnec lla, uřa d abarrani nni akidek iǧan daxeř i tewwura nnec lla.  
\v 11 Minzi di setta n wussan igga SIDI ijenwan d temmurt, řebḥar d marra min dayes uca yareyyeḥ deg wass wiss sebɛa. X uya ibarek SIDI ass n ssebt uca issqeddes i-t. \x ◘ \xo 20:11 \xt Amz. 2:2\x*   
\m
\v 12 \bd Weqqar babac d yemmac\bd*, maḥend ussan \add n tudart\add* nnec \add zemmaren\add* ad zzuggarten di temmurt i d ac ɣa yewc SIDI, AREBBI nnec. \x ◘ \xo 20:12 \xt Mt. 15:4; Afa. 6:2\x*   
\m
\v 13 \bd War neqq.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 20:13 \xt Mt. 5:21\x*   
\m
\v 14 \bd War zenna.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 20:14 \xt Mt. 5:27\x*   
\m
\v 15 \bd War ttacar.\bd*   
\m
\v 16 \bd War cehhed s ẓur\bd* ḍidd i jjar nnec.   
\m
\v 17 \bd War meẓri di ca\bd*, taddart n jjar nnec \add war dayes meẓri\add*. War meẓri di tamɣart n jjar nnec, niɣ deg yismeɣ nnes, niɣ di tayya nnes, niɣ deg ufunas nnes, niɣ deg weɣyuř nnes uřa deg ict n řḥajjet i iǧan n jjar nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 20:17 \xt Rum. 7:7\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 Marra řgens iẓra \add u isřa\add* i wajjajen d wassamen d ddriz n usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri d wedrar idduxxunen. \add Umi\add* iẓra řgens man aya, \add xenni\add* arjijen uca beɛɛden \add nitni\add* ɣar řaggʷaj. \x ◘ \xo 20:18 \xt Uf. 19:16; Asa. 4:5\x*  
\v 19 Nnan i Musa: “Siweř cek akidneɣ uca ad nseř. \add Maca\add* ittxeṣṣa AREBBI war kidneɣ issiwiř, ḥima war nettmetti!” \x ◘ \xo 20:19 \xt Aɛwd. 5:25; Ɛbr. 12:19\x*  
\v 20 Inna Musa i řgens: “War teggʷedem ca, aqa yusa-dd AREBBI, ḥima ad kenniw iqeǧeb u ḥima ad zzayes teggʷedem maḥend war txeṭṭim ca.”  
\v 21 Ibedd řgens zi řaggʷaj, maca Musa iqarreb-dd ɣar useynu ibbumbsen mani \add tuɣa\add* AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 20:21 \xt Uf. 19:17; Ɛbr. 12:18\x*   
\m
\v 22 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Ammu ittxeṣṣa ad tinid i ayt n Israil: ‘Kenniw teẓrim belli ssiwřeɣ-dd akidwem zeg ujenna.  
\v 23 War kidi tteggem irebbiten n nnuqart u war tteggem irebbiten n wureɣ i yixef nwem.  
\v 24 \bd Egg ayi ijj n uɛalṭar s ucař\bd*, qeddem xas tiɣarṣa nnec n wecmaḍ d tiɣarṣa nnec n řehna, uǧi nnec d ifunasen d tfunasin nnec. Di kuř amcan mani ɣa ggeɣ řidaret n Yisem inu, ad ɣarek dd-aseɣ uca ad ac barkeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 20:24 \xt Uf. 27:1; 38:1\x*  
\v 25 Mařa teggid ayi ijj n uɛalṭar n iẓra, war t tbennid s tṣuḍar ittwassuydan, minzi mařa teddzed s uřeyzim nnec, \add iři\add* ad t tessɛiǧted. \x ◘ \xo 20:25 \xt Aɛwd. 27:5; Yac. 8:30, 31\x*  
\v 26 War ttgiɛɛid ɣar uɛalṭar inu s yijj n ddruj, ḥima war ittbin useḍḥi nnec.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Tiweṣṣa zi jjihet jjar nnek  
\m
\v 1 “Tina \add i iǧan\add* d lfarayiḍ nni d asen ɣa tessiwḍed.  
\v 2 Mařa tesɣid ismeɣ d Aɛibrani, \add xenni\add* netta ad ac isexxar setta n iseggʷusa, maca deg \add useggʷas\add* wiss sebɛa ad iffeɣ d aḥurri baṭeř. \x ◘ \xo 21:2 \xt Aɛwd. 15:12; Irm. 34:14\x*  
\v 3 Mařa yudef weḥḥdes, weḥḥdes i ɣa iffeɣ, mařa ɣares tamɣart, ad iffeɣ netta d temɣart nnes.  
\v 4 Mařa sidis iwca as tamɣart uca nettat tejja as-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin, \add xenni\add* tamɣart d tarwa nnes ad iřin n sidis, u xenni netta ad iffeɣ s iman nnes.  
\v 5 \add Maca\add* mařa ismeɣ inna nican: ‘Necc xseɣ sidi inu d temɣart inu d tarwa inu, war xseɣ ad ffɣeɣ d aḥurri!’, \x ◘ \xo 21:5 \xt Aɛwd. 15:16\x*  
\v 6 \add řexdenni\add* sidis ad t issbedd zzat i AREBBI. Ad t yawi ɣar tewwart niɣ ɣar tefřawt \add ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart\add* uca sidis ad as issnuqqeb amejjun nnes s yict n tsineft uca netta ad as isexxar i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 21:6 \xt Aɛwd. 15:17\x*  
\v 7 Mařa izzenz ḥed yeǧis d tayya, war itteffiɣ am muxas tteffɣen isemɣan.  
\v 8 Mařa war teɛjib i tiṭṭawin n sidis u netta tuɣa ixḍeb i-tt, ad tt yejj ad tᵉttwafdi. War izemmar ad tt izzenz i yijj n řgens n barra minzi netta iɣdar zzayes s \add min igga\add*.  
\v 9 Mařa ixḍeb i-tt i mmis, ad kides yegg ɛlaḥsab lfariḍa zi jjhet n yeǧis.  
\v 10 Mařa iksi \add tamɣart\add* nneɣni i yixef nnes, war ineqqeṣ \add řɛuč n\add* weysum nnes, niɣ arruḍ nnes, niɣ řɛacart nnes.  
\v 11 Mařa netta war d as iggi třata-ya, \add xenni\add* nettat ad teffeɣ baṭeř, břa řexraṣ.”   
\b  
\m
\v 12 “Wenni i ɣa iwten ḥed ař ɣa immet, ad t nɣen nican. \x ◘ \xo 21:12 \xt Lawi 24:17\x*  
\v 13 Mařa war t iggi neɛmada, \add maca\add* AREBBI igga as-dd deg ufus nnes, \add řexdenni\add* Necc ad ac ssecneɣ amcan mani izemmar ad yarweř.  
\v 14 \add Maca\add* mařa yuff ḥed x wajjar nnes uca inɣa i-t s řeɣdaret, \add xenni\add* ad t teksid ɣar uɛalṭar inu, maḥend ad t nɣen.   
\m
\v 15 Wenni iwtin babas niɣ yemmas, ad ittwaneɣ nican. \x ◘ \xo 21:15 \xt Mt. 15:4\x*   
\m
\v 16 Wenni yucaren bnadem uca izzenz i-t, niɣ ittwaf \add ɛad\add* ɣares, ad ittwaneɣ nican.   
\m
\v 17 Wenni i ɣa ineɛřen babas niɣ yemmas, ad ittwaneɣ nican. \x ◘ \xo 21:17 \xt Lawi 20:9; Awřn. 20:20; Mt. 15:4; Mk. 7:10\x*   
\m
\v 18 Mařa iryazen mmcubbcen uca ijjen iwta wenneɣni s weẓru niɣ s řpuniyyet, uca wanita war immut, \add maca\add* iwḍa di tassut,  
\v 19 \add xenni\add*, mařa wanita ikkar ɛawed uca yuyur ɣar barra x teɣɣarct, ad yiři wenni t iwtin d amezdag. Ad as ixeǧeṣ mɣir min yareyyeḥ uca ad t yejj ad iggenfa mliḥ.   
\m
\v 20 Mařa iwta ḥed ismeɣ nnes niɣ tayya nnes s weɛmud uca immut sadu ufus nnes, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad as yaɣ x tesɣart nnes nican.  
\v 21 Maca mařa iqqim ibedd ijj niɣ tnayen n wussan, war d as yuɣi tasɣart, minzi netta d \add tamenyat n\add* nnuqart nnes i yeǧa.   
\m
\v 22 Mařa iryazen mmenɣen uca wtin ict n temɣart s ddeyset uca iwḍa as-dd uɛeddis nnes, maca war iǧi ca d ayezzim, \add xenni\add* netta ad ixeǧeṣ nican ijj n multa ɛlaḥsab min d as ɣa ittar weryaz n temɣart uca ad tt iwc i řquḍat. \f ◼ \fr 21:22 \ft \+fk řquḍat\ft  - niɣ ‘imezurfa’, aqa-ten d iwdan nni ɣar iǧa tussna n izerfan (ccariɛa) uca sřin i ddɛawi n iwdan maḥend ad xasen ḥekkmen.\f*  
\v 23 Mařa imsar ca n uyezzim d aɛeffan, \add řexdenni\add* ad tewced tudart s tudart,  
\v 24 tiṭṭ s tiṭṭ, tiɣmest s teɣmest, afus s ufus, aḍar s uḍar, \x ◘ \xo 21:24 \xt Lawi 24:20; Aɛwd. 19:21; Mt. 5:38\x*  
\v 25 acmaḍ s wecmaḍ, ayezzim s uyezzim, ticti s tecti.   
\m
\v 26 Mařa iřqef ḥed tiṭṭ n ismeɣ nnes niɣ tiṭṭ n tayya nnes, iḍeyyeɛ i-tt, \add xenni\add* ad t yejj ad yuyur amenni zi ssibbet n tiṭṭ nnes.  
\v 27 Mařa s tecti ittekkes tiɣmest n ismeɣ nnes, niɣ tiɣmest n tayya nnes, \add xenni\add* ad as yejj ad yuyur amenni zi ssibbet n teɣmest nnes.   
\m
\v 28 Mařa afunas ibarrez aryaz niɣ tamɣart, u wanita immut, \add xenni\add* ad arjmen afunas u aysum nnes war zzayes ttᵉtten. Bab n ufunas ad yiři d afurri. \x ◘ \xo 21:28 \xt Amz. 9:5\x*  
\v 29 \add Maca\add* mařa afunas tuɣa d abarrez iḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ uca bab nnes tuɣa issen uca war t iḥḍi uca inɣa aryaz niɣ tamɣart, \add xenni\add* ad arjmen afunas uca ɛawed ad nɣen bab nnes.  
\v 30 Mařa ggin xas ddeyyet, \add řexdenni\add* ad iwc marra min xas ggin d ttaman n ufekki i tudart nnes, \f ◼ \fr 21:30 \ft \+fk tudart\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*  
\v 31 niɣ mařa \add afunas\add* ibarrez aḥenjir niɣ taḥenjirt. Ad as ggen ɛlaḥsab lfariḍa-ya.  
\v 32 Mařa afunas ibarrez ismeɣ niɣ tayya, ad wcen třatin ciqlu n nnuqart i sidis, uca afunas ad t arjmen.   
\m
\v 33 Mařa yarzem ḥed anu niɣ mařa iɣza ḥed anu uca war t idři, uca iwḍa dayes ufunas niɣ aɣyuř,  
\v 34 \add xenni\add* bab n wanu ad ixeǧeṣ. Ad yarr nnuqart i bab nnes uca \add řebhimet\add* immuten ad tiři nnes.   
\m
\v 35 Mařa afunas iyzem afunas n wajjar nnes ařami immut, \add řexdenni\add* ad zzenzen afunas iddaren, ad bḍan tamenyat-a \add jar asen\add* uca ad bḍan ɛawed \add afunas\add* amettin.  
\v 36 \add Maca mařa\add* issen belli afunas ibarrez iḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ, uca bab nnes war t iḥḍi, ad ixeǧeṣ afunas s ufunas uca \add afunas\add* amettin ad yiři nnes.  
\v 37 Mařa yucar ḥed afunas niɣ ijjen zeg wuǧi uca iɣarṣ as niɣ izzenz i-t, \add xenni\add* ad ixeǧeṣ xemsa n ifunasen x yijj n ufunas u arebɛa n wuǧi x yijjen n wuǧi.” \x ◘ \xo 21:37 \xt 2 Ṣm. 12:6\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 22
\s1 Tiweṣṣa zi jjihet n wagřa n umqarreb  
\m
\v 1 “Mařa ittwaf uceffar \add ɛad\add* am ittacar, uca iwta i-t uca immut, war \add ttiřin\add* idammen x wenni t yufin.  
\v 2 Mařa tenqar-dd xas tfuct, \add ad\add* xas \add iřin\add* idammen di ssibbet-a. Ad as ixeǧeṣ uceffar marra. Mařa war ɣares ca, ad immenz di ssibbet n tucceffra nnes.  
\v 3 Mařa tᵉttwaf tucceffart teddar deg ufus nnes, ma d afunas \add i tt tuɣa\add* niɣ d aɣyuř niɣ d ijjen zeg wuǧi, ittxeṣṣa as ad ixeǧeṣ tnayen n tseqqar.   
\m
\v 4 Mařa ijja ḥed ad heddan \add řmař\add* iyyar niɣ amarjeɛ n uḍiř uca yarwes dayes taḥimart nnes uca ad asen iḍřeq ařami ad heddan di temmurt n wenneɣni, \add xenni\add* ad \add tt\add* ixeǧeṣ zi řemxeyyer n yeyyar nnes u zi řemxeyyer n umarjeɛ n uḍiř nnes.   
\m
\v 5 Mařa teffeɣ-dd tmessi uca teřqef asennan uca tecca tiqebbiḍin \add n imendi\add* niɣ imendi ibedden niɣ iyyar, \add xenni\add* wenni iqqden timessi ad ixeǧeṣ marra min ittwacemḍen.   
\m
\v 6 Mařa iḥḍa ḥed i wajjar nnes nnuqart niɣ řeqcuɛ u man aya ittwacar as zi taddart n weryaz \add nni\add*, \add xenni\add* aceffar, mařa ufin t, ad ixeǧeṣ tnayen n tseqqar.  
\v 7 Mařa war ittwif uceffar, \add řexdenni\add* ad ssqarrben bab n taddart ɣar AREBBI \add maḥend ad ssnen\add* ma \add war\add* isswiẓẓeḍ ufus nnes ɣar wagřa n wajjar nnes.   
\m
\v 8 Kuř aɛeddi zi jjihet n ufunas niɣ n weɣyuř niɣ n ijj zeg wuǧi niɣ n warruḍ niɣ n min iweddaren i zzayes inna \add ḥed:\add* ‘Aqa-t d wa!’, ad dd-tas tmesřact i iǧan jar asen s tnayen zzat i řquḍat uca wenni ad xas ḥekmen řquḍat ad ixeǧeṣ i wajjar nnes tnayen n tseqqar.   
\m
\v 9 Mařa iwca ḥed i wajjar nnes aɣyuř niɣ afunas niɣ ijj n zeg wuǧi, niɣ mammec ma tegga řebhimet, ḥima ad t iḥḍa uca immut niɣ yarreẓ niɣ ucaren t, am war iẓri ḥed,  
\v 10 \add xenni\add* ad tiři tjaǧit ɣar SIDI jar asen s tnayen belli war isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes ɣar wagřa n wajjar nnes. Bab nnes ad iqbeř \add tajaǧit nnes\add* uca ad taf břa ma ad \add t\add* ittxeǧeṣ wenneɣni.  
\v 11 \add Maca\add* mařa ittwacar nican zzayes, \add di lḥala-ya\add* ad ixeǧeṣ i bab nnes.  
\v 12 Mařa iban aqa ittwamezzeq nican, ad t yawi d burhan uca war ittxeǧiṣ min ittwamezzqen.   
\m
\v 13 Mařa yarḍeř ḥed ca x wajjar nnes uca tarreẓ niɣ temmut di řɣayeb n bab nnes, ittxeṣṣa as ad tt ixeǧeṣ marra.  
\v 14 Maca mařa bab nnes tuɣa iḥḍar, war tt ittxiǧaṣ. Mařa tuɣa icra tt \add xas\add*, ad dd-yas x řexřaṣ nnes.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 X usefsad n arruḥ d arrimet, x yinni iḍeɛfen u x uceqqef di Arebbi  
\m
\v 15 “Uca mařa immarḍen ḥed x ca n teɛzařect, tuɣa war tt ixḍib ḥed ɛad, uca iṭṭeṣ akides, ittxeṣṣa as ad as iwc ṣṣadaq imun \add maḥend\add* ad tt yawi d tamɣart.  
\v 16 Mařa babas war ixs ad as tt iwc, ad \add as\add* iwzen ɛad ṣṣadaq n teɛzuray s nnuqart.   
\m
\v 17 War ttejji taseḥḥart ad teddar. \x ◘ \xo 22:17 \xt Aɛwd. 18:10, 11\x*   
\m
\v 18 Man wen i ɣa iṭṭṣen ak-d ijj n řmař, ad t nɣen nican. \x ◘ \xo 22:18 \xt Lawi 18:23; 20:15\x*   
\m
\v 19 Wenni i ɣa iwehhben ca n tɣarṣt i irebbiten, war iǧi mɣir i SIDI waha, ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaḥarrem \add i uteḥḥi\add*. \x ◘ \xo 22:19 \xt Aɛwd. 17:2, 3, 4, 5\x*   
\m
\v 20 War ddeǧem abarrani u war xas ttzeyyarem, minzi tuɣa uřa d kenniw d ibarraniyyen di temmurt n Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 22:20 \xt Lawi 19:34\x*   
\m
\v 21 War ttdeǧi ca ict n tajjač niɣ ijj n uyujiř. \x ◘ \xo 22:21 \xt Zak. 7:10\x*  
\v 22 Mařa tiwḍed ad t tesseḥqared aṭṭas uca netta isɣuy-dd ɣari, aqa Necc s uɣiř ad sřeɣ i tɣuyyit nnes.  
\v 23 Ad yareɣ weɣḍab inu uca Necc ad kenniw nɣeɣ s ssif, timeṭṭa nwem ad dewřent d tijjař d tarrawt nwem d iyujiřen.   
\m
\v 24 Mařa tareḍřed nnuqart i řgens inu, i umezřuḍ i \add din\add* ɣarek, \add xenni\add* war kides ttegged am ittegg bab n umarwas: war xas ttegg ca arriba. \x ◘ \xo 22:24 \xt Lawi 25:36,37; Aɛwd. 23:18, 19; Izhd. 15:5; Awřn. 28:8; Ḥiz. 18:8\x*   
\m
\v 25 Mařa teksid arruḍ n wajjar nnec d aḍman, arr as t qbeř ma ad teɣři tfuct. \x ◘ \xo 22:25 \xt Aɛwd. 24:12, 13\x*  
\v 26 Minzi war ɣares mɣir ařeḥḥaf wanita, aqa-t d arruḍ x teřmect nnes. Min di ɣa iṭṭeṣ \add xenni\add*? Xmi ɣari dd ɣa isɣuy, řexdenni ad as sřeɣ, minzi Necc aqa d aḥnin!   
\m
\v 27 War ttceqqif di AREBBI u war ttekkʷar řḥakem n řgens nnec. \x ◘ \xo 22:27 \xt Uf. 21:6, 8; Řex. 23:3, 4, 5\x*   
\m
\v 28 War sɛeṭṭařa taccuret \add n tmeyra\add* nnec niɣ aḥřay \add n teysart\add* nnec. Ad ayi tewced \add uřa\add* d amenzu n iḥenjiren nnec. \x ◘ \xo 22:28 \xt Uf. 13:2, 12\x*  
\v 29 Ammu i ɣa tegged \add ɛawed\add* s ifunasen nnec d wuǧi nnec. Sebɛa n wussan ad iřin ak-d yemmatsen uca ɣar wass wiss tmenya ad ayi ten tewced. \x ◘ \xo 22:29 \xt Uf. 23:19; Lawi 22:27; Ḥiz. 44:30\x*   
\m
\v 30 Ad ayi tiřim d imqeddasen u war ttᵉttem aysum i ittwamezzqen di řexřa. Ad t tenḍarem i yiṭan.” \f ◼ \fr 22:30 \ft \+fk imqeddasen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘iwdan imqeddasen’ niɣ ‘iryazen imqeddasen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 22:30 \xt Lawi 22:8; Ḥiz. 44:31\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 23
\s1 Tiweṣṣa zi jjihet n mammec i ɣa nemṣurruf ak-d umqarreb  
\m
\v 1 “War ssuffuɣ řexbar issxarriqen. War ttic afus nnec i uɛeffan, maḥend ad tiřid d acehhad n ddeǧ.   
\m
\v 2 War areddef azyen ameqqran di řɣar u war dd-ttarri di ddeɛwet ař ɣa tmeyyřed \add teggʷejed x řḥeqq\add* awarni i waṭṭas, ad tfarɣed \add řḥeqq\add*.   
\m
\v 3 Di ddeɛwet nnes war ttriḥ ca ak-d řmeskin. \x ◘ \xo 23:3 \xt Lawi 19:15\x*   
\m
\v 4 Mařa teřqid afunas niɣ aɣyuř iweddar n řeɛdu nnec, ittxeṣṣa ad as t tarred nican. \x ◘ \xo 23:4 \xt Aɛwd. 22:1, 2; Lk. 6:27; Fil. 2:4\x*  
\v 5 Mařa teẓrid aɣyuř n wenni tcarrhed iwḍa s ddqeř nnes, ittxeṣṣa cek ad teḥḍid ixef nnec ad tejjed \add tamesřact\add* i netta waha, \add maca\add* cek d netta jmiɛ ad tfekkem \add aɣyuř\add* qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 23:5 \xt Aɛwd. 22:4\x*   
\m
\v 6 War sfarraɣ tasɣart n umezřuḍ i \add din\add* ɣarek di ddeɛwet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 23:6 \xt Aɛwd. 27:19\x*   
\m
\v 7 Beɛɛed x tmesřact iɣeccen. War neqq afurri niɣ amsegged, minzi Necc war ttbarriɣ aɛeffan.  
\v 8 War kessi tarzeft, minzi tarzeft tessdarɣař tiṭṭawin yarezmen u tessfarraɣ awařen n imseggden. \x ◘ \xo 23:8 \xt Aɛwd. 16:19; 1 Ṣm. 8:3; Awřn. 19:6; Amb. 7:7\x*   
\m
\v 9 War tzeyyarem x ubarrani. Aqa kenniw tessnem nnefs n ubarrani, minzi tuɣa kenniw d ibarraniyyen di temmurt n Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 23:9 \xt Uf. 22:21; Lawi 19:33; Aɛwd. 24:17\x*   
\m
\v 10 Setta n iseggʷusa ad tzarɛed tammurt nnec uca ad tessmuned řɣiǧet nnes.  
\v 11 Deg \add useggʷas\add* wiss sebɛa ad tt tejjed ad tareyyḥed uca ad as tarxud, ḥima ad \add zzayes\add* ccen imezřaḍ n řgens nnec. Uca min ɣa jjen nitni ad \add zzayes\add* ccen řmař n řexřa. Ammu i ɣa tegged ɛawed s umarjeɛ n uḍiř nnec d zzitun nnec. \x ◘ \xo 23:11 \xt Lawi 25:4, 5\x*   
\m
\v 12 Di setta n wussan ad tegged řxedmet nnec u deg wass wiss sebɛa ad tareyyḥed, maḥend ad yareyyeḥ ufunas nnec d weɣyuř nnec u ad yarr nnefs mmis n tayya nnec d ubarrani.”\x ◘ \xo 23:12 \xt Uf. 20:8; 31:13-17.\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tiweṣṣa zi jjihet n uweqqar i Sidi Arebbi  
\m
\v 13 Di marra min d awem nniɣ, ḥḍam t. War ttidarem isem n irebbiten nneɣni. War ttesřan \add isem nnes\add* zeg uqemmum nnec. \x ◘ \xo 23:13 \xt Řxř. 32:38; Yac. 23:7; Izhd. 16:4; Ḥuc. 2:19; Zak. 13:2\x*   
\m
\v 14 Třata n twařawin deg useggʷas ad ayi tɛeyydem ijj n řɛid.  
\v 15 Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun ad t teḥḍam. Sebɛa n wussan ad tecced aɣrum břa antun, am mammec kenniw umureɣ Necc, di řweqt ittwaggen deg uyur Abib, minzi dayes i dd-teffɣed zi Miṣra. War dd-ttusim \add s ifassen\add* xwan zzat i wudem inu. \x ◘ \xo 23:15 \xt Uf. 12:14, 15; 13:3; 34:20; Aɛwd. 16:16\x*  
\v 16 \add Ḥḍam ɛawed\add* Řɛid n Tmeyra, \add Řɛid n\add* Tmenzut n řxedmet nnec i tzarɛed deg iyyar, u Řɛid n Usmuni \add n ṣṣabet\add* deg uneggar n useggʷas, xmi ɣa tessmuned \add řɣiǧet n\add* řxedmet nnec zeg iyyar. \x ◘ \xo 23:16 \xt Uf. 34:22\x*  
\v 17 Třata n twařawin deg useggʷas ad ḍharen marra iryazen \add n řgens nnec\add* i wudem n Sidi, SIDI.   
\m
\v 18 War ttqeddam idammen n tɣarṣt inu ak-d min ixemmaren, u tadunt n \add tɣarṣt n\add* řɛid inu war ttnusi ǧiřet \add tekmeř\add* ař ṣṣbeḥ.   
\m
\v 19 Tamezwarut n tmenzut zeg wudem n temmurt nnec ad \add tt\add* tawyed ɣar Taddart n SIDI, AREBBI nnec. War snenni iɣayḍ d ameẓyan s uɣi n yemmas. \x ◘ \xo 23:19 \xt Uf. 34:26\x*   
\m
\v 20 Xzar, ad ssekkeɣ ijj n lmalak zzat i wudem nnec, ḥima ad cek iḥḍa deg webrid uca ad cek yawi ɣar wemcan nni sswejdeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 23:20 \xt Uf. 33:2\x*  
\v 21 Ḥḍa arendad i wudem nnes uca seř i wawař nnes, war xas ssarzig ca \add řeɛmar\add*, minzi netta war ittekkes iɛeddiyen nwem, minzi Isem inu aqa-t dayes.  
\v 22 Maca mařa s tidett ad tesřed i wawař nnes, ad tegged marra min d ac ɣa iniɣ, ad iřiɣ d řeɛdu i řɛedyan nnec uca ad ḥṣareɣ inni cek iḥeṣṣaren.\x ◘ \xo 23:22 \xt Amz. 12:3\x*  
\v 23 Minzi lmalak inu ad yiři zzatek, ad cek ssidfeɣ di \add temmurt n\add* Imuriyyen d Iḥittiyyen d Ifiriziyyen d ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen, u Necc ad ten teḥḥiɣ.  
\v 24 War ttbendiq i irebbiten nsen niɣ ad ten tɛebded niɣ ad tegged am tteggen nitni, maca ad ten tᵉteḥḥid qaɛ uca ad tarẓed marra imayḍuten nsen \add iqeddsen\add*.  
\v 25 Ad tɛebdem SIDI, AREBBI nwem, u Netta ad ibarek aɣrum nnec d waman nnec. Necc ad kkseɣ řehřacat zi řwesṭ nnec. \x ◘ \xo 23:25 \xt Uf. 15:26; Aɛwd. 7:15\x*  
\v 26 War ttiři \add temɣart\add* nni umi iwḍa uɛeddis niɣ war ittirwen di temmurt nnec. Necc ad kemmřeɣ řqedd n wussan nnec. \x ◘ \xo 23:26 \xt Aɛwd. 7:14\x*  
\v 27 Ad ssekkeɣ anexřiɛ zzat i uɣembub nnec, ad ssxarewḍeɣ marra řgens i ɣa tafed \add deg webrid nnec\add* uca ad arreɣ marra řɛedyan nnec ad xak arewřen. \x ◘ \xo 23:27 \xt Uf. 14:24; Yac. 10:10\x*  
\v 28 Necc ad ssekkeɣ irezzan zzat i uɣembub nnec, inni ɣa yaẓẓřen x Iḥiwiyyen d ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥittiyyen zzat i wudem nnec. \x ◘ \xo 23:28 \xt Aɛwd. 7:20; Yac. 24:12\x*  
\v 29 War xasen ttaẓẓřeɣ zi zzat nwem deg ijj n useggʷas, maḥend war tᵉttɣimi temmurt d řexřa u řmař \add n řexřa\add* war xak ttmarnin aṭṭas.  
\v 30 S cway cway ad xasen aẓẓřeɣ zi zzat necc, ař ɣa temmarenyed \add deg waṭṭas\add* uca \add ad tzemmared\add* ad teksid tammurt d řwart.  
\v 31 Necc ad ggeɣ iymiren zi Řebḥar n Telga ař řebḥar n Ifilisṭiniyyen u zi řexřa ař iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, minzi ad arreɣ imezdaɣ n temmurt deg ufus nnec uca \add ad cek arreɣ\add* ad xasen taẓẓřed zi zzat nnec. \x ◘ \xo 23:31 \xt Řxř. 34:3, 4\x*  
\v 32 War kidsen ttegg řɛahd niɣ ak-d irebbiten nsen. \x ◘ \xo 23:32 \xt Uf. 34:12, 15; Aɛwd. 7:2\x*  
\v 33 War iɛeddeř ad zedɣen di temmurt nnec, ḥima war cek ttarrin ad akidi texḍid. Mařa tɛebded i irebbiten nsen, ad ac yiři man aya d řfex i cek.” \x ◘ \xo 23:33 \xt Yac. 23:13; Řqḍ. 2:3\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 24
\s1 Řɛahd n Arebbi ak-d řgens  
\m
\v 1 Uca inna Netta i Musa:  
\m “Geɛɛed ɣar SIDI, cek d Harun d Nadab d Abihu, d sebɛin n imɣaren n Israil, uca bendqem zi řaggʷaj.  
\v 2 Musa weḥḥdes ad dd-iqarreb ɣar SIDI, \add maca\add* war iɛeddeř ad qarrben nitni. Uřa d řgens war kides ittgiɛɛid ca.”  
\v 3 Musa iɛqeb-dd uca ixebbar řgens x marra awařen n SIDI u x marra lfarayiḍ. Marra řgens yarra-dd s yijj n wawař, nnan: “Marra awařen i inna SIDI ad zzaysen negg.” \f ◼ \fr 24:3 \ft \+fk s yijj n wawař\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s yijj n uqemmum’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 24:3 \xt Uf. 19:8; 24:7; Aɛwd. 5:27\x*  
\v 4 Musa yura marra awařen n SIDI. Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ zic ikkar uca ibna ijj n uɛalṭar ɣar iḍaren n wedrar uca \add igga\add* tenɛac n imayḍuten n weẓru, ɛlaḥsab \add řqedd n\add* tenɛac n tqebbař n Israil.  
\v 5 Issekk iḥudriyyen zeg ayt n Israil, inni issbexxaren tiɣarṣi n wecmaḍ u qeddmen tiɣarṣi n řehna zeg ifunasen imeẓyanen i SIDI.  
\v 6 Iksi Musa azyen n idammen, igga \add i-t\add* di ṭṭbaṣi uca azyen \add nneɣni\add* n idammen izeǧeɛ i-ten x uɛalṭar.  
\v 7 Iksi adlis ittwannḍen n Řɛahd, iɣra i-t x imezzuɣen n řgens uca nitni nnan: “Marra min \add d aneɣ\add* inna SIDI, ad \add t\add* negg, ad \add t\add* nṭaɛ.”  
\v 8 Iksi Musa idammen, irucc i-ten x řgens, inna: “Xzar, ina d idammen n Řɛahd nni igga SIDI akidwem x marra awařen-a.” \x ◘ \xo 24:8 \xt Ɛbr. 9:20; 1 Bṭ. 1:2\x*   
\m
\v 9 Igeɛɛed Musa ak-d Harun d Nadab d Abihu d sebɛin n imɣaren n Israil.  
\v 10 Ẓrin AREBBI n Israil. Tuɣa sadu iḍaren nnes am tisi n zzellij i ittwaggen n ṣaffir aziza, iṣfa am ujenna simant nnes. \x ◘ \xo 24:10 \xt Asa. 4:6\x*  
\v 11 War isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes x imcennɛen n ayt n Israil uca nitni xzaren ɣar AREBBI, ccin, swin.   
\m
\v 12 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Geɛɛed-dd ɣari ɣar wedrar uca qqim din uca Necc ad ac wceɣ tiřwiḥin n weẓru, Ccariɛa d řumarat tinni uriɣ x teřwiḥin, ḥima ad asen \add tent\add* tessřemded.”  
\v 13 Ikkar Musa ak-d Yacuwa, amsexxar nnes, uca igeɛɛed Musa ɣar wedrar n AREBBI.  
\v 14 Inna i imɣaren: “Rajam aneɣ danita ař dd ɣarwem i ɣa nedweř. Xzar, Harun d Ḥur akidwem. Mařa din ḥed ɣares ddɛawi, ittxeṣṣa as ad ɣarsen iraḥ.”   
\m
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed Musa ɣar wedrar, uca ijj n useynu idřa adrar.  
\v 16 Aɛuǧi n SIDI tuɣa izeddeɣ deg wedrar n Sina u aseynu idřa i-t setta n wussan uca deg wass wiss sebɛa iřaɣa-dd Netta x Musa zi řwesṭ n useynu.  
\v 17 Ascan n uɛuǧi n SIDI tuɣa-t di tiṭṭawin n ayt n Israil am tmessi ittetten x tqiccat n wedrar. \x ◘ \xo 24:17 \xt Ɛbr. 12:29\x*  
\v 18 Yudef Musa ɣar řwesṭ n useynu uca igeɛɛed adrar. Tuɣa Musa iqqim arebɛin n wussan d arebɛin n ǧyaři deg wedrar.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 25
\s1 Tiweṣṣa zi jjihet n řebni n Tzeddiɣt n Sidi Arebbi  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Ini i ayt n Israil ad ayi dd-ssgaɛɛden tawhibt. Zi kuř aryaz nni d as iɛarren wuř nnes, ad zzayes teksim \bd tawhibt n usgaɛɛed\bd* i Necc. \x ◘ \xo 25:2 \xt Uf. 35:5; 1 Im. 29:3, 5, 9,14; Ɛiz. 2:68; 3:5; Naḥ. 11:2\x*  
\v 3 Ta d \bd tawhibt n usgeɛɛed\bd*, tenni i ɣa teksid zzaysen: ureɣ d nnuqart d nnḥas,  
\v 4 d \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d řeqṭen azdad d ccɛar n iɣayḍen, \f ◼ \fr 25:4 \ft \+fk azeggʷaɣ iḥedqen\ft  - niɣ ‘qirmiz’.\f*  
\v 5 d iřmawen izeggʷaɣen n icarriyyen, d iřmawen n ddenfiřat, d ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya, \f ◼ \fr 25:5 \ft \+fk akasiya\ft  - ict n tcejjart s ukeccuḍ iqesḥen aṭṭas. Tᵉttwaf tcejjart-a aṭṭas di řexřa n Sinayi. S Teɛrabt qqaren as ‘سَنْط’.\f*  
\v 6 zzect i tfawt n řqendiř, řeɛṭur i zzect n wedhan u i řebxur ittfuḥen,  
\v 7 iẓra n uniks d iẓra \add iɣřan nneɣni\add*, maḥend ad ten ggen x upalṭu u x tajmect. \x ◘ \xo 25:7 \xt Uf. 28:4-14\x*   
\m
\v 8 Ad ayi ggen \bd ict n Zzawect Iqeddsen\bd*, ḥima ad zedɣeɣ di řwesṭ nsen.  
\v 9 Ad \add t\add* tegged am marra min d ac ɣa ssecneɣ, \add ɛlaḥsab\add* amedya n Tzeddiɣt u \add ɛlaḥsab\add* amedya n marra řeqcuɛ i dayes iǧan.   
\m
\v 10 Ad ggen ɛawed ict n \bd Ttabut\bd* n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya. Ad tiři tuzzeggart \add nnes\add* tnayen n iɣaǧen d wezyen u tiru \add nnes\add* ijj n uɣiř d wezyen u řuɛřa \add nnes\add* ijj n uɣiř d wezyen. \x ◘ \xo 25:10 \xt Uf. 37:1; Ɛbr. 9:1\x*  
\v 11 Ad t ttcelled s wureɣ iṣfan, zi daxeř u zi barra ad tt tcelled, uca ɣar sennej ad as tennḍed ijj n zzwaq n wureɣ.  
\v 12 Ad as tessfesyed arebɛa n texrazin n wureɣ. Ad tent tcedded ɣar arebɛa n tyarsawin nnes. Tnayen n texrazin ad iřint ɣar yijj n uɣezdis u tnayen n texrazin i uɣezdis nneɣni.  
\v 13 Ad tegged iɛumad \add i trebbut\add* zeg ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya uca ad ten tedřed s wureɣ.  
\v 14 Sidfem iɛumad di texrazin nni iǧan ɣar iɣezdisen n Ttabut, ḥima ad zzaysen arbun Ttabut.  
\v 15 Iɛumad ad iřin di texrazin n Ttabut, war zzaysent ten ttekksen ca. \x ◘ \xo 25:15 \xt 1 Ij. 8:8\x*  
\v 16 Ad tessarsed Cchadet, tenni i d ac ɣa wceɣ, di Ttabut. \x ◘ \xo 25:16 \xt Ɛbr. 9:4\x*  
\v 17 Ad tegged ɛawed ict n \bd tqebbart n weṣřaḥ\bd* n wureɣ iṣfan s yict n tuzzeggart n tnayen n iɣaǧen d wezyen u s ict n tiru n ijj n uɣiř d wezyen. \f ◼ \fr 25:17 \ft \+fk taqebbart n weṣřaḥ\ft  - ḥima ad tfehmed ktar min ixs ad yini awař-a, xzar Lawi 16:14, 15 uřa Di Řexřa 7:89.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 25:17 \xt Uf. 37:6\x*  
\v 18 Ad tegged ɛawed \bd tnayen n ikiruben\bd* n wureɣ iɛdeř s wefḍis, ařami i ɣa ffɣen \add ikiruben\add* zi tnayen n ixfawen n tqebbart n weṣřaḥ. \f ◼ \fr 25:18 \ft \+fk ikiruben\ft  - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 25:18 \xt Ɛbr. 9:5\x*  
\v 19 Ad tegged ijj n ukirub ɣar ijj n yixef u ijj n ukirub nneɣni ɣar yixef nneɣni. Ad teggem ikiruben zi tqebbart n weṣřaḥ ɣar tnayen n ixfawen nnes.  
\v 20 Ad bezzɛen ikiruben afriwen nsen sennej nsen uca ad dřen taqebbart n weṣřaḥ s wafriwen nsen. Udmawen nsen ad iřin ijj qibač i wenneɣni uca ad ẓaren udmawen n ikiruben ɣar tqebbart n weṣřaḥ. \x ◘ \xo 25:20 \xt Ɛbr. 9:5\x*  
\v 21 Ad tegged taqebbart n weṣřaḥ x Ttabut uca ad tessarsed Cchadet i d ac ɣa wceɣ di Ttabut. \x ◘ \xo 25:21 \xt Ɛbr. 9:4, 5\x*  
\v 22 Dinni i kic ɣa mmeřqiɣ uca ad kik ssiwřeɣ zi sennej i tqebbart n weṣřaḥ, zi jar tnayen n ikiruben nni iǧan sennej i Ttabut n Cchadet, x marra min d ac ɣa umureɣ i ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 25:22 \xt Řxř. 7:89\x*   
\m
\v 23 Ad tegged ict n \bd tzewḍa\bd* n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya, ad ɣares tiři ict n tuzzeggart n tnayen n iɣaǧen d ict n tiru n ijjen uɣiř d ijj n řuɛřa n ijjen uɣiř d wezyen.  
\v 24 Ad tt tedřed s wureɣ iṣfan uca ad as tegged ɣar tma nnes ijj zzwaq n wureɣ.  
\v 25 Ad tegged ict n tma i d as dd-innḍen n ijj n cbar n ufus u ɣar tma i d as dd-innḍen ad tegged ijj n zzwaq n wureɣ.  
\v 26 Ad tegged arebɛa n texrazin n wureɣ uca ad tent tcedded ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura nni iǧan ɣar arebɛa n iḍaren nsen.  
\v 27 Tixrazin ad iřint udsent i tma, maḥend ad \add daysent\add* ttwaṭṭfen iɛumad i tarebbut n tzewḍa.  
\v 28 Ad tegged iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* zeg ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya, ad ten tɣeǧfed s wureɣ uca ad zzaysen arbun tazewḍa.  
\v 29 Ad tegged ɛawed ṭṭbaṣi nnes d tɣenjayin nnes d iɣarrafen nnes d řkisan nnes i zi ɣa farrɣen. Ad ten tegged s wureɣ iṣfan.   
\m
\v 30 X tzewḍa ad tegged \bd aɣrum n wescan\bd* řebda zzat i wudem inu.   
\m
\v 31 Ad tegged \bd řqendiř\bd* s wureɣ iṣfan. Ad tegged řqendiř s wefḍis n wemziř. Afud ak-d uḍar nnes d iɣaǧen nnes uřa d řkisan nnes d tɛebbuzin nnes i dd-ittasen ak-d nnuwwarat nnes ad iřin d aɣezdis d ijj. \x ◘ \xo 25:31 \xt Uf. 37:17\x*  
\v 32 Setta n iɣaǧen ad dd-ffɣen zeg iɣezdisen nnes, třata n iɣaǧen zeg ijj n uɣezdis n řqendiř d třata n iɣaǧen zeg uɣezdis nneɣni n řqendiř.  
\v 33 Třata n řkisan \add ad iřin\add* deg ijj n uɣiř di furma n nnuwwarat n ǧewz \add ak-d\add* tɛebbuzt d nnewwac, uca \add ɛawed\add* ɣar uɣiř nneɣni třata n řkisan di furma n nnuwwarat n ǧewz \add ak-d\add* tɛebbuzt d nnewwac. Ammu \add i ɣa ggen\add* marra setta n iɣaǧen nni dd-iffɣen zi řqendiř.  
\v 34 Ɣar řqendiř \add simant nnes ad din iřin\add* arebɛa n řkisan di furma n nnuwwarat n ǧewz, \add ak-d\add* tɛebbuzin nsen i dd-ittasen ak-d nnuwwarat nsen.  
\v 35 Ad \add din\add* tiři ict n tɛebbuzt sadu tyuya n iɣaǧen i zzayes dd-iffɣen u ict n tɛebbuzt sadu tyuya n iɣaǧen i zzayes dd-iffɣen \add awarni as\add*, u \add ɛawed\add* ict n tɛebbuzt sadu tyuya n iɣaǧen i zzayes dd-iffɣen \add awarni as\add*. \add Ammu i ɣa yiři\add* i setta n iɣaǧen i dd-iffɣen zi řqendiř.  
\v 36 Tiɛebbuzin \add nsen\add* d iɣaǧen nsen ad zzayes-dd ffɣen uca marra aya ad yiři d ict n řqecɛet tᵉttwaɛdeř s wefḍis n wemziř s wureɣ iṣfan.  
\v 37 Ad tegged setta n řefnarat nnes uca ad ssarsen řefnarat nnes x řqendiř, maḥend ad wcent tfawt ɣar ṭṭarf n ujemmaḍ.  
\v 38 Tijeqqaḍin \add n teftič\add* nnes d tmejmarin nnes \add ad iřint\add* s wureɣ iṣfan. \f ◼ \fr 25:38 \ft \+fk Tijeqqaḍin\ft  - niɣ ‘tineqqaḍin’.\f*  
\v 39 Ad ittwagg \add řqendiř\add* zeg ict n talint n wureɣ iṣfan s marra řeqcuɛ-a \add akides\add*.  
\v 40 Uca xzar, ad t tegged am umedya nnes, wenni i d ac ittwamřen deg wedrar.” \x ◘ \xo 25:40 \xt Řex. 7:44; Ɛbr. 8:5\x*  *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 26
\m
\v 1 “Ad tegged \bd Tazeddiɣt s ɛecra n tjartiřin s řeqṭen azdad imuden u s \+bdit ufiřu\+bdit* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen, \+bdit ak-d\+bdit* ikiruben\bd*. Ad ten tegged \add am\add* řxedmet n ufennan. \x ◘ \xo 26:1 \xt Uf. 36:8\x*  
\v 2 Tuzzeggart n yict n tjartiřt ad tiři tmenya u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen u tiru n yict n tjartiřt arebɛa n iɣaǧen. Marra tijartiřin \add ad ɣarsent yiři\add* řeɛbar d ijj.  
\v 3 Xemsa n tjartiřin ad tent ssmunen ict ak-d tenneɣni u \add ɛawed\add* xemsa n tjartiřin ad tent ssmunen ict ak-d tenneɣni.  
\v 4 Ɣar tma n yict n tjartiřt ɣar ṭṭarf mani tt ɣa ssmunen, ad tegged tisarawin tideḥmanin. Ammu i tent ɣa tegged \add ɛawed\add* ɣar tma n tjartiřt \add nneɣni\add* ɣar ṭṭarf i ɣar iǧa useřqi nneɣni.  
\v 5 Xemsin n tsarawin i ɣa tegged deg ict n tjartiřt u xemsin n tsarawin ɣar ṭṭarf n tjartiřt nni ɣar iǧa useřqi nneɣni, maḥend tisarawin ad mmeřqant ict ak-d tenneɣni.  
\v 6 Ad tegged ɛawed xemsin n tsennarin n wureɣ uca ad tessmuned tijartiřin ict ak-d tenneɣni s tsennarin, maḥend ad tedweř d ict n Tzeddiɣt.   
\m
\v 7 Ad tegged ɛawed \bd tijařtiřin s ccɛar n iɣayḍen\bd*, maḥend ad iřint d ijj n uqiḍun x Tzeddiɣt. Ad tegged \bd ḥiṭac n tjartiřin\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 26:7 \xt Uf. 36:14\x*  
\v 8 Tuzzeggart n ict n tjartiřt \add ad tiři\add* třatin n iɣaǧen u tiru n ict n tjartiřt \add ad tiři\add* arebɛa n iɣaǧen. Ḥiṭɛac n tjartiřin \add ad ɣarsent yiři\add* řeɛbar d ijj.  
\v 9 Ad tessmuned xemsa n tjartiřin weḥḥedsent d setta n tjartiřin \add ɛawed\add* weḥḥedsent. Tajartiřt wiss setta ad tt tḍefṣed zzat i wudem n Uqiḍun.  
\v 10 Ad tegged xemsin n tsarawin ɣar tma n yict n tjartiřt ɣar ṭṭarf ɣar useřqi, uca xemsin n tsarawin x tma n tjartiřt ɣar useřqi nneɣni.  
\v 11 Ad tegged xemsin n tsennarin n nnḥas uca ad tent tessidfed di tsarawin uca ad tessmuned Aqiḍun, maḥend ad yiři d ijjen.  
\v 12 Min iceṭṭen n tjartiřin n uqiḍun, azyen n tjartiřt nni iceṭṭen ad yayeř ɣar ḍeffar n Tzeddiɣt.  
\v 13 Zi min iceṭṭen di tuzzeggart n tjartiřin, ijj n uɣiř ad yayeř ɣar yijj n ṭṭarf d ijj n uɣiř ɣar ṭṭarf nneɣni, ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen n Tzeddiɣt, maḥend ad as iřeḥḥef i yijj \add n uɣezdis\add* u i \add uɣezdis\add* nneɣni.   
\m
\v 14 Ad tegged i Uqiḍun \add ɛawed\add* \bd ict n tseqqaft n iřmawen izeggʷaɣen n icarriyyen\bd* u sennej i man aya \bd ict n tseqqaft n iřmawen n ddenfiřat.\bd*   
\m
\v 15 Ad tegged i Tzeddiɣt \bd tifeřwin n ukeccuḍ\bd* n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya nni ibedden nican.  
\v 16 Řeɛbar n tuzzeggart n ict n tefřawt dayes ɛecra n iɣaǧen u řeɛbar n tiru n ict n tefřawt dayes ijj n uɣiř d wezyen.  
\v 17 I kuř tafřawt ad ɣares iřin tnayen n iḍaren, inni issmeřqan twečmatin ict ak-d tenneɣnit, ammu i ɣa tegged i marra tifeřwin n Tzeddiɣt.  
\v 18 Ad tegged i Tzeddiɣt \bd tifeřwin\bd*, ɛicrin n tfeřwin ɣar jjihet n ljanub, ɣar yefus.  
\v 19 Ad tegged arebɛin n \bd tyarsawin n nnuqart\bd* \add maḥend ad tent ssarsen\add* sadu ɛicrin n tfeřwin, tnayen n tyarsawin sadu ict n tefřawt i tnayen n iḍaren nnes, d tnayen n tyarsawin sadu tafřawt nneɣni i tnayen n iḍaren nnes.  
\v 20 \add Ɛawed ad tegged\add* ɛicrin n tfeřwin i uɣezdis nneɣni n Tzeddiɣt, ɣar jjihet n ccamal,  
\v 21 s arebɛin n tyarsawin nsen n nnuqart: tnayen n tyarsawin i kuř tafřawt d tnayen n tyarsawin sadu tafřawt nneɣni.  
\v 22 U ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb n Tzeddiɣt ad as tegged setta n tfeřwin.  
\v 23 Ad tegged tnayen n tfeřwin i tɣemmura n Tzeddiɣt i iǧan ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen n ḍeffar.  
\v 24 Zi swadday ad iřint ṣqent am wacniwen uca ammu i ɣa iřint nican d icten ař ɣa awḍent sennej deg ict n texrazt. Ammu i ɣa yiři i tnayen \add n tfeřwin\add* ɣar tnayen n tɣemmura.  
\v 25 Ad \add din\add* iřint tmenya n tfeřwin ak-d tyarsawin nsent n nnuqart. \add Xenni\add* seṭṭac n tyarsawin, tnayen n tyarsawin sadu ict n tefřawt d tnayen n tyarsawin sadu tafřawt nneɣni.   
\m
\v 26 Ad tegged \bd tiḥenya n uɛarreḍ\bd* zeg ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya, \add inni ɣa iɛdun x tfeřwin\add*, xemsa i tfeřwin n ijj n uɣezdis n Tzeddiɣt  
\v 27 u xemsa n tḥenya n uɛarreḍ i tfeřwin ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni n Tzeddiɣt u xemsa n tḥenya n uɛarreḍ i tfeřwin n uɣezdis n Tzeddiɣt ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen n ḍeffar.  
\v 28 Taḥnact n uɛarreḍ di řwesṭ ad teɛdu x tfeřwin di řwesṭ, zeg ijj n yixef ɣar wenneɣni.  
\v 29 Ad tɣeǧfed tifeřwin s wureɣ uca ad tegged tixrazin nsen n wureɣ, maḥend ad daysent ssidfen tiḥenya n uɛarreḍ. Ad tedřed \add ɛawed\add* tiḥenya n uɛarreḍ s wureɣ.  
\v 30 Ad tessgeɛɛded Tazeddiɣt ɛlaḥsab amedya \add n řebni\add* nni d ac ittwamřen x wedrar. \x ◘ \xo 26:30 \xt Uf. 25:9,40; Řex. 7:44; Ɛbr. 8:5\x*   
\m
\v 31 Ad teggeḍ ijj n \bd uřeḥḥaf\bd* s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden, ad t ggen \add am\add* řxedmet n ufennan, uca ikiruben \add ad xas iřin\add*. \x ◘ \xo 26:31 \xt Uf. 36:35\x*  
\v 32 Ad t tayřed x arebɛa n ipilaren n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya i idřin s wureɣ. Tisennarin nsen \add ad iřint\add* n wureɣ uca \add ipilaren nni\add* \add ad bedden\add* x arebɛa n tyarsawin n nnuqart.  
\v 33 Ad tayřed ařeḥḥaf ɣar wadday n tsennarin uca ad tessidfed Ttabut n Cchadet daxeř i uřeḥḥaf uca ařeḥḥaf ad ibḍa jar Uqeddas d Weqdas x Uqeddas.   
\m
\v 34 Ad tessarsed taqebbart n weṣřaḥ x Ttabut n Cchadet deg Weqdas x Uqeddas.   
\m
\v 35 Ad tegged tazewḍa barra i uřeḥḥaf uca ad tessarsed řqendiř qibač i tzewḍa ɣar uɣezdis n Tzeddiɣt ɣar jjihet n ljanub u ad tegged tazewḍa ɣar uɣezdis ɣar jjihet n ccamal.   
\m
\v 36 Ad tegged \bd arwaq\bd* s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden i wadaf n Uqiḍun, \add am\add* ijj n umudi n uxeyyaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 26:36 \xt Uf. 36:37\x*  
\v 37 Uca ad tegged i arwaq xemsa n ipilaren n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya uca ad ten tcelled s wureɣ. Tisennarin nsen ad iřint n wureɣ u \add i ipilaren nni\add* ad asen tfesyed xemsa n tyarsawin n nnḥas.” *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 27
\m
\v 1 “Ad tegged \bd aɛalṭar\bd* n ukeccuḍ n ukasiya n xemsa n iɣaǧen di tuzzeggart d xemsa n iɣaǧen di tiru. Ad yiři s arebɛa n tɣemmura u řuɛřa nnes \add ad yiři\add* třata n iɣaǧen. \x ◘ \xo 27:1 \xt Uf. 38:1\x*  
\v 2 Ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura ad tegged accawen nnes. Accawen nnes ad dewřen d ijjen akides uca ad t třeḥḥfed s nnḥas. \f ◼ \fr 27:2 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iqiccawen’.\f*  
\v 3 Ad tegged tiydurin nnes, ḥima ad daysent tenḍared iɣɣeḍ n min iqqimen n tadunt nnes ittwacemḍen uca \add ad tegged\add* ɛawed iɣenjayen nnes d ṭṭawyat nnes i urucci d furcayat nnes d tmejmarin nnes. Ad tegged marra řeqcuɛ nnes s nnḥas.  
\v 4 Ad tegged ict n tracca, ict n umudi n nnḥas, uca ad tegged arebɛa n texrazin n nnḥas i umudi nni, ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura nnes.  
\v 5 Ad t tzeyyared sadu i tma n uɛalṭar, swadday, \add maḥend\add* ad yiři umudi \add n nnḥas nni\add* ɣar wezyen n uɛalṭar.  
\v 6 Ad tegged iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* i uɛalṭar, iɛumad n ukeccuḍ n ukasiya uca ad ten třeḥḥfed s nnḥas.  
\v 7 Iɛumad nnes ad ttwassidfen di texrazin. Ad iřin iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen n uɛalṭar xmi \add t\add* ɣa arbun.  
\v 8 Ad tegged ijj n řxawi \add ɣar daxeř\add* n tfeřwin. Am mammec i d ac imřa x wedrar, ammu i \add t\add* ɣa ggen nitni.   
\m
\v 9 Ad tegged \bd řemraḥ\bd* n Tzeddiɣt. Ɣar jjihet n ljanub, ɣar yefus, ad tegged řizarat s řeqṭen azdad imuden, \add kuř ict zzaysent\add* n mya n iɣaǧen di tuzzeggart i yijj n uɣezdis. \x ◘ \xo 27:9 \xt Uf. 38:9\x*  
\v 10 Ɛicrin n ipilaren nnes d ɛicrin n tyarsawin nnes \add ad iřin\add* n nnḥas. Tisennarin n ipilaren d iqeḍban nsen i useřqi \add ad iřin\add* n nnuqart.  
\v 11 Ammu ɣar jjihet n ccamal, di tuzzeggart, \add ad din iřint\add* řizarat n mya \add iɣaǧen\add*. Ad iřin ɛicrin n ipilaren nsent d ɛicrin n tyarsawin nsen n nnḥas. Tisennarin n ipilaren d iqeḍban nsen i useřqi \add ad iřin\add* n nnuqart.  
\v 12 Di tiru n řemrah, ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb, \add ad din iřint\add* řizarat n xemsin n iɣaǧen \add di tuzzeggart\add* ak-d ɛecra n ipilaren nsent d ɛecra n tyarsawin nsen.  
\v 13 Tiru n řemraḥ ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq, zi manis dd-tneqqar tfuct, \add ad tiři\add* xemsin \add iɣaǧen\add*.  
\v 14 Řizarat ɣar \add yijj\add* n uɣezdis n zzat \add ad iřint\add* xemmesṭac n iɣaǧen \add di tuzzeggart\add*, ak-d třata n ipilaren nsent d třata n tyarsawin nsen.  
\v 15 Ɣar uɣezdis n zzat nneɣni \add ad din iřint ɛawed\add* řizarat n xemmesṭac n iɣaǧen \add di tuzzeggart\add* ak-d třata n ipilaren nsent d třata n tyarsawin nsen.  
\v 16 Ɣar wadaf n řemraḥ \add ad din yiři\add* ijj n arwaq n ɛicrin n iɣaǧen, \add ggin t\add* s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden, ijj n umudi n uxeyyaḍ, ak-d arebɛa n ipilaren nnes d arebɛa n tyarsawin nsen.  
\v 17 Marra ipilaren i d as dd-innḍen i řemraḥ \add ad iřin\add* s iqeḍban n nnuqart i useřqi uca tisennarin nsen \add ad iřint\add* n nnuqart d tyarsawin nsen n nnḥas.  
\v 18 Tuzzeggart n řemraḥ \add ad tiři\add* mya n iɣaǧen u tiru \add ad tiři\add* xemsin n iɣaǧen d xemsin \add ɛawed\add* uca řuɛřa \add ad yiři\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen, \add marra\add* s řeqṭen azdad imuden uca tyarsawin nsen \add ad iřint\add* n nnḥas.   
\m
\v 19 Marra \bd řeqcuɛ n Tzeddiɣt\bd* i iǧan i marra tasexxart nnes uřa d marra řewtad nnes d marra řewtad n řemraḥ \add ad iřin\add* n nnḥas. *   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Ad tumured ayt n Israil, ḥima ad ac dd-awyen \bd zzect teṣfa teddez zi zzitun i tfawt\bd*, ḥima ad tareɣ tfawt řebda. \x ◘ \xo 27:20 \xt Lawi 24:2\x*  
\v 21 Harun d warraw nnes ad ḥḍan man aya zi ǧiřet ař ṣṣbeḥ zzat i wudem n SIDI deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar zzat i uřeḥḥaf i iǧan zzat i Cchadet. D man aya ad yiři d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda \add nni ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwaḥḍa\add* zi jjihet n ayt n Israil di \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 28
\m
\v 1 “Uca cek ad ɣarek dd-tessqarrbed \bd Harun, umac, d warraw nnes akides\bd* zi řwesṭ n ayt n Israil, ḥima \bd ad ayi ɛebden am yikehhanen\bd*, Harun, Nadab, Abihu, Aliɛazar d Itamar, zeg warraw n Harun. \x ◘ \xo 28:1 \xt Ɛbr. 5:4\x*   
\m
\v 2 Ad tegged \bd arruḍ iqeddsen i Harun, umac\bd*, ad \add as\add* yiři i uɛuǧi d telwizt.  
\v 3 Ad tessiwřed ɣar marra inni iǧan d imiɣisen n wuř, inni ccureɣ s arruḥ n tiɣit, \add maḥend\add* ad ggen arruḍ i Harun, ḥima ad as ssqeddsen d akehhan i Necc.  
\v 4 Ina d arruḍ i ɣa ggen: \bd ict n tejmect d ijj n upalṭu d ijj n useřham d ict tcamir imuden \+bdit am\+bdit* ijj n ureqqam n ufennan, d ict n areẓẓet d ict n tḥezzamt\bd*. Ad ggen arruḍ iqeddsen i Harun, umac, u i warraw nnes, ḥima ad ayi sexxaren am ukehhan.  
\v 5 Nitni ad ksin \add ifiřan n\add* wureɣ d \add afiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d řeqṭen azdad,  
\v 6 uca ad ggen apalṭu s \add ifiřan n\add* wureɣ u s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden, \add ad yiři\add* \add am\add* řxedmet n ufennan. \x ◘ \xo 28:6 \xt Uf. 39:2\x*  
\v 7 Ad ɣares yiři tnayen n tɣarḍin immseřsaqen ɣar tnayen n ṭṭrufa nnes i zi ɣa ittwassmun \add upalṭu\add*.  
\v 8 Taḥezzamt izewwqen, wenni iǧan x upalṭu nnes n ukehhan, ad zzayes tᵉttwagg d icten akides, s \add ifiřan n\add* wureɣ u s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden.  
\v 9 Ad teksid tnayen n iẓra n uniks uca ad xasen tneqced ismawen n ayt n Israil.  
\v 10 Setta n ismawen x yijj n weẓru d setta n ismawen nneɣni x weẓru nneɣni ɛlaḥsab \add asettef n\add* wexřaq nsen.  
\v 11 \add D man aya\add* d ict n ṣṣenɛet n uneqqac n weẓru \add iɣřan\add*. Am ict n txadent n ucemmiɛ, \add ammu i\add* ɣa ttwaneqcen tnayen n yeẓra s ismawen n ayt n Israil. Ad asen tegged ticuyar n wureɣ i d as dd-innḍen.  
\v 12 Ad tegged iẓra nni x tɣarḍin n upalṭu, \add aqa aten d\add* iẓra n řidaret i ayt n Israil. Harun ad yarbu ismawen nsen i řidaret zzat i wudem n SIDI x tnayen tɣarḍin nnes.  
\v 13 Ad tegged ticuyar n wureɣ  
\v 14 uca \add ɛawed\add* tnayen n ssnaseř n wureɣ iṣfan. Ad ten tegged \add amecnaw\add* ifiřan, \add amecnaw\add* ict n řxedmet n umudi. Ad tcedded ssnaseř imuden ɣar tcuyar.   
\m
\v 15 Ad tegged \bd tajmect\bd* i řeḥkam. Ad tt tegged \add am\add* řxedmet n ufennan, am upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add*. Ad tt tegged s \add ifiřan n\add* wureɣ u s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden. \x ◘ \xo 28:15 \xt Uf. 39:8\x*  
\v 16 \add Tajmect\add* ad \add tiři\add* s arebɛa n tɣemmura, tᵉttwaḍfeṣ. Tuzzeggart nnes ad tiři d ijj n wezyen n uɣiř, u tiru nnes d ijj n wezyen n uɣiř.  
\v 17 Ad xas tegged iẓra, arebɛa n řeṣfuf n iẓra. Ijj n ṣṣef \add ad yiři s\add* yijj n řeɛqiq d azeggwaɣ d ict n tyaqut d ict n smaraxt. \add Wa\add* d ṣṣef amezwaru.  
\v 18 Ṣṣef wiss tnayen \add ad yiři s\add* yijj n karbunkel d yijj n ṣaffir aziza d yijj n diamanti.  
\v 19 Ṣṣef wiss třata \add ad yiři s\add* yijj n \add weẓru n\add* yasintu d yijj n axat d yijj n umatist.  
\v 20 U ṣṣef wiss arebɛa \add ad yiři s\add* yict n texrisulit d yijj n uniks d yijj n yaspis. Ina ad ttwaṭṭfen deg wureɣ di tcuyar nsen.  
\v 21 Iẓra ad xasen iřin ismawen n ayt n Israil, tenɛac \add n yeẓra\add* ɛlaḥsab ismawen nsen, s ineqqacen n txadent n ucemmiɛ, kuř \add aneqqic\add* ɛlaḥsab isem nnes i d as dd-yusin. Aqa aten i tenɛac n tqebbař.  
\v 22 Ad tegged ssnaseř x tejmect, ifiřan imuden n wureɣ iṣfan.  
\v 23 Ad tegged tnayen n texrazin n wureɣ ɣar tejmect uca ad tcedded tnayen n texrazin nni ɣar tnayen n ṭṭrufa n tejmect.  
\v 24 Ad tcedded tnayen n ssnaseř n wureɣ imuden ɣar tnayen n texrazin ɣar řeḍruf n tejmect.  
\v 25 Ad tcedded tnayen n ixfawen n tnayen n \add ssnaseř\add* imuden ɣar tnayen n tcuyar uca ad tent tcedded ɣar tɣarḍin \add i iǧan\add* ɣar uɣezdis n zzat n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add*.  
\v 26 Ad tegged \add ɛawed\add* tnayen n texrazin n wureɣ uca ad tent tegged ɣar tnayen n ixfawen n tejmect \add ɣar swadday\add*, x tma nsen \add nni iǧan\add* ɣar upalṭu, ɣar daxeř.  
\v 27 Ad tegged tnayen n texrazin n wureɣ, tinni i ɣa tcedned x tnayen n tɣarḍin n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add*, swadday, ɣar zzat, qibač i useřqi nnes ɣar sennej i tḥezzamt izewwqen n upalṭu.  
\v 28 Ad tessmuned tajmect s texrazin nnes ɣar texrazin n upalṭu ak-d ijj n ufiřu imuden adeḥmi, maḥend ad tiři \add tejmect\add* sennej i tḥezzamt izewwqen n upalṭu uca war tᵉttbeṭṭi tejmect x upalṭu.  
\v 29 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa yawi Harun ismawen n ayt n Israil di tejmect n řeḥkam x wuř nnes x minni i ɣa yadef ɣar Uqeddas, \add ařami i ɣa qqimen\add* i řidaret zzat i wudem n SIDI i řebda.  
\v 30 Ad tessarsed \add iẓra n\add* ‘Urim’ d ‘Tummim’ di tejmect n řeḥkam, \add maḥend\add* ad iřin x wuř n Harun x minni i ɣa yadef zzat i wudem n SIDI. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa yarbu Harun řebda řeḥkam n ayt n Israil x wuř nnes zzat i wudem n SIDI.   
\m
\v 31 Ad tegged \bd aseřham\bd* n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* marra zeg \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi. \x ◘ \xo 28:31 \xt Uf. 39:22\x*  
\v 32 Ad yiři warzam i uzeǧif nnes di řwesṭ nnes. Ɣar tma n warzam ad din tiři ict n tma imuden, tenni i ɣa yiřin am warzam \add i yiri\add* deg ijj n warruḍ n wuzzař n uɛeskari, war tᵉttcarrig. \f ◼ \fr 28:32 \ft \+fk arzam\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘aqemmum’.\f*  
\v 33 Ɣar tmuwwa nnes ad tegged tiremmanin n \add ifiřan\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen, ɣar tmuwwa nnes i d as dd-innḍen, u jar asent \add ad tegged\add* nnwaqes n wureɣ i d as dd-innḍen.  
\v 34 Ijj awarni i wenneɣni, ijj n nnaqus n wureɣ d ict n tremmant, uca \add ɛawed\add* ijj awarni i wenneɣni, ijj n nnaqus n wureɣ d ict n tremmant, \add ammu i ɣa iřin\add* ɣar tmuwwa n useřham u deg wenneḍ nnes.  
\v 35 Harun ad t yarḍ xmi ittssexxar netta, \add ařami\add* i ɣa ittwaseř ddriz nnes x minni i ɣa yadef ɣar Zzawect Iqeddsen zzat i wudem n SIDI u xmi ɣa iffeɣ \add ɛawed\add*, \add ḥima\add* war ittmetti.   
\m
\v 36 Ad tegged ict n \bd \+bdit teřwiḥt s\+bdit* nnuwwar\bd* n wureɣ iṣfan uca ad xas tneqced \add awařen-a\add* am mammec neqqcen taxadent n ucemmiɛ: “AMQEDDAS i SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 28:36 \xt Uf. 39:30\x*  
\v 37 Ad tt tcedded ɣar yijj n ufiřu adeḥmi x areẓẓet. Ad tiři \add teřwiḥt\add* ɣar zzat n ureẓẓet.  
\v 38 Ad tiři \add teřwiḥt\add* x tenyart n Harun, \add ḥima\add* Harun ad yarbu řmuɛṣiyyet i iǧan di tmesřayin iqeddsen nni i ɣa ssqeddsen ayt n Israil ak-d marra tiwhibin n tmesřayin nsen iqeddsen. Ad tiři řebda x tenyart nnes, ḥima ad iřint \add tmesřayin nni\add* arḍant zzat i wudem n SIDI.   
\m
\v 39 Ad tegged \bd tcamir\bd* s řeqṭen azdad. Ad tegged \bd areẓẓet\bd* \add ɛawed\add* s řeqṭen azdad. \bd Taḥezzamt\bd* ad tt tegged \add am\add* ijj n umudi n uxeyyaḍ.”*   
\b  
\m
\v 40 “\bd I warraw n Harun\bd* ad tegged \bd tcamir\bd* u ad asen tegged \bd tiḥezzamin\bd* u ad asen tegged \bd ticuccay\bd*, maḥend ad \add asen\add* iřin i uɛuǧi d telwizt.  
\v 41 Ad tessyarḍed Harun, umac, d warraw nnes i kides iǧan, uca cek ad ten tdehned, ad ten třeqqmed u ad ten tessqeddsed, ḥima ad ayi xedmen am yikehhanen.  
\v 42 Egg asen \bd ssraweř n řeqṭen\bd*, ḥima ad dřen aysum n useḍḥi nsen. Ad iřin zi tejɛinna uca ad awḍen ɣar ifadden.  
\v 43 \add Ssřaweř nni\add* ad iřin x \add arrimet\add* n Harun d warraw nnes xmi ɣa yadfen ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar niɣ xmi dd ɣa qarrben ɣar uɛalṭar maḥend ad sexxaren di Zzawect Iqeddsen, \add ḥima\add* war dd-ttiwyen řmuɛṣiyyet uca ad mmten. Ta ad tiři d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i netta u i zzariɛet nnes awarni as.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 29
\m
\v 1 “D man aya i d asen ɣa tegged, ḥima ad ten tessqeddsed, maḥend ad ayi iřin d ikehhanen. Ksi ijj n ufunas - ameẓyan n ufunas - d tnayen n wacraren icnan qaɛ, \x ◘ \xo 29:1 \xt Lawi 8:2; 9:2\x*  
\v 2 u \add ɛawed\add* aɣrum břa antun d řemsemnat břa antun ixeǧḍen s zzect d teřfaf břa antun ttwadehnent s zzect, tinni i ɣa tegged \add marra\add* s waren azdad n yirden.  
\v 3 Ad tent tegged deg ict n tsuǧet uca ad tent tawyed di tsuǧet \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ufunas ameẓyan d tnayen n icarriyyen.  
\v 4 Ad dd-tessqarrbed Harun d warraw nnes ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar uca ad ten tessirded s waman.  
\v 5 Ad teksid arruḍ, ad tyarḍed Harun tcamir d useřḥam i upalṭu d upalṭu \add simant nnes\add* d tejmect uca ad as tbeysed s tḥezzamt izewwqen n upalṭu.  
\v 6 Ad tessarsed areẓẓet x uzeǧif nnes u x areẓẓet ad tegged ttaj iqeddsen \add n weɛzař\add*.  
\v 7 Ad teksid zzect i wedhan uca ad tt tzeǧɛed x uzeǧif nnes uca ad t tdehned. \x ◘ \xo 29:7 \xt Uf. 30:25\x*  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* ad tawyed iḥenjiren nnes, ad asen tyarḍed tcamirat.  
\v 9 Ad asen tbeysed s tḥezzamt, i Harun d warraw nnes, uca ad asen tarekkbed ticuccay. Ad ɣarsen tiři tukehhant ɛlaḥsab ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda. Ad tařeqqmed Harun d warraw nnes. \f ◼ \fr 29:9 \ft \+fk tukehhant\ft  - awař-a ixs ad yini ‘řxedmet n ukehhan’. \fk Ad tařeqqmed Harun d tarwa nnes.\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Ad teccured ifassen n Harun d tarwa nnes.’\f*   
\m
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* ad tawyed afunas ameẓyan zzat i \bd Uqiḍun n Umsagar\bd* u Harun d warraw nnes ad ssarsen ifassen nsen x uzeǧif n ufunas ameẓyan. \x ◘ \xo 29:10 \xt Lawi 1:3\x*  
\v 11 Ad tɣarṣed i ufunas ameẓyan zzat i wudem n SIDI, ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* ad teksid idammen n ufunas ameẓyan uca ad ten tegged s uḍaḍ nnec x waccawen n uɛalṭar uca ad tzeǧɛed marra idammen \add iqqimen\add* ɣar iḍaren n uɛalṭar. \f ◼ \fr 29:12 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iqiccawen’.\f*  
\v 13 Ad teksid \add ɛawed\add* marra tadunt nni idřin adan d min yuyřen ɣar tsa, d tnayen n tiẓẓař ak-d tadunt i xasent \add iǧan\add* uca ad tessbexxared aya x uɛalṭar. \f ◼ \fr 29:13 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’. Uřa di ayet 22.\f*  
\v 14 \add Maca\add* aysum n ufunas ameẓyan d yiřem nnes d umessař nnes ad ten tesscemḍed s tmessi barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, aqa d taɣarṣt n ddenb. \x ◘ \xo 29:14 \xt Lawi 4:12; Ɛbr. 13:11\x*   
\m
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* ad teksid ijj n ucarri uca Harun d warraw nnes ad ssarsen ifassen nsen x uzeǧif n icarri.  
\v 16 Ad tɣarṣed i icarri uca ad teksid idammen nnes, ad \add ten\add* tzeǧɛed x uɛalṭar zi marra iɣezdisen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 29:16 \xt Ɛbr. 9:12, 19\x*  
\v 17 Ad tebḍid icarri d iceǧiqen, ad tessirded adan nnes d icekrad nnes uca ad ten tegged x iceǧiqen nnes u x uzeǧif nnes.  
\v 18 Ad tessiɣed i icarri am ikmeř x uɛalṭar, aqa d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI, ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen, aqa d ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI.  
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* ad teksid icarri nneɣni uca Harun d warraw nnes ad ssarsen ifassen nsen x uzeǧif n icarri.   
\m
\v 20 Ad tɣarṣed i icarri uca ad teksid zeg idammen nnes uca ad tegged man aya x iɣes n umezzuɣ afusi n Harun u x iɣes n umezzuɣ afusi n warraw nnes u \add ɛawed\add* x uḍaḍ n yimez n ufus nsen afusi u x uḍaḍ n yimez n uḍar nsen afusi uca ad tzeǧɛed iḍammen \add iqqimen\add* x uɛalṭar zi kuř jjihet.  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* ad teksid zeg idammen nni iǧan x uɛalṭar u zi zzect i wedhan uca ad zzaysen trucced Harun d warruḍ nnes uca \add ad trucced ɛawed\add* arraw nnes d arruḍ n warraw nnes akides, ḥima ad yiři ittwaqeddes, netta d arruḍ nnes, uřa d tarwa nnes d arruḍ n tarwa nnes akides.  
\v 22 Ad teksid tadunt n icarri řa d tadunt ɣar unewwar řa tadunt nni idřin adan, uřa min yuyřen ɣar tsa d tnayen n tiẓẓař s tadunt i xasent iǧan d acekrud afusi, minzi wa d icarri i udeccen \add n ikehhanen\add*.  
\v 23 Ksi \add ɛawed\add* ict n tecnift n weɣrum d ict n temsemment n weɣrum \add ittwasswejden\add* s zzect d ict n teřfeft zi tsuǧet n weɣrum břa antun \add i iǧan\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 24 Sars man aya marra x ifassen n Harun u x ifassen n warraw nnes uca ad ten tessenhezzed zi ssa ɣar da \add am\add* ict n tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 25 \add Awarni as\add* ad tt teksid zeg ifassen nsen uca ad tt tessbexxared x uɛalṭar, x tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, \add ad tiři\add* d ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen zzat i wudem n SIDI. \add Aqa-tt\add* d ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI.  
\v 26 Ad teksid idmaren n icarri i udeccen n Harun uca ad ten tᵉssenhezzed zi ssa ɣar da \add am\add* ict n tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI. Tanita ad tiři d tasɣart nnec.  
\v 27 Ad tessqeddsed idmaren n tewhibt n wenhezzi i ittwanhezzen zi ssa ɣar da, uřa d ucekrud i ittwanhezzen zi ssa ɣar da d wenni ittwassgeɛɛden. Aqa-ten zeg icarri n udeccen, am zeg wenni i yeǧan i Harun am zeg wenni i yeǧan i warraw nnes.  
\v 28 Aya ad yiři i Harun d warraw nnes d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda zi jjihet n ayt n Israil, minzi d tawhibt n usgeɛɛed i teǧa. Ad tiři d ict n tewhibt i ɣa ssgeɛɛden ayt n Israil zi tɣarṣa nsen n řehna. Aqa d tawhibt nsen n usgeɛɛed i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 29:28 \xt Lawi 7:31,34; 10:14\x*   
\m
\v 29 Arruḍ iqeddsen n Harun ad yiři i warraw nnes awarni as, maḥend ad ten dehnen u ad ten ařeqmen dayes.  
\v 30 Man wen zeg iḥenjiren nnes \add i ɣa yiřin\add* d akehhan deg wemcan nnes uca ad yadef ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar, maḥend ad isexxar di Zzawect Iqeddsen, ad t yarḍ sebɛa n wussan.   
\m
\v 31 Ad teksid icarri i udeccen uca ad tᵉssengwed aysum nnes deg ijj n wemcan iqeddsen.  
\v 32 Harun d warraw nnes ad ccen aysum n icarri d weɣrum i iǧan di tsuǧet ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar. \x ◘ \xo 29:32 \xt Lawi 8:31; 24:9\x*  
\v 33 Ad ccen zi min zi ittwagg wesřaḥ, ḥima ad ten řeqqmen u ad ten ssqeddsen. \add Maca\add* ijj n ubarrani war zzayes ittett, minzi aqa d ict n řḥajjet d tamqeddest. \x ◘ \xo 29:33 \xt Lawi 10:14; Mt. 12:4\x*  
\v 34 Mařa iceṭṭ ca zeg weysum \add n tɣarṣa\add* i udeccen niɣ zeg weɣrum ař ṣṣbeḥ, ad tesscemḍed min iceṭṭen di tmessi. Ittxeṣṣa war t ittett ḥed, minzi d ict n řḥajjet iqeddsen \add i yeǧa\add*.   
\m
\v 35 Ammu i ɣa tegged ak-d Harun u ak-d warraw nnes, \add ad tegged\add* ɛlaḥsab marra min d ac weṣṣiɣ. Ad ten tařeqqmed sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 36 Kuř ass ad tesswejded afunas ameẓyan d taɣarṣt n ddenb i weṣřaḥ uca ad tekksed ddenb x uɛalṭar umi xas ɣa tessiwḍed aṣřaḥ, uca \add xenni\add* ad t tdehned, maḥend ad t tessqeddsed.  
\v 37 Sebɛa n wussan ad tegged aṣřaḥ x uɛalṭar uca ad t tessqeddsed, \add xenni\add* ad yiři d amqeddas qaɛ. Wenni i ɣa iḥadan aɛalṭar, ad yiři d amqeddas.  
\v 38 D man aya i ɣa tesswejded x uɛalṭar: tnayen n izmaren n ijj n useggʷas, kuř ass řebda. \x ◘ \xo 29:38 \xt Řxř. 28:3\x*  
\v 39 Ad tesswejded ijj n yezmar di ṣṣbeḥ u izmar nneɣni ad t tesswejded jar beddu n wezyen n wass ař dd-tewḍa tmeddit.  
\v 40 I yijj n yezmar \add ad teksid\add* ɛecra di tesɣart n ijj n ifa n waren azdad ixeǧḍen s zzect ddzen tt-i-dd \add zi zzitun\add*, u arebɛa di tesɣart n ijj n uhinu n binu d tawhibt n useyyeb. \f ◼ \fr 29:40 \ft \+fk ahinu\ft  - ijj n ‘uhinu’ dayes 6 ½ litru n waman niɣ n uceffay u n řeḥwayej nneɣni, u 6,5 litru ittawi-dd 1/6 ‘bath’. Ijj n ‘bath’ imun dayes xenni 6 n ‘uhinu’, ixs ad yini ɛřayen 40 litru.\f*  
\v 41 Ad tɣarṣed i yezmar nneɣni jar beddu n wezyen n wass ař dd-tewḍa tmeddit. Ad ɣares tarnid tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* am mammec tenni n ṣṣbeḥ u \add ɛawed\add* tawhibt nnes n useyyeb. Aqa d řefwaḥet ittfuḥen. \add Aqa\add* d tawhibt n tmessi i SIDI.  
\v 42 \add Ad tiři\add* d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ řebda di \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar zzat i wudem n SIDI, mani ɣa ssmuneɣ akidwem, maḥend ad kidek ssiwřeɣ din.  
\v 43 Ad mmsagareɣ din ak-d ayt n Israil, u \add Aqiḍun\add* ad ittwaqeddes s uɛuǧi inu.  
\v 44 Ad ssqeddseɣ Aqiḍun n Umsagar d uɛalṭar. Ad ssqeddseɣ \add ɛawed\add* Harun d warraw nnes, ḥima ad ayi iřin d ikehhanen.  
\v 45 Ad zedɣeɣ di řwesṭ n ayt n Israil, ad asen iřiɣ d AREBBI \x ◘ \xo 29:45 \xt Uf. 25:8; Lawi 26:12; Izhd. 78:60; Zak. 2:14; 2 Kur. 6:16; Asa. 21:3\x*  
\v 46 uca ad ssnen belli Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nsen, wenni ten issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, maḥend ad zedɣeɣ di řwesṭ nsen. Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nsen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 30
\m
\v 1 “Ad tegged \add ɛawed\add* \bd aɛalṭar n řebxur\bd*. Ad t tegged zeg ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya. \x ◘ \xo 30:1 \xt Uf. 37:25\x*  
\v 2 Tuzzeggart ad tiři d ijjen uɣiř, u tiru \add ɛawed\add* d ijjen uɣiř. Ad yiři \add uɛalṭar\add* s arebɛa n tɣemmura. Řuɛřa nnes ad yiři d tnayen n iɣaǧen u accawen nnes ad iřin d ijjen akides. \f ◼ \fr 30:2 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iqiccawen’. Uřa di ayet 3 d 10.\f*  
\v 3 Ad t tɣeǧfed s wureɣ iṣfan, udem nnes n sennej d iɣezdisen nnes i d as dd-innḍen d waccawen nnes. Ad as tegged ijj n zzwaq n wureɣ i d as dd-innḍen.  
\v 4 Ad as tegged tnayen n texrazin n wureɣ sadu zzwaq nnes. Ad tent tegged ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen nnes, ɣar tnayen n tɣemmar nnes. Ad iřint i iɛumad, ḥima ad zzaysen arbun \add aɛalṭar n řebxur\add*.  
\v 5 Ad tegged tnayen n iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* zeg ukeccuḍ n ukasiya uca ad ten tɣeǧfed s wureɣ.  
\v 6 Ad t tessarsed zzat i uřeḥḥaf i iǧan zzat i Ttabut n Cchadet, zzat i tqebbart n weṣřaḥ tenni iǧan x Cchadet, mani kik i ɣa mmsagareɣ.  
\v 7 Ad issbexxar Harun řebxur ittfuḥen kuř ṣṣbeḥ. \add Awarni řami\add* iɛdeř tiftiřin, ad issbexxar. \x ◘ \xo 30:7 \xt 1 Ṣm. 3:3\x*  
\v 8 Meřmi i ɣa issireɣ Harun tiftiřin jar beddu n wezyen n wass ař dd-tewḍa tmeddit, ad yejj řebxur ad ibexxar. \add Ad yiři\add* d ijj n řebxur i řebda zzat i wudem n SIDI i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem.  
\v 9 Kenniw war xas tessgeɛɛdem ca řebxur d aɣrib, niɣ taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ niɣ tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* u war xas ttzeǧaɛem tawhibt n useyyeb.  
\v 10 Harun ad igg aṣřaḥ x waccawen nnes ict n twařa deg useggʷas s idammen n tɣarṣa n ddenb i weṣřaḥ. Ad t isseṣřeḥ ict n twařa deg useggʷas i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem. \add Aqa-t\add* d amqeddas qaɛ i SIDI.”   
\m
\v 11 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 12 “Xmi ɣa teksid řqedd n ayt n Israil, \add řqedd n\add* yinni ittwaḥesben, \add xenni\add* nitni ad wcen, kuř ijj i yixef nnes, \bd ttaman n weṣřaḥ\bd* i SIDI ɣar useddi nsen, \add ḥima\add* war tᵉttiři jjriḥect jar asen x minni ten ɣa tḥesbed. \x ◘ \xo 30:12 \xt Řxř. 1:2\x*  
\v 13 D man aya i ɣa wcen nitni, kuř ijj zeg inni ɣa iẓwan ɣar yinni ittwaḥesben: azyen ciqlu ɛlaḥsab ciqlu n Zzawect Iqeddsen - ciqlu-ya d ɛicrin jira - azyen ciqlu-ya ad yiři d tawhibt n usgeɛɛed i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 30:13 \xt Lawi 27:25; Řxř. 3:47; Ḥiz. 45:12\x*  
\v 14 Kuř ijj zeg inni ɣa iẓwan ɣar yinni ittwaḥesben, zi ɛicrin iseggʷusa sennej, ad issgeɛɛed tawhibt i SIDI.  
\v 15 Bu-wagřa war ittic ktar u amezřuḍ war issenqis zeg wezyen ciqlu, xmi ɣa tessgeɛɛdem tawhibt n SIDI i weṣřaḥ n řeɛmur nwem.  
\v 16 Ad teksid nnuqart i weṣřaḥ n ayt n Israil uca ad tt tfarzed i tsexxart n Uqiḍun n Umsagar. Ad tiři d řidaret i ayt n Israil zzat i wudem n SIDI i weṣřaḥ n řeɛmur nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 30:16 \xt Uf. 38:25\x*   
\m
\v 17 Issiweř SIDi ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 18 “Ad tegged ɛawed \bd tbanyut n nnḥas\bd* i usird, ak-d uḍar n nnuqart nnes i x tt ɣa ssarsen, maḥend ad ssirden \add ixef nsen\add*. Ad tt tessarsed jar Uqiḍun n Umsagar d uɛalṭar uca ad dayes tegged aman,  
\v 19 maḥend Harun d warraw nnes ad zzayes ssirden ifassen nsen d iḍaren nsen.  
\v 20 Xmi ɣa yadfen ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar ad ssirden s waman \add ḥima\add* war ttmettin ca, uřa xmi dd ɣa qarrben ɣar uɛalṭar, maḥend ad sexxaren xmi ɣa ssbexxaren tawhibt n tmessi i SIDI.  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* ad ssirden ifassen nsen d iḍaren nsen ḥima war ttmettin ca. Man aya ad asen yiři d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda, i netta u i zzariɛet nnes, i \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen.”   
\m
\v 22 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 23 “Cek, ksi řexxu ɣarek řeɛṭur icnan aṭṭas: xems-mya \add ciqlu\add* n mirru yuzzřen ak-d řqedd n wezyen n manawenni, aqa-t d mitayen u-xemsin \add ciqlu\add* zi řqarfa ittfuḥen u mitayen u-xemsin \add ciqlu\add* zeg uɣanim uḥemmum ittfuḥen,  
\v 24 xemsa-mya \add ciqlu\add* n qassiya \add iwezznen\add* ɛlaḥsab ciqlu n Zzawect Iqeddsen, d ijj n uhinu n zzect n zzitun.  
\v 25 Egg zzaysen ict n \bd zzect tamqeddast i wedhan\bd*, ijj n řeɛṭur ixeǧḍen ɛlaḥsab ṣṣenɛet n uɛeṭṭar. Aya ad yiři d ict n zzect tamqeddest i wedhan.  
\v 26 S man aya ad tdehned Aqiḍun n Umsagar, Ttabut n Cchadet,  
\v 27 tazewḍa ak-d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d řqendiř ak-d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d uɛalṭar n řebxur,  
\v 28 d uɛalṭar n wecmaḍ ak-d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d tbanyut ak-d uḍar nnes.  
\v 29 Ad tessqeddsed marra aya, ḥima ad yiři d amqeddas qaɛ. Marra wi ɣa iḥadan zi man aya, ad ittwaqeddes.  
\v 30 Ad tdehned Harun d warraw nnes uca ad ten tessqeddsed, ḥima \add ad\add* ayi \add iřin\add* d ikehhanen.  
\v 31 Ad tessiwřed ak-d ayt n Israil uca ad tinid: ‘Ta ad tiři d ict n zzect tamqeddast i wedhan i Necc di \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem. \f ◼ \fr 30:31 \ft \+fk i Necc\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini ‘i AREBBI’.\f*  
\v 32 War iɛeddeř ad tt farrɣen x arrimet n bnadem, u mammec teǧa war zzayes tteggem učmas. Tamqeddast i teǧa uca ad tiři d tamqeddast i kenniw.  
\v 33 Wenni i ɣa isswejden s řebzar \add ict n zzect n wedhan\add* am tanita uca ad zzayes tmesḥed x yijj n ubarrani, ad ittwaqess zi řgens nnes.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 34 Inna SIDI i Musa:  
\m “Ksi i yixef nnec řebzar ittfuḥen: tuddimin n userɣaɣ d weqcur n tcejjart n řqarfa d ɣalba, řebzar ittfuḥen d jjawi iṣfan. \add Ad yiři\add* řqedd nnes am řqedd n wenneɣni.  
\v 35 Egg zzayes ijj n \bd řeɛṭur\bd*, ijj n uxeǧeḍ am tenni igga uɛeṭṭar: ittwameǧed, iṣfa, iqeddes.  
\v 36 Ḥri-dd zzayes taneɣda tazdadt uca sars \add ca\add* zzayes zzat i Cchadet deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar mani akidek ɣa msagareɣ. Ad awem tiři d tamqeddast qaɛ.  
\v 37 Řeɛtur nni i ɣa tegged, war t tteggem s uxeǧeḍ d ijjen akides i yixef nwem. Ad yiři d amqeddas i cek, \add ad yiři\add* i SIDI.  
\v 38 Wenni i iggin ca am wanita uca ad t icemm, ad ittwaqess zi řgens nnes.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 31
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Xzar, Necc řaɣiɣ-dd x Baṣaliyil, mmis n Uri, mmis n Ḥur, zi teqbič n Yahuda s yisem nnes. \x ◘ \xo 31:2 \xt Uf. 35:30; 1 Im. 2:20\x*  
\v 3 Ccureɣ t s Arruḥ n AREBBI, s tiɣit, s řeɛqeř, s tussna u s marra \add min ittxeṣṣan n\add* tzemmar n ṣṣnayeɛ, \x ◘ \xo 31:3 \xt Uf. 35:13; Ica. 11:2; 1 Kur. 12:8; Kul. 1:9\x*  
\v 4 ḥima ad ixemmem ireqqamen s lfenn, maḥend ad \add ten\add* tteggen s wureɣ d nnuqart d nnḥas,  
\v 5 u ḥima ad neqcen iẓra \add iɣřan\add* maḥend ad ten ggen \add di tcuyar nsen\add*, u ḥima ad neqcen akeccuḍ, ḥima \add ammu\add* i ɣa ggen marra řxedmet.  
\v 6 Aqa Necc ggiɣ akides Ahuliyab, mmis n Axisamak, zi řaǧ n Dan. Deg wuř n marra \add inni ɣar iǧa\add* wuř d amiɣis, ggiɣ tiɣit. Nitni ad ggen marra min xef weṣṣiɣ:  
\v 7 Aqiḍun n Umsagar, Ttabut n Cchadet, taqebbart n weṣřaḥ nni xas iǧan, u marra řeqcuɛ n Uqiḍun:  
\v 8 tazewḍa ak-d marra řeqcuɛ nnes, d řqendiř iṣfan s marra řeqcuɛ nnes d uɛalṭar n řebxur,  
\v 9 aɛalṭar n wecmaḍ ak-d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d tbanyut s uḍar nnes,  
\v 10 arruḍ n tsexxart d warruḍ iqeddsen n Harun, akehhan, d warruḍ n warraw nnes, maḥend ad sexxaren am ukehhan,  
\v 11 d zzect i wedhan, d řebxur ittfuḥen i Zzawect Iqeddsen. Ɛlaḥsab marra minzi cek umureɣ ad ggen \add marra\add* aya.”   
\b  
\m
\v 12 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 13 “Cek, siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, ini: ‘Ad teḥḍam \add ussan n\add* ssebt inu, minzi \add ssebt\add* d řeɛřamet jar ayi d kenniw, i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem, ḥima ad tessnem belli Necc d SIDI, wenni kenniw issqeddsen.  
\v 14 Ḥḍam \add ass n\add* ssebt, minzi iqeddes \add i iǧa\add* i kenniw! Wenni t ɣa issfesden, ad t nɣen nican, minzi man wen i dayes ɣa iggin ca n řxedmet, ad ittwaqḍeɛ zi řwesṭ n řgens nnes. \f ◼ \fr 31:14 \ft \+fk man wen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar nni’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 31:14 \xt Uf. 20:8; Aɛwd. 5:12; Ḥiz. 20:12\x*  
\v 15 Setta n wussan ad tegged řxedmet uca deg wass wiss sebɛa ad yiři d ssebt, arraḥet tmun, tqeddes i teǧa i SIDI! Kuř ijj, wenni iggin \add ca n\add* řxedmet deg wass n ssebt, ad t nɣen nican.  
\v 16 Ayt n Israil ad ḥḍan \add ass n\add* ssebt, ad ḥḍan ssebt di \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen \add am\add* ijj n Řɛahd i řebda.  
\v 17 \add Ad tiři\add* d ict n řeɛřamet jar ayi d ayt n Israil, minzi di setta n wussan igga SIDI ajenna d temmurt u deg wass wiss sebɛa yareyyeḥ, yarra nnefs.” \x ◘ \xo 31:17 \xt Amz. 1:31; 2:2, 3; Uf. 20:11\x*  
\v 18 \add Řami\add* ikemmeř \add SIDI\add* awař i kides issiwřen x wedrar n Sina, iwca i Musa tnayen n teřwiḥin n Cchadet. \add Tuɣa\add* tiřwiḥin nni zeg weẓru, ttwarint s uḍaḍ n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 31:18 \xt Uf. 32:16\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 32
\s1 Aɛejmi n wureɣ  
\m
\v 1 \add Řami\add* iẓra řgens belli Musa iɛeṭṭař, war dd-ihwi ɛad zeg wedrar, inneyru-dd řgens ɣar Harun, nnan as: “Kkar, egg aneɣ irebbiten, inni i ɣa yuyuren zzatneɣ, minzi Musa aya, aryaz nni d aneɣ dd-issuffɣen zi Miṣra, war nessin min t yuɣin.” \x ◘ \xo 32:1 \xt Řex. 7:40\x*  
\v 2 Harun inna asen: “Qeřɛem tixrazin n wureɣ nni iǧan deg imejjan n temɣarin nwem u n iḥenjiren nwem uřa n yessitwem, awyem \add tent-i-dd\add* ɣari.”  
\v 3 Ikkes marra řgens tixrazin n wureɣ nni iǧan deg imejjan nsen uca iwyen as tent-i-dd ɣar Harun.  
\v 4 Netta iksi \add tent\add* zeg ifassen nsen uca icekkeř i-tent s imeydi, igga zzaysent ijj n uɛejmi n ufessi. \add Řexdenni\add* nnan: “\add A\add* Israil, wa d arebbi nnec, wenni cek dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra.” \f ◼ \fr 32:4 \ft \+fk aɛejmi\ft  - niɣ ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*  
\v 5 \add Řami\add* iẓra Harun aya, ibna ijj n uɛalṭar zzat i \add uɛejmi\add* uca iřaɣa Harun, inna: “Tiwecca \add ad yiři\add* d řɛid i SIDI.”  
\v 6 Tiwecca nnes kkaren zic uca ssbexxaren tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ uca qeddmen \add akidsent\add* \add ɛawed\add* tiɣarṣa n řehna. \add Xenni\add* iqqim řgens, icca, iswa, ikkar, maḥend ad yegg řefrayej. \x ◘ \xo 32:6 \xt 1 Kur. 10:7\x*   
\m
\v 7 \add Xas uca\add* issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa: “Uyur, hwa, minzi řgens nnec, wenni dd-tessuffɣed zi temmurt n Miṣra, aqa igga min war iḥřin. \x ◘ \xo 32:7 \xt Aɛwd. 32:5\x*  
\v 8 Aqa ffɣen deɣya x webrid nni x ten weṣṣiɣ. Ggin ijj n uɛejmi n ufessi i yixef nsen uca bendqen as, qeddmen as tiɣarṣa uca nnan: ‘A Israil, wanita d arebbi nnec, wenni cek dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra.’” \x ◘ \xo 32:8 \xt 1 Ij. 12:28\x*  
\v 9 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Necc ẓriɣ řgens-a, xzar, aqa-t d ijj n řgens iqseḥ! \x ◘ \xo 32:9 \xt Uf. 33:3; Aɛwd. 9:6, 13; Ica. 48:4; Irm. 5:3; Ḥuc. 4:16\x*  
\v 10 Řexxu ejj ayi ad raḥeɣ, ad areɣ aɣḍab inu xasen uca ad ten teḥḥiɣ, u Necc ad cek arreɣ d ijj n řgens imɣar.”   
\m
\v 11 \add Maca\add* Musa izawg zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, inna: “\add A\add* SIDI, mayemmi ɣa yareɣ weɣḍab nnec x řgens nnec, wenni dd-tessuffɣed zi temmurt n Miṣra s yijj n jjehd imɣar u s ufus ijehden? \x ◘ \xo 32:11 \xt Izhd. 106:21\x*  
\v 12 Mayemmi ssawařen Imiṣriyyen jar asen, qqaren: ‘Netta issuffeɣ i-ten s nneyyet taɛeffant, maḥend ad ten ineɣ x idurar u maḥend ad ten iteḥḥa zeg wudem n temmurt?’ Dweř x řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnec uca ndem x tuɛeffna \add i texsed ad tarred\add* x řgens nnec. \x ◘ \xo 32:12 \xt Řxř. 14:13-19. \x*  
\v 13 Fekkar di Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Israil, imsexxaren nnec, inni umi tejjuǧed s Yixef nnec u tessiwřed akidsen: ‘Necc ad arniɣ zzariɛet nwem am yitran n ujenna uca ad wceɣ marra tammurt-a i xef ssiwřeɣ i zzariɛet nnec uca nitni ad tt ṭṭfen d ict n řwart i řebda.” \x ◘ \xo 32:13 \xt Amz. 12:7; 13:15; 15:18; 26:4; 28:13; Aɛwd. 34:4\x*   
\m
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* indem SIDI x tuɛeffna i tuɣa inna ad tt yegg x řgens nnes.  
\v 15 Uca idweř-dd Musa, ihwa-dd zeg wedrar s tnayen n teřwiḥin n Cchadet deg ufus nnes. Tiřwiḥin-a ttwarint x tnayen n iɣezdisen nsent: ttwarint x yijj n uɣezdis u x uɣezdis nneɣni.  
\v 16 Tiřwiḥin tuɣa atent d řxedmet n AREBBI uca tira nni ineqcen di teřwiḥin d tira n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 32:16 \xt Uf. 31:18; Aɛwd. 9:10\x*  
\v 17 Isřa Yacuwa i řḥess n řgens isɣuyyu uca inna i Musa: “\add Aqa da\add*, řḥess n umenɣi di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.”  
\v 18 \add Maca\add* netta inna: “War iǧi d řḥess n usřewřiw ɣar řeɣřeb niɣ d řḥess n usɣuyyi ɣar txessart, maca min ttesřiɣ d řḥess n iɣuyyan war iḥřin.”  
\v 19 Uca imsar, am dd-ireḥḥeg ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar uca iẓra aɛejmi d ccḍiḥ \add s nnubtat\add*, yarɣa weɣḍab n Musa uca inḍar tiřwiḥin zeg ifassen nnes, yarẓa i-tent ɣar iḍaren n wedrar. \x ◘ \xo 32:19 \xt Aɛwd. 9:17\x*  
\v 20 Iṭṭef uɛejmi nni ggin, isscemḍ i-t di tmessi, ařami idweř d iɣɣeḍ uca izzuzar i-t x wudem n waman uca yarra ayt n Israil ad \add t\add* swen. \x ◘ \xo 32:20 \xt Aɛwd. 9:21\x*  
\v 21 Inna Musa i Harun: “Min zzayek igga řgens-a ařami d as dd-tiwyed ijj n ddenb d ameqqran aṭṭas?”  
\v 22 Harun inna: “War yareqq weɣḍab n sidi inu! Cek tessned řgens-a, aqa-t di řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 32:22 \xt 1 Yḥ. 5:19\x*  
\v 23 Nnan ayi: ‘Egg aneɣ irebbiten nni ɣa yuyuren zzat i uɣembub nneɣ, minzi Musa wanita, aryaz wenni d aneɣ dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, war nessin min t yuɣin.’  
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ asen: ‘Wi ɣar iǧa ureɣ, ad \add t-i-dd-\add*ikkes, uca ad ayi t yewc!’ Uca nḍareɣ t di tmessi uca iffeɣ-dd uɛejmi-ya.”   
\m
\v 25 \add Umi\add* iẓra Musa, aqa řgens idweř d imfelles, minzi Harun ijja afelles \add nsen\add* ad idweř d taḍeḥḥact jar řɛedyan nsen,  
\v 26 ibedd Musa ɣar wadaf n řmargeḥ, inna: “Man wen i iǧan i SIDI, \add as-dd da\add* ɣari!” Uca munen-dd ɣares marra iḥenjiren n Lawi.  
\v 27 Inna asen: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil! Sarsem kuř ijj ssif nnes x tmeṣṣaḍt nnes, ɛdum uca ɛeqbem x řmargeḥ zeg wadaf ɣar wadaf \add nneɣni\add* uca ad ineɣ kuř ijj umas d kuř ijj umeddukkeř nnes d kuř ijj jjar nnes!”  
\v 28 Tarwa n Lawi ggin ɛlaḥsab awař n Musa. Deg wass nni wḍan ɛřaḥař teřt-ařaf n yeryazen n řgens.  
\v 29 Musa inna: “Ksim ifassen nwem ass-a ɣar SIDI, kuř ijj x mmis u x umas. Meɛlik ufiɣ Netta ad ibarek i kenniw \add ammu\add* ass-a!”   
\m
\v 30 Tiwecca nnes inna Musa i řgens: “Kenniw teggim ijj n ddenb imɣar. \add Ɛad\add* necc ad ařyeɣ řexxu ɣar SIDI, balak ad ufiɣ aṣřaḥ x ddenb nwem.”  
\v 31 Idweř-dd Musa ɣar SIDI uca inna \add as\add*: “\add Wayyaw\add*, řgens-a igga ijj n ddenb imɣar, minzi ggin ijj n arebbi n wureɣ i yixef nsen.  
\v 32 Řexxu, ɣfar \add asen\add* i ddenb nsen! Niɣ mḥa ayi zeg wedlis nnec ittwannḍen nni turid.”  
\v 33 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Wenni xafi ixḍan, d wa i ɣa mḥiɣ zeg wedlis inu ittwannḍen.  
\v 34 Ruḥ řexxu, awi řgens-a ɣar mani d ac nniɣ. Aqa lmalak inu ad iraḥ zzat nnec! Deg wass n uxeǧeṣ inu ad asen xeǧṣeɣ ddnub nsen!”  
\v 35 \add Ammu i\add* iwta SIDI řgens, minzi ggin aɛejmi nni igga Harun.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 33
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa: “Ruḥ, geɛɛed ssa, cek d řgens nni dd-tessuffɣed zi temmurt n Miṣra, ɣar temmurt nni x jjuǧeɣ i Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub, nniɣ: ‘I zzariɛet nnec ad tt wceɣ!’ \x ◘ \xo 33:1 \xt Amz. 12:7; 26:4; 28:13\x*  
\v 2 Necc ad ssekkeɣ zzat i uɣembub nnec lmalak, uca ad aẓẓřeɣ x ayt n Kenɛan d Imuriyyen d Iḥittiyyen d Ifiriziyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyibusiyyen  
\v 3 \add deg webrid nwem\add* ɣar ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment. Necc \add s imant inu\add* war ttgiɛɛideɣ akidwem, ḥima war kenniw tᵉtteḥḥiɣ deg webrid, minzi kenniw d ijj n řgens iqseḥ.” \x ◘ \xo 33:3 \xt Uf. 32:9; Aɛwd. 9:13\x*  
\v 4 Umi isřa řgens awař-a aɛeffan, ceḍnen uca uřa d ijj igga \add ɛad\add* řehzuṭ nnes.  
\v 5 Aqa inna SIDI i Musa: “Ini i ayt n Israil: ‘Kenniw d ijj n řgens iqseḥ. Mařa geɛɛdeɣ jar awem mɣir ijj n wermac, ad kenniw teḥḥiɣ. \add Xenni\add* řexxu kksem řehzuṭ nwem, aqa Necc ad ssneɣ min d ac ɣa ggeɣ.’”  
\v 6 Kksen ayt n Israil řehzuṭ nsen zeg wedrar n Hurib.   
\m
\v 7 Iksi Musa Aqiḍun uca iwta \add Aqiḍun\add* barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, iggʷej aṭṭas x řmargeḥ, uca iřaɣa as ‘Aqiḍun n Umsagar’. Kuř ijj wenni tuɣa yarezzun SIDI, iffeɣ ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar, wenni iǧan barra i řmargeḥ.  
\v 8 Umi iffeɣ Musa ɣar Uqiḍun, ikkar marra řgens, bedden barra, kuř ijj ɣar wadaf n uqiḍun nnes, uca nitni xzaren ɣares am tiṭṭawin nsen ḍeffaren Musa ařami yudef ɣar Uqiḍun.  
\v 9 Umi yudef Musa ɣar Uqiḍun, aqa aqellij n useynu ihwa, ibedd ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun uca Netta issiweř ak-d Musa.  
\v 10 Uca marra řgens iẓra aqellij n useynu ibedd ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun, \add xenni\add* ikkar marra řgens uca ibendeq kuř ijj ɣar wadaf n uqiḍun nnes.   
\m
\v 11 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa aɣembub deg uɣembub, am mammec issiweř bnadem ak-d umeddukkeř nnes. Xenni iɛqeb-dd ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, \add maca\add* amsexxar nnes Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, \add wenni ɛad d\add* aḥudri, ɛemmarṣ war ibeɛɛed x řwesṭ n Uqiḍun.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aɛuǧi n SIDI  
\m
\v 12 Inna Musa i SIDI: “Xzar, Cek tennid ayi: ‘Ndeh řgens-a!’, maca Cek war d ayi tessecned wi kidi i ɣa tessekked. Cek tennid: ‘Necc ssneɣ cek s yisem nnec!’ uřa: ‘Tufid arḍa di tiṭṭawin inu!’  
\v 13 Řexxu xenni, mařa ufiɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, zawgeɣ Cek ad ayi tessecned abrid nnec, ḥima ad Cek ssneɣ, maḥend ad afeɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec. Xzar, cceɛb-a d řgens nnec!”  
\v 14 Inna: “\add Lmalak n\add* wudem inu ad yuyur \add akidek\add* u Necc ad cek ssareyyḥeɣ.”  
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd xas: “Mařa udem nnec war \add kidneɣ\add* ittriḥ, war ttejji \add xenni\add* ad ngeɛɛed ssa!  
\v 16 Mammec ɣa ssnen belli aqa ufiɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, necc d řgens nnec? Ma war iǧi minzi Cek truḥed akidneɣ, aqa neccin, necc d řgens nnec, nfarrez x kuř řgens i iǧan x wudem n temmurt?” \x ◘ \xo 33:16 \xt Aɛwd. 4:7\x*  
\v 17 Inna SIDI i Musa: “\add Ɛawed\add* ad ggeɣ awař-a i tennid umi tufid arḍa di tiṭṭawin inu uca ssneɣ cek s yisem \add nnec\add*.”   
\m
\v 18 \add Xas uca\add* inna \add Musa\add*: “Zawgeɣ Cek, scen ayi aɛuǧi nnec!”  
\v 19 Inna: “Necc ad sseɛduɣ marra tcuni inu zzatek uca ad ɛeyydeɣ Isem n SIDI zzat i uɣembub nnec uca ad ḥinneɣ x wi ɣa ḥinneɣ, ad areḥmeɣ x wi ɣa areḥmeɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 33:19 \xt Rum. 9:15\x*  
\v 20 Inna \add ɛawed\add*: “Cek war tzemmared ad tẓared udem inu, minzi war d ayi iẓarr bnadem uca ad iqqim iddar.”  
\v 21 \add Xas uca\add* inna SIDI: “Xzar, zzat inu amcan \add mani\add* ɣa tbedded x teṣḍart.  
\v 22 Xmi ɣa iɛdu uɛuǧi inu, ad cek ggeɣ deg ijj n ufeǧiq n teṣḍart uca ad cek dřeɣ s třeqqa n ufus inu ař dd-ẓwiɣ.  
\v 23 U xmi ɣa kkseɣ afus inu, \add xenni\add* ad ayi tẓared zi ḍeffar, \add maca\add* war tẓarred udem inu!”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 34
\s1 Tnayen n teřwiḥin n jdid n weẓru  
\m
\v 1 SIDI inna i Musa: “Qess i yixef nnec tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru am tmezwura, uca Necc ad ariɣ x teřwiḥin nni awařen \add d ijjen\add* i tuɣa di teřwiḥin timezwura i tarẓid. \x ◘ \xo 34:1 \xt Aɛwd. 10:1\x*  
\v 2 Sewjed i ṣṣbeḥ uca geɛɛed di ṣṣbeḥ ɣar wedrar n Sina uca bedd din zzati x tqiccet n wedrar.  
\v 3 War iɛeddeř ad igeɛɛed uřa d ijj n bnadem akidek, niɣ ad iban ḥed deg wedrar am ikmeř. Uřa d uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin war zemmaren ad arewsen ṭṭarf i wedrar.” \f ◼ \fr 34:3 \ft \+fk bnadem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘aryaz’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 34:3 \xt Uf. 19:12, 13\x*   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* iqess tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru am tmezwura, uca ikkar Musa di ṣṣbeḥ zic uca igeɛɛed ɣar wedrar n Sina am mammec t iweṣṣa SIDI uca yiwi \add akis\add* deg ufus nnes tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru.   
\m
\v 5 Ihwa-dd SIDI deg useynu, ibedd akides din uca iřaɣa s Yisem n ‘SIDI’.  
\v 6 Iẓwa SIDI zzat i uɣembub nnes uca iɛeyyed: “SIDI, SIDI, Arebbi, d wenni iccuren s arreḥmet d teḥnunect, ɣares ttasiɛ n řxaḍar, dayes aṭṭas n tmexsiwt icewwaren d řaman, \x ◘ \xo 34:6 \xt Uf. 33:19\x*  
\v 7 d wenni iḥeṭṭan tamexsiwt \add nnes\add* icewwaren i řuřuf, d wenni iɣeffaren řmuɛṣiyyet d xeṭṭu d ddnub, d wenni war ittbarrin wenni itteggen ddenb, d wenni dd-yarezfen řmuɛṣiyyet n ibabaten deg iḥenjiren u deg iḥenjiren n iḥenjiren nsen ař \add jjiř\add* wiss třata d wiss arebɛa.” \x ◘ \xo 34:7 \xt Uf. 20:6; Řxř. 14:18; Aɛwd. 5:10; Izhd. 86:15; 103:8; 145:8; Irm. 32:18\x*   
\m
\v 8 Musa yuḍar \add s wudem nnes\add* ɣar temmurt uca ibendeq.  
\v 9 Inna: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, mařa ufiɣ xenni arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, ad yuyur xenni Sidi inu di řwesṭ nneɣ, minzi řgens iqseḥ. Ɣfar aneɣ řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ u qbeř aneɣ d řwart nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 34:9 \xt Lawi 25:38; Izhd. 28:9; 33:12; Zak. 2:16\x*  
\v 10 Netta inna: “Xzar, Necc ad ggeɣ Řɛahd. Zzat i marra řgens nnek, ad ggeɣ řeɛjayeb war ittwaggen ca di marra tammurt u jar marra řegnus, ařami marra řgens di řwesṭ nnes i zi teǧid, ad iẓar min igga SIDI, minzi min ɣa ggeɣ akidek ad isseggʷed aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 34:10 \xt Aɛwd. 5:2; Yac. 10:12, 13\x*  
\v 11 Ḥḍa min x cek weṣṣiɣ ass-a! Xzar, ad aẓẓřeɣ zzat i uɣembub nnec x Imuriyyen d ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥittiyyen d Ifiriziyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyibusiyyen.  
\v 12 Ɣarek ad tegged řɛahd ak-d umezduɣ n temmurt mani ɣa tadfed, ḥima netta war d ac ittiři d řfex di řwesṭ nnec. \x ◘ \xo 34:12 \xt Uf. 23:32; Řxř. 33:51; Aɛwd. 7:2\x*  
\v 13 Ittxeṣṣa awem ad tɣeḍřem iɛalṭaren nsen u ad tarẓam imayḍuten nsen \add iqeddsen\add* u ad thedmem tirebbin nsen n cwarti.  
\v 14 War ttbendiq i arebbi nneɣni, minzi SIDI, wenni umi qqaren ‘Anessam’, aqa-t d ijj n Arebbi ittasmen. \f ◼ \fr 34:14 \ft \+fk Anessam\ft  - Arebbi ixs aqa iwdan ad ɛebden Netta waha, minzi war dinni Arebbi yuɛřan x marra min iǧan am Netta. S uyenni nzemmar ad nini aqa Netta ittasem, Netta war ittexs ad t neɣdar, ad nuyur awarni i irebbiten nneɣni. Awař ‘anessam’ ixs ad yini ‘wenni ittasmen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 34:14 \xt Uf. 20:5\x*  
\v 15 Ɣarek ad tegged řɛahd ak-d imezdaɣ n temmurt, uca \add xenni\add* ad ssfesden nitni ixef nsen umi ɣa dewřen awarni i irebbiten nsen, ad qeddmen tiɣarṣa i irebbiten nsen, uca ad cek ɛarḍen i macca n tɣarṣa nsen.  
\v 16 Ad teksid tiḥenjirin nsen \add d timɣarin\add* i iḥenjiren nnec, \add maca\add* ad ssfesdent tḥenjirin nsen ixef nsent umi ɣa dewřen awarni i irebbiten nsent uca ad arrent iḥenjiren nnec ad dewřen awarni i irebbiten nsent. \x ◘ \xo 34:16 \xt 1 Ij. 11:2\x*   
\m
\v 17 War ttegg i yixef nnec irebbitten n ufessay. \f ◼ \fr 34:17 \ft \+fk irebbiten n ufessay\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘řexyarat ifesyen n irebbiten nsen’.\f*   
\m
\v 18 Ad teḥḍiḍ Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun: sebɛa n wussan ad tecced aɣrum břa antun, di řweqt ittwaggen deg uyur Abib, am mammec cek weṣṣiɣ, minzi deg uyur Abib i dd-teffɣed zi Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 34:18 \xt Uf. 12:15; 23:15\x*   
\m
\v 19 Marra min yarezzmen řemřawet \add d amezwaru\add* Inu, marra iwetman n řebhayem nnec i ɣa yarzzmen \add řemřawet d amezwaru\add*, am wenni n ufunas, am wenni n wuǧi. \x ◘ \xo 34:19 \xt Uf. 13:2; 22:29; Ḥiz. 44:30\x*  
\v 20 \add Mařa\add* amenzu n weɣyuř yarzem \add řemřawrat d amezwaru\add*, ad t tefdid s yijj zeg wuǧi. Mařa war t tefdid, ad as tarẓed iri. Ad tefdid marra imenza n iḥenjiren nnec.  
\m War iɛeddeř ad ḍharen s ifassen xwan zzat i wudem inu. \x ◘ \xo 34:20 \xt Uf. 13:13; 23:15; Aɛwd. 16:16\x*   
\m
\v 21 Setta n wussan ad txedmed, \add maca\add* deg wass wiss sebɛa ad tareyyḥed. Uřa di \add řweqt n\add* tyarza d tmeyra ad tareyyḥed. \x ◘ \xo 34:21 \xt Uf. 20:9\x*   
\m
\v 22 Ad tegged Řɛid n Simanat, aqa-t d \add Řɛid n\add* Tmenzut n tmeyra n yirden, uřa d Řɛid n Usmuni ɣar uneggar n useggʷas. \x ◘ \xo 34:22 \xt Uf. 23:16\x*   
\m
\v 23 Kuř aryaz ad dd-iban třata n twařawin deg useggʷas zzat i wudem n Sidi, SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, \x ◘ \xo 34:23 \xt Uf. 23:17; Aɛwd. 16:16\x*  
\v 24 minzi zzat i uɣembub nnec ad kkseɣ tasɣart n řwart x řegnus uca ad sswesɛeɣ iymiren nnec uca uřa d ijjen ad immeẓri \add ad yacar\add* tammurt nnec, xmi ɣa tgeɛɛded třata n twařawin deg useggʷas, ḥima ad tbaned zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.   
\m
\v 25 War ttqeddem idammen n tɣarṣt inu ak-d min ixemmaren. Taɣarṣt n Řɛid \add n Tɣarṣt\add* n Useɛdu war ttnusi ǧiřet ař ṣṣbeḥ. \x ◘ \xo 34:25 \xt Uf. 23:18\x*   
\m
\v 26 Tamezwarut n tmenzut n wudem n temmurt nnec ad \add tt\add*-i-dd-tawyed ɣar Taddart n SIDI, AREBBI nnec.  
\m War snenni iɣayḍ d ameẓyan s uɣi n yemmas.” \x ◘ \xo 34:26 \xt Uf. 23:19; Lawi 22:27; Aɛwd. 14:21\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 27 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Ari awařen-a i yixef nnec, minzi am mammec qqaren wawařen-a, aqa ggiɣ Řɛahd akidek u ak-d Israil.”  
\v 28 Uca \add Musa\add* tuɣa din ak-d SIDI arebɛin n wussan d arebɛin n ǧyaři. War icci aɣrum niɣ iswa aman. Uca yura di teřwiḥin awařen n Řɛahd, Ɛecra n Wawařen. \x ◘ \xo 34:28 \xt Uf. 24:1, 18; 31:18; 34:1; Aɛwd. 4:13; 9:9, 18; 10:2\x*   
\m
\v 29 \add Řami\add* dd-ihwa Musa zeg wedrar n Sina, am tuɣa tnayen n teřwiḥin n Cchadet deg ifassen n Musa am dd-ihwa zeg wedrar, imsar aqa war issin Musa belli tiřmect n uɣembub nnes tareqq minzi tuɣa akides issawař. \x ◘ \xo 34:29 \xt 2 Kur. 3:7\x*  
\v 30 Harun d marra ayt n Israil ṣewḍen ɣar Musa, u xzar, tiřmect n wudem nnes tuɣa tareqq, ggʷeden ad ɣares dd-qarrben.  
\v 31 Iřaɣa-dd xasen Musa uca idweř-dd Harun d marra řḥukkam n tmesmunt ɣares uca issiweř Musa akidsen.  
\v 32 Awarni as qarrben-dd marra ayt n Israil uca netta yumur i-ten marra min xef issiweř SIDI akides deg wedrar n Sina.  
\v 33 \add Řami\add* ikemmeř Musa awař nnes akidsen, igga ařeḥḥaf x wudem nnes. \x ◘ \xo 34:33 \xt 2 Kur. 3:7, 13\x*  
\v 34 \add Xmi\add* i ɣa yiři Musa zzat i wudem n SIDI ḥima ad kides issiweř, ikkes ařeḥḥaf, ař dd-iffeɣ \add ɛawed\add*. U řami dd-iffeɣ ɣar barra, issiweř ak-d ayt n Israil min d as yumur \add SIDI\add*.  
\v 35 Uca ẓrin ayt n Israil aɣembub n Musa, aqa tiřmect n wudem nnes tareqq, \add xenni\add* yarra Musa ařeḥḥaf x wudem nnes, ař dd-yudef \add ɛawed\add*, ḥima akides issiweř.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 35
\s1 Asewjed n řebni n Uqiḍun n Umsagar  
\m
\v 1 Musa issmun marra tamesmunt n ayt n Israil uca inna asen: “Ina d awařen nni yumur SIDI, ḥima ad ten teggem. \x ◘ \xo 35:1 \xt 34:32\x*  
\v 2 Setta n wussan ad tegged řxedmet u ass wiss sebɛa ad awem yiři iqeddes, aqa d ssebt, arraḥet tmun i SIDI. Kuř ijj, wenni dayes iggin \add ca n\add* řxedmet, ad ittwaneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 35:2 \xt Uf. 20:8; 31:15; Lawi 23:3; Aɛwd. 5:12; Lk. 13:14\x*  
\v 3 War tessruɣim kenniw timessi di marra tizeddiɣin nwem deg wass n ssebt.” \x ◘ \xo 35:3 \xt Uf. 16:23\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Issiweř Musa ak-d marra tamesmunt n ayt n Israil, inna: “D wa d min iweṣṣa SIDI, \add umi\add* inna: \f ◼ \fr 35:4 \ft \+fk D wa d min iweṣṣa SIDI\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘D wa d awař i yumuren SIDI’.\f*  
\v 5 ‘Ksim zi min ɣarwem ict n tewhibt n usgeɛɛed i SIDI. Kuř ijj, wenni umi yennurzem wuř nnes, ad tt yawi, aqa-tt d \bd tawhibt n usgeɛɛed\bd* i SIDI: ureɣ d nnuqart d nnḥas, \x ◘ \xo 35:5 \xt Uf. 25:2\x*  
\v 6 \add afiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d řeqṭen azdad d ccɛar n iɣayḍen, \x ◘ \xo 35:6 \xt Uf. 25:4\x*  
\v 7 iřmawen izeggʷaɣen n icarriyyen d iřmawen n ddenfiřat d ukeccuḍ n ukasiya, \x ◘ \xo 35:7 \xt Uf. 25:5\x*  
\v 8 zzect i tfawt, řeɛṭur i zzect n wedhan u i řebxur ittfuḥen, \x ◘ \xo 35:8 \xt Uf. 25:6\x*  
\v 9 iẓra n uniks d iẓra \add iɣřan nneɣni\add*, maḥend ad ten ggen x upalṭu u x tejmect. \x ◘ \xo 35:9 \xt Uf. 25:7; 28:17, 20\x*  
\v 10 Marra inni \add iǧan\add* jar awem s wuř d amiɣis, ad dd-asen ad ggen marra min yumur SIDI:  
\v 11 Tazeddiɣt, Aqiḍun nnes d tseqqaft nnes d tsennarin nnes d tfeřwin nnes d tḥenya nnes n uɛarreḍ d ipilaren nnes d tyarsawin nnes, \x ◘ \xo 35:11 \xt Uf. 26:26\x*  
\v 12 d Ttabut ak-d iɛumad nnes \add i tarebbut\add* d tqebbart n weṣřaḥ d uřeḥḥaf i dduri,  
\v 13 d tzewḍa ak-d iɛumad nnes \add i tarebbut\add* d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d weɣrum n wescan, \x ◘ \xo 35:13 \xt Uf. 25:23, 30\x*  
\v 14 d řqendiř i tfawt d řeqcuɛ nnes d teftiřin nnes d zzect i tfawt  
\v 15 d uɛalṭar n řebxur ak-d iɛumad nnes \add i tarebbut\add* d zzect i wedhan d řebxur ittfuḥen d arwaq n wadaf ɣar wadaf n Tzeddiɣt, \x ◘ \xo 35:15 \xt Uf. 26:36; 30:1; 31:11\x*  
\v 16 d uɛalṭar n wecmaḍ d tracca nnes n nnḥas d iɛumad nnes \add i tarebbut\add* d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d tbanyut s uḍar nnes, \x ◘ \xo 35:16 \xt Uf. 27:4; 30:18\x*  
\v 17 d řizarat n řemraḥ, ipilaren nnes ak-d tyarsawin nsen d arwaq i wadaf n řemraḥ, \x ◘ \xo 35:17 \xt Uf. 27:9, 16\x*  
\v 18 d řewtad n Tzeddiɣt d řewtad n řemraḥ d ifiřan nsen, \x ◘ \xo 35:18 \xt Uf. 27:19\x*  
\v 19 arruḍ i řxedmet deg Uqeddas, arruḍ iqeddsen n ukehhan Harun d warruḍ n warraw nnes, maḥend ad xedmen am yikehhanen.’”\x ◘ \xo 35:19 \xt Uf. 28; 31:10\x*  
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* ffɣen nitni, marra tamesmunt n ayt n Israil, \add ggʷejen\add* zi zzat n uɣembub n Musa.   
\m
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd kuř ijj, wenni umi inhezz wuř nnes, u marra wenni umi innurzem buḥbeř nnes, uca iwyen-dd nitni tawhibt n usgeɛɛed, \add tenni ssgeɛɛden nitni ɣar\add* SIDI, d tenni i ɣa yiřin i Uqiḍun n Umsagar u i tsexxart i dayes u i warruḍ iqeddsen.  
\v 22 \add Ammu\add* dd-usin iryazen jmiɛ ak-d temɣarin, marra inni umi innurzem wuř \add nsen\add* uca iwyen-dd timessakin d texrazin n umezzuɣ d tinzar d txudan \add n ucemmiɛ\add* d tseddiyin s wedmam n wureɣ d marra řeqcuɛ n wureɣ, \add wah,\add* kuř ijjen yiwi ict n tewhibt n wenhezzi n wureɣ i SIDI.  
\v 23 Marra wi ɣar ittwaf \add afiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen niɣ řeqṭen azdad niɣ ccɛar n iɣayḍen niɣ iřmawen izeggʷaɣen n icarriyyen niɣ iřmawen n ddenfiřat, iwyen-dd \add man aya\add*.  
\v 24 Marra wi issgeɛɛden tawhibt n nnuqart niɣ n nnḥas, iwyen tawhibt-a n usgeɛɛed ɣar SIDI, d marra wi ɣar ittwaf ukeccuḍ n ukasiya i marra řxedmet n tsexxart, iwyen \add man aya\add*.   
\m
\v 25 Marra timɣarin s wuř amiɣis ttqarḍcent s ifassen nsent uca nitenti iwyent-i-dd min qareḍcent: \add afiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d řeqṭen azdad. \f ◼ \fr 35:25 \ft \+fk s wuř amiɣis\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘amiɣis n wuř’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 35:25 \xt Awřn. 31:19\x*  
\v 26 Marra timɣarin nni umi inhezz wuř nsent s tiɣit, qareḍcent ccɛar n iɣayḍen.   
\m
\v 27 Řḥukkam iwyen-dd iẓra n uniks d iẓra \add iɣřan nneɣni\add*, ḥima ad ten ggen x upalṭu u x tejmect,  
\v 28 řeɛṭur d zzect i tfawt d zzect i wedhan u i řebxur ittfuḥen. \x ◘ \xo 35:28 \xt Uf. 25:6\x*   
\m
\v 29 Ayt n Israil wcin s řxaḍar i SIDI, marra iryazen d temɣarin, inni umi inhezz wuř nsen, maḥend ad wcen s řxaḍar i marra řxedmet nni yumur SIDI, ḥima ad tᵉttwagg s tsexxart n Musa.   
\m
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa i ayt n Israil: “Xzarem, SIDI iřaɣa-dd i \bd Baṣaliyil\bd*, mmis n Uri, mmis n Ḥur, zi řaǧ n Yahuda, s yisem \add nnes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 35:30 \xt Uf. 31:2\x*  
\v 31 Iccur i-t Arruḥ n AREBBI s tiɣit d řeɛqeř d tussna u s marra \add min ittxeṣṣan n\add* tzemmar n ṣṣnayeɛ \x ◘ \xo 35:31 \xt Uf. 31:3; Ica. 11:2; 1 Kur. 12:8; Kul. 1:9\x*  
\v 32 i uxemmem n \add ɛřam kuř\add* ireqqamen, ḥima ad ten yegg s wureɣ d nnuqart d nnḥas, \x ◘ \xo 35:32 \xt Uf. 31:4\x*  
\v 33 u i uneqqac n iẓra \add iɣřan\add* d usarsi nsen, u i uneqqac n ukeccuḍ u ḥima ad igg marra ireqqamen s lfenn. \x ◘ \xo 35:33 \xt Uf. 31:5\x*  
\v 34 Igga \add Arebbi\add* deg wuř nnes tawengit i useřmed, \add deg wuř\add* nnes u \add deg wuř n\add* \bd Ahuliyab\bd*, mmis n Axisamak, zi řaǧ n Dan.  
\v 35 Iccur i-ten s tiɣit n wuř, maḥend ad ggen marra řxedmet: \add řxedmet n\add* taneqqact d warcam d umudi s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d řeqṭen azdad uřa d \add řxedmet n\add* uxeyyaḍ.” Nitni ggin kuř řxedmet u ttsaqaren arcamen s lfenn. \x ◘ \xo 35:35 \xt Uf. 26:1\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 36
\m
\v 1 Baṣaliyil d Ahuliyab d kuř aryaz s wuř amiɣis i umi iwca SIDI tiɣit d řeɛqeř, maḥend ad ssnen mammec ɣa ggen marra řxedmet i tsexxart n Zzawect Iqeddsen, ggin marra am mammec ten yumur SIDI.  
\v 2 Musa iřaɣa-dd i Baṣaliyil d Ahuliyab d kuř aryaz s wuř amiɣis, umi igga SIDI tiɣit deg wuř nnes, uřa marra wenni umi inhezz wuř nnes, maḥend ad dd-yas ɣar řxedmet uca ad tt igg.   
\m
\v 3 Nitni ksin zi zzat n wudem n Musa marra tawhibt nni ssgeɛɛden ayt n Israil i řxedmet di ṭṭweɛ ni tsexxart n Zzawect Iqeddsen, maḥend ad ggen řxedmet nni. Uca \add aqa\add* ɛad ggin ad as dd-awyen kuř ṣṣbeḥ tiwhibin s řxaḍar.  
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* usin-dd marra iryazen imiɣisen, inni tuɣa iceɣřen x marra řxedmet n Zzawect Iqeddsen, ijj ijj dewřen-dd zi řxedmet nni ggin nitni, \f ◼ \fr 36:4 \ft \+fk ijj ijj\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘aryaz aryaz’.\f*  
\v 5 uca ssiwřen ak-d Musa, nnan: “Řgens yiwi-dd ktar zi min ittxeṣṣan di ṭṭweɛ n řxedmet nni i \add d aneɣ\add* yumur SIDI, ḥima ad tt negg.”  
\v 6 \add Xas uca\add* yumur Musa, ḥima ad barrḥen di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, ad inin: “War ttejji aryaz niɣ tamɣart ɛad ad yegg ca n řxedmet nni i ɣa issgeɛɛed d tawhibt i Zzawect Iqeddsen!” Ammu i issbedd \add Musa\add* řgens ad yawi \add ɛad ktar\add*,  
\v 7 minzi cfa timesřayin nni d iwyen i marra řxedmet i ɣa ggen, aqa tceṭṭ \add ɛad\add* ktar.   
\m
\v 8 Jar yinni ɣar tuɣa řxedmet, aqa marra imiɣisen n wuř ggin \bd Tazeddiɣt\bd* zi \bd ɛecra n tjartiřin n řeqṭen azdad imuden u s \+bdit ufiřu\+bdit* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen ak-d ikiruben\bd* nni \add xasent\add* igga am yijj n warcam n ufennan. \f ◼ \fr 36:8 \ft \+fk ikiruben\ft  - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*  
\v 9 Tuzzeggart n ict n tjartiřt tuɣa-tt tmenya u-ɛecrin n iɣaǧen u tiru n ict n tjartiřt tuɣa-t arebɛa n iɣaǧen u marra tijartiřin ɣarsent d řeɛbar d ijj. \x ◘ \xo 36:9 \xt Uf. 26:2\x*  
\v 10 Issmun xemsa n tjartiřin ict ak-d tenneɣni uca xemsa n tjartiřin issmun i-tent \add ɛawed\add* ict ak-d tenneɣnit. \f ◼ \fr 36:10 \ft \+fk ict ak-d tenneɣnit\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ict ɣar yict’.\f*  
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* igga tisarawin ideḥmaniyyen di tma n yict n tjartiřt ɣar ṭṭarf ɣar useřqi uca amenni i tent igga \add ɛawed\add* di tma n tjartiřt nneɣni ɣar ṭṭarf, ɣar \add mani iǧa\add* useřqi nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 36:11 \xt Uf. 26:4\x*  
\v 12 Igga xemsin n tsarawin x tma n yict n tjartiřt d xemsin n tsarawin ɣar ṭṭarf n tjartiřt \add nneɣni\add* ɣar useřqi nneɣni. Tisarawin ṭṭfent \add nican\add* ict di tenneɣnit. \x ◘ \xo 36:12 \xt Uf. 26:5, 10\x*  
\v 13 Igga \add ɛawed\add* xemsin n tsennarin n wureɣ uca issmun tijartiřin ict i tenneɣni s tsennarin uca \add ammu\add* tedweř Tzeddiɣt d ict. \x ◘ \xo 36:13 \xt Uf. 26:6\x*   
\m
\v 14 Igga \add ɛawed\add* \bd tijařtiřin n ccɛar n iɣayḍen\bd*, ad iřint d Aqiḍun x Tzeddiɣt. Igga ḥiṭac n tjartiřin.  
\v 15 Tuzzeggart n ict n tjartiřt tuɣa-tt třatin n iɣaǧen u tiru n ict n tjartiřt d arebɛa n iɣaǧen. Ḥiṭɛac n tjartiřin ɣarsent řeɛbar d ijj.  
\v 16 Netta issmun xemsa n tjartiřin weḥḥedsent u \add ɛawed\add* setta n tjartiřin weḥḥedsent.  
\v 17 Igga xemsin n tsarawin x tma n tjartiřt taneggarut ɣar \add ṭṭarf n\add* useřqi \add ak-d tenneɣni\add* uca igga \add ɛawed\add* xemsin n tsarawin x tma n tjartiřt ɣar \add ṭṭarf n\add* useřqi nneɣni.  
\v 18 Igga \add ɛawed\add* xemsin n tsennarin n nnḥas, ḥima ad issmun Aqiḍun maḥend ad t yarr d ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 36:18 \xt Uf. 26:11\x*   
\m
\v 19 Igga \add ɛawed\add* \bd ict n tseqqaft n iřmawen izeggʷaɣen n icarriyyen i Uqiḍun\bd* uca sennej i man aya \bd ict n tseqqaft n iřmawen n ddenfiřat\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 36:19 \xt Uf. 26:14\x*   
\m
\v 20 Igga \bd tifeřwin\bd* i Tzeddiɣt s ukeccuḍ n ukasiya nni ibedden \add nican\add*. \x ◘ \xo 36:20 \xt Uf. 26:15\x*  
\v 21 Tuzzeggart n \add ict n\add* tefřawt tuɣa-tt ɛecra n iɣaǧen u tiru n yict n tefřawt d ijj n uɣiř d wezyen. \x ◘ \xo 36:21 \xt Uf. 26:16\x*  
\v 22 Kuř tafřewt ɣares tnayen n iḍaren, inni issmeřqan ict ak-d tenneɣnit am twečmatin Ammu i igga s marra tifeřwin n Tzeddiɣt. \x ◘ \xo 36:22 \xt Uf. 26:17\x*  
\v 23 Igga tifeřwin i Tzeddiɣt, ɛicrin n tfeřwin ɣar jjihet n ljanub, ɣar yefus. \x ◘ \xo 36:23 \xt Uf. 26:18\x*  
\v 24 Igga ɛawed arebɛin n \bd tyarsawin n nnuqart\bd* sadu ɛicrin n tfeřwin, tnayen n tyarsawin sadu ict n tefřawt i tnayen n iḍaren nnes, uřa d tnayen n tyarsawin sadu tafřawt nneɣni i tnayen n iḍaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 36:24 \xt Uf. 26:19\x*  
\v 25 Igga \add ɛawed\add* ɛicrin n tfeřwin i uɣezdis nneɣni n Tzeddiɣt, ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal, \x ◘ \xo 36:25 \xt Uf. 26:20\x*  
\v 26 s arebɛin n tyarsawin nnes n nnuqart: tnayen n tyarsawin sadu ict n tefřawt d tnayen n tyarsawin sadu tafřawt nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 36:26 \xt Uf. 26:21\x*  
\v 27 I iɣezdisen n ḍeffar n Tzeddiɣt, ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb, igga setta n tfeřwin. \x ◘ \xo 36:27 \xt Uf. 26:22\x*  
\v 28 Igga tnayen n tfeřwin \add d tifeřwin\add* i tɣemmura n Tzeddiɣt ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen ɣar ḍeffar. \x ◘ \xo 36:28 \xt Uf. 26:23\x*  
\v 29 Zi swadday tuɣa řeṣqent am wacniwen uca ammu i tent tuɣa d icten ař dd-awḍent sennej deg ict n texrazt. Ammu i igga s tnayen \add n tfeřwin\add* i tnayen n tɣemmura. \x ◘ \xo 36:29 \xt Uf. 26:24\x*  
\v 30 \add Ammu\add* i din tuɣa tmenya n tfeřwin s tyarsawin nsent n nnuqart, \add aqa atent\add* d seṭṭac n tyarsawin, tnayen n tyarsawin sadu kuř tafřewt. \x ◘ \xo 36:30 \xt Uf. 26:25\x*  
\v 31 Igga ɛawed \bd tiḥenya \+bdit n uɛarreḍ\+bdit*\bd* zeg ukeccuḍ n ukasiya, xemsa n tfeřwin ɣar ijj n uɣezdis n Tzeddiɣt, \x ◘ \xo 36:31 \xt Uf. 26:26\x*  
\v 32 u xemsa n tḥenya n uɛarreḍ i tfeřwin ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni n Tzeddiɣt d xemsa n tḥenya n uɛarreḍ i tfeřwin n Tzeddiɣt ɣar tnayen n tɣemmura n ḍeffar ɣar řɣarb. \x ◘ \xo 36:32 \xt Uf. 26:27\x*  
\v 33 Taḥnact n uɛarreḍ di řwesṭ igga i-tt ad teẓwa zi řwesṭ n tfeřwin zeg ixef ař wenneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 36:33 \xt Uf. 26:28\x*  
\v 34 Iɣeǧef tifeřwin s wureɣ uca igga tixrazin nsent n wureɣ, maḥend ad daysent ssidfen tiḥenya n uɛarreḍ uca \add uřa d\add* tiḥenya n uɛarreḍ icellel i-tent s wureɣ. \x ◘ \xo 36:34 \xt Uf. 26:29\x*   
\m
\v 35 Igga ijj n \bd uřeḥḥaf\bd* s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden, igga i-t d ijj n warcam n ufennan ak-d ikiruben \add xas\add*. \x ◘ \xo 36:35 \xt Uf. 26:31\x*  
\v 36 Igga as arebɛa n ipilaren n ukeccuḍ n ukasiya uca iɣeǧef i-ten s wureɣ. \bd Tisennarin\bd* nsen tuɣa atent n wureɣ. Issefsi \add i ipilaren\add* arebɛa n tyarsawin nsent n nnuqart. \x ◘ \xo 36:36 \xt Uf. 26:32\x*   
\m
\v 37 Igga ijj n \bd arwaq\bd* i wadaf n Uqiḍun s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden, \add igga i-t\add* d ijj n umudi n uxeyyaḍ, \x ◘ \xo 36:37 \xt Uf. 26:36\x*  
\v 38 s xemsa n ipilaren nnes d tsennarin nnes. Iɣeǧef tizeǧifin nsen d iqeḍban nsen i useřqi s wureɣ. Tiyarsawin nsen tuɣa atent n nnḥas. \x ◘ \xo 36:38 \xt Uf. 26:37\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 37
\m
\v 1 Igga Baṣaliyil \bd Ttabut\bd* n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya. Tuzzeggart nnes tuɣa-tt tnayen n iɣaǧen d wezyen u tiru nnes ijj n uɣiř d wezyen uca řuɛřa nnes ijj n uɣiř d wezyen. \x ◘ \xo 37:1 \xt Uf. 25:10\x*  
\v 2 Iɣeǧef i-t zi daxeř d barra s wureɣ iṣfan uca igga as ijj n zzwaq n wureɣ i d as dd-innḍen.  
\v 3 Issefsi as arebɛa n texrazin i arebɛa n tɣemmura nnes: tnayen n texrazin ɣar yijj n uɣezdis d tnayen n texrazin ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni.  
\v 4 Igga iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* zeg ukeccuḍ n ukasiya uca iɣeǧef i-ten s wureɣ.  
\v 5 Igga iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* di texrazin ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen n Ttabut, maḥend ad \add zzaysen\add* arbun Ttabut.  
\v 6 Igga \bd taqebbart n weṣřaḥ\bd* n wureɣ iṣfan s tuzzeggart nnes n tnayen n iɣaǧen d wezyen u tiru nnes n ijj n uɣiř d wezyen.  
\v 7 Igga \bd tnayen n ikiruben\bd* n wureɣ. Iɛdeř i-ten \add am\add* řxedmet n wemziř \add i dd-itteffɣen\add* zi tnayen n ixfawen n tqebbart n weṣřaḥ.  
\v 8 Ijj n ukirub \add iffeɣ\add* zeg ijj n ixef ɣar uɣezdis-a u akirub nneɣni zeg ixef nneɣni ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni. Igga ikiruben zi tnayen n ixfawen n tqebbart n weṣřaḥ. \x ◘ \xo 37:8 \xt Uf. 25:19\x*  
\v 9 Ikiruben sswiẓẓḍen afriwen nsen sennej uca s wafriwen nsen dřin taqebbart n weṣřaḥ. Iɣembab nsen tuɣa ijjen qibač i wenneɣni uca \add di řweqt d icten tuɣa\add* iɣembab n ikiruben ɣar tqebbart n weṣřaḥ. \x ◘ \xo 37:9 \xt Uf. 25:20\x*   
\m
\v 10 Igga \bd tazewḍa\bd* n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya. Tuɣa tuzzeggart nnes tnayen n iɣaǧen u tiru nnes ijj n uɣiř d řuɛřa nnes ijj n uɣiř d wezyen. \x ◘ \xo 37:10 \xt Uf. 25:23\x*  
\v 11 Iɣeǧef i-tt s wureɣ iṣfan uca igga as ijj n zzwaq n wureɣ i d as dd-innḍen. \x ◘ \xo 37:11 \xt Uf. 25:24\x*  
\v 12 Igga \add ɛawed\add* ict n tma i d as dd-innḍen n ijj n cbar n ufus uca igga ijj n zzwaq n wureɣ ɣar tmewwa nnes i d as dd-innḍen. \x ◘ \xo 37:12 \xt Uf. 25:25\x*  
\v 13 Issefsi as arebɛa n texrazin n wureɣ uca igga tixrazin ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura nni iǧan ɣar arebɛa n iḍaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 37:13 \xt Uf. 25:26\x*  
\v 14 Tuɣa tixrazin zzat n tma, maḥend ad \add daysent\add* ssidfen iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add*, ḥima ad \add zzaysen\add* arbun tazewḍa. \x ◘ \xo 37:14 \xt Uf. 25:27\x*  
\v 15 Igga iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* zeg ukeccuḍ n ukasiya uca iɣeǧef i-ten s wureɣ, maḥend ad \add zzaysen\add* arbun tazewḍa.  
\v 16 Igga řeqcuɛ i ɣa yiřin x tzewḍa s wureɣ iṣfan: ṭṭbaṣi nnes d tɣenjayin nnes d řkisan nnes d iɣarrafen, maḥend ad zzaysen kebben. \x ◘ \xo 37:16 \xt Uf. 25:29\x*   
\m
\v 17 Igga \bd řqendiř\bd* n wureɣ iṣfan. Iɛdeř řqendiř s wefḍis n wemziř: afud x uḍar nnes d iɣaǧen nnes d řkisan nnes d tɛebbuzin nnes i dd-ittasen ak-d nnuwarat nnes, aqa-ten \add marra\add* tuɣa zzayes \add dd-itteffɣen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 37:17 \xt Uf. 25:31\x*  
\v 18 Zeg iɣezdisen nnes ffɣen-dd setta n iɣaǧen, třata n iɣaǧen n řqendiř zeg ijj n uɣezdis d třata n iɣaǧen n řqendiř zeg uɣezdis nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 37:18 \xt Uf. 25:32\x*  
\v 19 Ɣar ijj n uɣiř \add tuɣa\add* din třata n řkisan am \add nnewwac n\add* ǧewz s tɛebbuzt d nnewwac uca x uɣiř nneɣni \add ɛawed\add* třata n řkisan am \add nnewwac n\add* ǧewz s \add ict n\add* tɛebbuzt i dd-ittasen ak-d \add ijj n\add* nnewwac. Ammu \add i yeǧan marra\add* setta n iɣaǧen nni dd-itteffɣen zi řqendiř. \x ◘ \xo 37:19 \xt Uf. 25:33\x*  
\v 20 Ɣar řqendiř \add simant nnes\add* tuɣa din arebɛa n řkisan am \add nnuwarat n\add* ǧewz ak-d tɛebbuzin nsen i dd-ittasen ak-d nnuwarat nsen. \x ◘ \xo 37:20 \xt Uf. 25:34\x*  
\v 21 Sadu tyuya n iɣaǧen i zzayes \add dd-iffɣen d amezwaru\add* aqa din ict n tɛebbuzt uca \add amenni\add* i din ict n tɛebbuzt sadu tyuya n iɣaǧen i zzayes \add dd-iffɣen awarni as\add* uca ɛawed din ict n tɛebbuzt sadu tyuya n iɣaǧen i zzayes \add dd-iffɣen d aneggaru\add*. \add Man aya iǧa amenni\add* i setta n iɣaǧen i zzayes dd-iffɣen.  
\v 22 Tuɣa tiɛebbuzin nsen d iɣaǧen nsen ffɣen-dd zzayes. Marra aya \add tuɣa\add* d ict n řxedmet n wemziř s wureɣ iṣfan. \x ◘ \xo 37:22 \xt Uf. 25:36\x*  
\v 23 Igga setta n řefnarat nnes ak-d tjeqqaḍin \add n teftič\add* nnes d tmejmarin nnes, \add marra\add* s wureɣ iṣfan. \f ◼ \fr 37:23 \ft \+fk tijeqqaḍin\ft  - niɣ ‘tineqqaḍin’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 37:23 \xt Uf. 25:37,38\x*  
\v 24 Igga \add řqendiř\add* ak-d marra řeqcuɛ nnes zeg ict n talint n wureɣ iṣfan. \x ◘ \xo 37:24 \xt Uf. 25:39\x*   
\m
\v 25 Igga \bd aɛalṭar n řebxur\bd* zeg ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ukasiya s tuzzeggart nnes n ijj uɣiř u tiru nnes n ijj n uɣiř. Tuɣa-t s arebɛa n tɣemmura. Řuɛřa nnes tuɣa-t tnayen n iɣaǧen. Zzayes tuɣa accawen nnes \add d ijj akides\add*. \f ◼ \fr 37:25 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iqiccawen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 37:25 \xt Uf. 30:1, 2\x*  
\v 26 Iɣeǧef i-t s wureɣ iṣfan, udem nnes n sennej d iɣezdisen nnes i d as dd-innḍen u ɛawed accawen nnes. Igga as ijj n zzwaq n wureɣ i d as dd-innḍen. \x ◘ \xo 37:26 \xt Uf. 30:3\x*  
\v 27 Igga as tnayen n texrazin n wureɣ sadu zzwaq nnes i tnayen n tɣemmura nnes, ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen nnes, ḥima ad daysent ssidfen iɛumad, maḥend ad zzaysen arbun aɛalṭar n řebxur. \x ◘ \xo 37:27 \xt Uf. 30:4\x*  
\v 28 Igga iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* zeg ukeccuḍ n ukasiya uca iɣeǧef i-ten s wureɣ. \x ◘ \xo 37:28 \xt Uf. 30:5\x*   
\m
\v 29 Igga ɛawed \bd zzect tamqeddest i wedhan\bd* d \bd řebxur iṣfan ittfuḥen\bd*, \add ɛlaḥsab\add* ṣṣenɛet n uɛeṭṭař. \x ◘ \xo 37:29 \xt Uf. 30:22,34\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 38
\m
\v 1 Igga \bd aɛalṭar n wecmaḍ\bd* s ukeccuḍ n ukasiya. Tuzzeggart nnes tuɣa-tt xemsa n iɣaǧen u tiru nnes xemsa n iɣaǧen, tuɣa-t s arebɛa n tɣemmura, u řuɛřa nnes tuɣa-t třata n iɣaǧen. \x ◘ \xo 38:1 \xt Uf. 27:1\x*  
\v 2 Ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura igga accawen nnes. Accawen nnes tuɣa aten d ijjen akides. Iɣeǧef i-t s nnḥas. \f ◼ \fr 38:2 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iqiccawen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 38:2 \xt Uf. 27:2\x*  
\v 3 Igga marra řeqcuɛ i uɛalṭar: tiydurin d iɣenjayen d ṭṭawyat i urucci d furcayat d tmejmarin, marra řeqcuɛ-a igga i-ten s nnḥas. \x ◘ \xo 38:3 \xt Uf. 27:3\x*  
\v 4 Igga ict n tracca i uɛalṭar, ijj n umudi n nnḥas sadu tma nnes, swadday ɣar wezyen \add n uɛalṭar\add*. \x ◘ \xo 38:4 \xt Uf. 27:4, 5\x*  
\v 5 Issefsi arebɛa n texrazin i arebɛa n ixfawen n tracca n nnḥas maḥend ad daysent ssidfen iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add*.  
\v 6 Igga iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* zeg ukeccuḍ n ukasiya uca iɣeǧef i-ten s nnḥas.  
\v 7 Igga iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* di texrazin ɣar iɣezdisen n uɛalṭar, maḥend ad zzaysen t arbun. Igga i-t s tfeřwin \add ak-d\add* řxawi \add di daxeř nsent\add*. \x ◘ \xo 38:7 \xt Uf. 27:8\x*   
\m
\v 8 Igga \bd tabanyut n nnḥas\bd* s uḍar nnes n nnḥas zi tisitin n terbiɛin n temɣarin nni xedment ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar. \x ◘ \xo 38:8 \xt Uf. 30:18\x*   
\m
\v 9 Igga \bd řemraḥ.\bd* Ɣar jjihet n ljanub, ɣar yefus, tuɣa tuzzeggart n \bd řizarat n řemraḥ\bd* mya n iɣaǧen n řeqṭen azdad imuden. \x ◘ \xo 38:9 \xt Uf. 27:9\x*  
\v 10 Ɛicrin n \bd ipilaren\bd* nnes d ɛicrin n \bd tyarsawin\bd* nsen \add tuɣa aten\add* n nnḥas. \bd Tisennarin\bd* n ipilaren d \bd iqeḍban nsen i useřqi\bd* \add tuɣa aten\add* n nnuqart.  
\v 11 Ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal \add tuɣa din řizarat s ict n tuzzeggart n\add* mya n iɣaǧen ak-d ɛicrin n ipilaren nsent u ak-d ɛicrin n tyarsawin nsen n nnḥas. Tisennarin n ipilaren d iqeḍban nsen i useřqi \add tuɣa aten\add* n nnuqart.  
\v 12 Ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb \add tuɣa din\add* řizarat n xemsin n iɣaǧen ak-d ɛecra n ipilaren nsent d ɛecra n tyarsawin nsen. Tisennarin n ipilaren d iqeḍban nsen i useřqi \add tuɣa aten\add* n nnuqart.  
\v 13 Ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq, ɣar jjihet n wenqar n tfuct, \add tuɣa din řizarat n\add* xemsin n iɣaǧen.  
\v 14 Tuɣa řizarat ɣar ijj n uɣezdis n zzat xemmesṭac n iɣaǧen \add di tuzzeggart\add* ak-d třata n ipilaren nsent d třata n tyarsawin nsen.  
\v 15 Ɣar uɣezdis n zzat nneɣni n wadaf n řemraḥ, ɣar uɣezdis-a d uɣezdis nni, \add tuɣa\add* řizarat daysent xemmesṭac n iɣaǧen di tuzzeggart, ak-d třata n ipilaren nsent d třata n tyarsawin nsen.  
\v 16 Marra řizarat nni d as dd-innḍen i řemraḥ tuɣa atent n řeqṭen azdad imuden.  
\v 17 Tiyarsawin n ipilaren \add tuɣa atent\add* n nnḥas d tsennarin n ipilaren d iqeḍban nsen i useřqi \add tuɣa aten\add* s nnuqart uca takursit x tzeǧifin nsen \add tuɣa-tt\add* zi nnuqart d marra ipilaren n řemraḥ \add tuɣa ɣarsen\add* iqeḍban n nnuqart i useřqi.  
\v 18 Arwaq ɣar wadaf n řemraḥ ggin t d ijj n umudi n uxeyyaḍ s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden. Tuzzeggart \add nnes\add* tuɣa ɛicrin n iɣaǧen u řuɛřa x \add marra\add* tiru \add n řemraḥ\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen, am řizarat n řemraḥ.  
\v 19 Arebɛa n ipilaren d arebɛa n tyarsawin nsen tuɣa aten s nnḥas d tsennarin nsen s nnuqart uca takursit x tzeǧifin nsen uřa d iqeḍban nsen i useřqi \add tuɣa aten\add* s nnuqart.  
\v 20 Marra řewtad n Tzeddiɣt d řemraḥ i d as dd-innḍen \add tuɣa aten\add* s nnḥas.   
\m
\v 21 \bd Man aya d min ssuffɣen nitni i Tzeddiɣt\bd*, Tazeddiɣt n Cchadet, uca zemmen t s řumur n Musa s tsexxart n Ilawiyyen, s ufus n Itamar, mmis n Harun, akehhan.  
\v 22 Baṣaliyil mmis n Uri, mmis n Ḥur, zi teqbič n Yahuda, igga marra min d as yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 23 \add Tuɣa\add* akides Ahuliyab, mmis n Axisamak, zi teqbič n Dan. \add Tuɣa-t\add* d aneqqac d bu-ṣṣenɛet, axeyyaḍ n \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d řeqṭen azdad.   
\m
\v 24 \bd Marra ureɣ i ssxedmen nitni i řxedmet\bd* ɣar marra řxedmet \add i iggin\add* di Zzawect Iqeddsen, \add ixs ad yini\add* ureɣ n tewhibin n wenhezzi, tuɣa: tesɛa u-ɛicrin talint u sebɛa-mya u-třatin ciqlu ɛlaḥsab ciqlu iqeddsen.   
\m
\v 25 \bd Nnuqart n yinni ittwaḥesben\bd* n tmesmunt tuɣa-tt mya talint d ařef u-sebɛa-mya u-xemsa u-sebɛin ciqlu, ɛlaḥsab ciqlu iqeddsen.  
\v 26 Ijj n wezyen i yijj n bnadem, aqa-t d azyen ciqlu ɛlaḥsab min dd-ittawi ciqlu iqeddsen, zi marra wi iɛdun ɣar yinni ittwaḥesben zi ɛicrin n iseggʷusa sennej, \add d man aya\add* i setta-mya u-teřt-ařaf u-xemsa-mya u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add*.  
\v 27 Mya talint n nnuqart nni tuɣa atent ḥima ad \add zzaysent\add* ssfesyen tyarsawin n Zzawect Iqeddsen d tyarsawin n uřeḥḥaf: mya n tyarsawin zi mya talint, \add ixs ad yini\add* ict n talint i yict n tyarsa.  
\v 28 Zeg wařef u-sebɛa-mya u-xemsa u-sebɛin \add ciqlu\add* igga tisennarin i ipilaren. Iɣeǧef tizeǧifin nsen uca icedd \add ɣarsen\add* iqeḍban i useřqi.   
\m
\v 29 \bd Nnḥas n tewhibin n wenhezzi\bd* \add tuɣa-t\add* sebɛin talint d ařfayen u-arebɛa-mya ciqlu.  
\v 30 S man aya igga tyarsawin i wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar d uɛalṭar n nnḥas d tracca nnes n nnḥas d marra řeqcuɛ n uɛalṭar  
\v 31 d tyarsawin \add n ipilaren\add* n řemraḥ i d as dd-innḍen d tyarsawin n wadaf n řemraḥ d marra řewtad n Tzeddiɣt d marra řewtad n \add ipilaren\add* i d as dd-innḍen i řemraḥ.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 39
\s1 Musa iqeǧeb marra řxedmet uca ibarek řgens  
\m
\v 1 Ggin \add ɛawed\add* arruḍ i tsexxart s \add ufiři\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen, ḥima ad \add zzayes\add* sexxaren \add ikehhanen\add* di Zzawect Iqeddsen. \add Ɛawed\add* ggin \bd arruḍ iqeddsen i Harun\bd*, am mammec d as yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 39:1 \xt Uf. 31:10; 35:19\x*   
\m
\v 2 Igga \bd apalṭu \+bdit n ukehhan\+bdit*\bd* s \add ifiřan n\add* wureɣ u s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden. \x ◘ \xo 39:2 \xt Uf. 28:6\x*  
\v 3 Nitni bezzɛen tiřwiḥin n wureɣ uca qessen zzaysent ifiřan, ḥima ad ten xeyyḍen jar \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u jar řeqṭen azdad, \add d man aya tuɣa\add* d ict n řxedmet \add am\add* tt ittegg ufennan. \x ◘ \xo 39:3 \xt Uf. 28:6\x*  
\v 4 Ggin as tiɣarḍin imseřsaqen uca ssmunen \add apalṭu\add* ɣar tnayen n ixfawen nnes.  
\v 5 Taḥezzamt izewwqen i tuɣa ɣar upalṭu nnes, tuɣa teřseq dayes, tedweř d ict akides. Tᵉttwagg tḥezzamt s webrid d ijjen \add ak-d upalṭu\add* s \add ifiřan n\add* wureɣ u s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 39:5 \xt Uf. 28:8\x*  
\v 6 Nitni ggin ɛawed iẓra n uniks, inni ittwaṭṭfen di tcuyar n wureɣ, neqcen ten am yijj n wenqac n txadent n ucemmiɛ s ismawen n ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 39:6 \xt Uf. 28:9, 10, 11\x*  
\v 7 Igga i-ten x tɣarḍin n upalṭu, \add am\add* iẓra n řidaret i ayt n Israil, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 39:7 \xt Uf. 28:12\x*   
\m
\v 8 Igga \bd tajmect\bd*, ict n řxedmet \add am\add* tt ittegg ufennan, \add am mammec igga\add* apalṭu, s \add ifiřan n\add* wureɣ u s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad imuden.  
\v 9 \add Tuɣa-tt\add* s arebɛa n tɣemmura. Ḍefsen tajmect. \add Tuɣa\add* tuzzeggart nnes d ijj n wezyen n uɣiř, uca uřa d tiru nnes d ijj n wezyen n uɣiř. Tuɣa iḍfes x tnayen. \x ◘ \xo 39:9 \xt Uf. 28:16\x*  
\v 10 Settfen dayes arebɛa n řeṣfuf n yeẓra: ijj n ṣṣef \add s\add* yijj n řeɛqiq d azeggwaɣ d ict n tyaqut d yict n smaraxt. D wa d ṣṣef amezwar. \x ◘ \xo 39:10 \xt Uf. 28:17\x*  
\v 11 Ṣṣef wiss tnayen s yijj n karbunkel d yijj n ṣaffir aziza d yijj n diamanti. \x ◘ \xo 39:11 \xt Uf. 28:18\x*  
\v 12 Ṣṣef wiss třata s yijj \add n weẓru\add* n yasintu d yijj n axat d yijj umatist.  
\v 13 Ṣṣef wiss arebɛa s yict n texrisulit d yijj n uniks d yijj n yaspis. Tuɣa ttwaṭṭfen di tcuyar nsen n wureɣ.  
\v 14 Iẓra tuɣa xasen ismawen n ayt n Israil, tenɛac \add n yeẓra\add* ɛlaḥsab ismawen nsen, s ineqqacen n ijj n ucemmiɛ, kuř \add aneqqac\add* ak-d yisem nnes i d as dd-yusin. Aqa aten i tenɛac n tqebbař.  
\v 15 Ɣar ixfawen n tejmect ggin tiseddyin s wureɣ iṣfan, \add tinni\add* imuden am yijj n ufiřu.  
\v 16 Ggin tnayen n tcuyar n wureɣ d tnayen n texrazin n wureɣ uca cedden tnayen n texrazin ɣar tnayen n ixfawen n tejmect.  
\v 17 Cedden tnayen n ssnaseř imuden n wureɣ ɣar tnayen n texrazin ɣar ixfawen n tejmect.  
\v 18 Tnayen n ixfawen nneɣni n tnayen n ssnaseř imuden, cedden ten ɣar tnayen n tcuyar uca wcin ten x ṭɣarḍin n upalṭu, deg wudem n zzat.  
\v 19 Ggin \add ɛawed\add* tnayen n texrazin n wureɣ, cedden tent ɣar tnayen n ixfawen nneɣni n tejmect, di tma nnes nni qibač i upalṭu, ɣar daxeř.  
\v 20 Ggin \add ɛawed\add* tnayen n texrazin n wureɣ, cedden tent x tnayen n tɣarḍin n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add*, swadday, ɣar zzat, qibač i useřqi nnes ɣar sennej i tḥezzamt izewwqen n upalṭu.  
\v 21 Uca cedden tajmect s texrazin nnes ɣar texrazin n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* ak-d ijj n ufiřu adeḥmi ařami idweř sennej i tḥezzamt izewwqen n upalṭu, uca \add xenni\add* war tbeṭṭi tejmect x upalṭu, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa.   
\m
\v 22 Igga ɛawed \bd aseřham\bd* n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* \add am mammec t\add* ittegg uxeyyaḍ, \add tuɣa-t d\add* adeḥmi marra.  
\v 23 Arzam n useřham \add tuɣa-t\add* di řwesṭ nnes \add am mammec ggin\add* arzam n yiri n warruḍ n wuzzař n uɛeskari. Deg wenneḍ n warzam tuɣa din ict n tma, \add ḥima\add* war ittcarrig.  
\v 24 Ɣar tmuwwa \add n wadday\add* n useřham ggin tiremmanin s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen \add zeg ifiřan\add* imuden.  
\v 25 Ggin ɛawed nnwaqes n wureɣ iṣfan uca ssarsen nnwaqes nni jar tremmanin ɣar tmuwwa \add n wadday\add* n useřham, deg wenneḍ jar tremmanin.  
\v 26 Ijj n nnaqus d ict n tremmant, \add xenni ɛawed\add* ijj n nnaqus d ict n tremmant ɣar tmuwwa \add n wadday\add* n useřham deg wenneḍ, maḥend ad dayes ggen tasexxart nsen, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa.   
\m
\v 27 Ggin \bd tcamir\bd* i Harun d warraw nnes s řeqṭen azdad, \add am mammec t\add* ittegg uxeyyaḍ, \x ◘ \xo 39:27 \xt Uf. 28:39\x*  
\v 28 \bd areẓẓet\bd* n řeqṭen azdad d \bd tcuccay izewwqen\bd* n řeqṭen azdad d \bd ssraweř n řeqṭen\bd* s řeqṭen azdad imuden  
\v 29 u tuɣa \bd taḥezzamt\bd* n řeqṭen azdad imuden u n \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d urjuwani d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen, aqa-tt d ijj n umudi n uxeyyaḍ, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa.   
\m
\v 30 Ggin \bd \+bdit tařwiḥt s\+bdit* nnuwar n ttaj iqeddsen \+bdit n weɛzař\+bdit*\bd* s wureɣ iṣfan uca neqcen dayes tira-ya: “AMQEDDAS i SIDI!”, am mammec neqcen taxadent n ucemmiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 39:30 \xt Uf. 28:36; 29:6\x*  
\v 31 Uca cedden as ijj n ufiřu imuden adeḥmi, ḥima ad tt ayřen sennej i areẓẓet, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 39:31 \xt Uf. 28:37\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 32 Ammu i tkemmeř marra řxedmet n Tzeddiɣt, Aqiḍun n Umsagar. Ayt n Israil aqa ggin tt am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa, ammu i tt ggin.   
\m
\v 33 Ksin Tazeddiɣt ɣar Musa, Aqiḍun d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d tsennarin nnes d tfeřwin nnes d tḥenya nnes n uɛarreḍ d ipilaren nnes d tyarsawin nnes \x ◘ \xo 39:33 \xt Uf. 35:11\x*  
\v 34 d tseqqaft n iřmawen izeggʷaɣen n icarriyyen d tseqqaft n iřmawen n ddenfiřat d uřeḥḥaf i dduri,  
\v 35 Ttabut n Cchadet d iɛumad nnes \add i tarebbut\add* d tqebbart n weṣřaḥ  
\v 36 d tazewḍa ak-d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d weɣrum n wescan \x ◘ \xo 39:36 \xt Uf. 31:8\x*  
\v 37 d řqendiř \add n wureɣ\add* iṣfan d řefnarat nnes - řefnarat nni tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad ttwasswejdent, d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d zzect i tfawt -  
\v 38 d uɛalṭar n wureɣ d zzect i wedhan d řebxur ittfuḥen d arwaq i wadaf n Uqiḍun  
\v 39 d uɛalṭar n nnḥas s tracca n nnḥas d iɛumad nnes \add i tarebbut\add* d marra řeqcuɛ nnes d tbanyut ak-d uḍar nnes  
\v 40 d řizarat n řemraḥ ak-d ipilaren nsent d tyarsawin nsen, uřa d arwaq n wadaf n řemraḥ d ifiřan nnes d řewtad nnes d marra řeqcuɛ i tsexxart n Tzeddiɣt, i Uqiḍun n Umsagar  
\v 41 uřa d arruḍ i tsexxart, ḥima ad \add zzayes\add* sexxaren \add ikehhanen\add* di Zzawect Iqeddsen, arruḍ iqeddsen i ukehhan Harun d arruḍ i warraw nnes, ḥima \add ad sexxaren d\add* ikehhanen. \x ◘ \xo 39:41 \xt Uf. 31:10\x*  
\v 42 Ggin ayt n Israil marra řxedmet am mammec marra i yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 43 Ixzar Musa ɣar marra řxedmet uca iẓra belli tᵉttwagg am mammec yumur SIDI, \add wah,\add* ammu i-tt ggin. Uca ibark i-ten Musa.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 40
\s1 Musa issgeɛɛed Aqiḍun n Umsagar  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Deg wass amezwaru n uyur amezwaru ad tessgeɛɛded Tazeddiɣt, Aqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 3 Ad dayes tegged Ttabut n Cchadet uca ad tedřed Ttabut s uřeḥḥaf.  
\v 4 Ad tessidfed tazewḍa uca ad tt tsettfed asettef nnes. Ad tessidfed řqendiř uca ad tessiɣed řefnarat nnes. \x ◘ \xo 40:4 \xt Uf. 26:35; 27:20\x*  
\v 5 Ad tessarsed aɛalṭar n wureɣ i řebxur zzat i Ttabut n Cchadet uca ad tegged arwaq n wadaf zzat n Tzeddiɣt. \x ◘ \xo 40:5 \xt Uf. 26:36\x*  
\v 6 Ad tessarsed aɛalṭar n wecmaḍ zzat i wadaf n Tzeddiɣt, Aqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 7 Ad tessarsed tabanyut jar Uqiḍun n Umsagar d uɛalṭar uca ad dayes tegged aman.  
\v 8 Ad tessbedded řemraḥ ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnes uca ad tayřed arwaq n wadaf n řemraḥ. \x ◘ \xo 40:8 \xt Uf. 27:16\x*  
\v 9 Ad teksid zzect i wedhan uca ad tdehned Tazeddiɣt d marra min dayes \add iǧan\add*. Ad tt tessqeddsed ak-d marra řeqcuɛ nnes. Ad tiři nettat d tamqeddast.  
\v 10 Ad tdehned aɛalṭar n wecmaḍ s marra řeqcuɛ nnes. Ad tessqeddsed aɛalṭar. Aɛalṭar \add ad yiři\add* d amqeddas qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 40:10 \xt Uf. 29:37\x*  
\v 11 Ad tdehned tabanyut d uḍar nnes uca ad tt tessqeddsed.  
\v 12 Ad dd-tessqarrbed Harun d warraw nnes ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar uca ad ten tessirded s waman.  
\v 13 Ad tessyarḍed i Harun arruḍ iqeddsen uca ad t tdehned uca ad t tessqeddsed, maḥend ad ayi yiři d akehhan i Necc.  
\v 14 Xenni ad dd-tessqarrbed iḥenjiren nnes uca ad asen tyarḍed tcamirat.  
\v 15 Ad ten tdehned am mammec tdehned babatsen, maḥend ad ayi sexxaren am yikehhanen. Ad yiři wedhan nsen i nitni d ict n tukehhant i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Igga Musa marra am mammec yumur SIDI, \add wah,\add* ammu i t igga.   
\b  
\m
\v 17 \bd Imsar deg uyur amezwaru n useggʷas wiss tnayen, deg wass amezwaru n uyur, aqa ssgeɛɛden Tazeddiɣt.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 40:17 \xt Řxř. 7:1\x*  
\v 18 Musa issgeɛɛed Tazeddiɣt, issars tiyarsawin nnes, igga daysent tifeřwin, igga xasent tiḥenya n uɛarreḍ \add tinni xasent iẓwan\add*, uca issbedd ipilaren nnes.  
\v 19 Ibezzeɛ Aqiḍun x Tzeddiɣt uca issars xas taseqqaft n Uqiḍun am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 20 Iksi Cchadet uca issars i-tt daxeř di Ttabut uca icedd iɛumad \add i tarebbut\add* ɣar Ttabut uca issars taqebbart n weṣřaḥ x Ttabut.  
\v 21 Issidef Ttabut di Tzeddiɣt uca yuyeř ařeḥḥaf am dduri uca issduriy Ttabut n Cchadet am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 40:21 \xt Uf. 35:12\x*  
\v 22 Issars tazewḍa deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar, ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal n Tzeddiɣt, ɣar barra n uřeḥḥaf.  
\v 23 Isettef xas aɣrum zzat i wudem n SIDI, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 40:23 \xt Uf. 25:30\x*  
\v 24 Issars řqendiř deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar, nican deg urendad n tzewḍa, ɣar jjihet n ljanub n Tzeddiɣt.  
\v 25 Issars xas tiftiřin zzat i wudem n SIDI, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 26 Iwca amcan i uɛalṭar n wureɣ deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar zzat i uřeḥḥaf.  
\v 27 Issbexxar xas řebxur ittfuḥen am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 28 Yuyeř arwaq ɣar wadaf n Tzeddiɣt.  
\v 29 Iwca amcan i uɛalṭar n wecmaḍ ɣar wadaf n Tzeddiɣt, Aqiḍun n Umsagar. Issbexxar xas taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 30 Issars tabanyut jar Uqiḍun n Umsagar d uɛalṭar. Igga dayes aman i usird.  
\v 31 Musa d Harun d warraw nnes ssirden zzayes ifassen d iḍaren nsen.  
\v 32 Řami tuɣa ttadfen ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar u řami dd-ttqarraben ɣar uɛalṭar, ssirden ixef nsen am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 33 Ɣar marra iɣezdisen n Tzeddiɣt d uɛalṭar ittwagg as-dd řemraḥ uca yuyeř netta arwaq n wadaf n řemraḥ. \add Ammu\add* i ikemmeř Musa řxedmet.   
\m
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* idřa useynu Aqiḍun n Umsagar uca aɛuǧi n SIDI iccur Tazeddiɣt. \x ◘ \xo 40:34 \xt Řxř. 9:15; 1 Ij. 8:10\x*  
\v 35 War izemmar Musa ad yadef ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar, minzi aseynu yarsa xas u aɛuǧi n SIDI iccur Tazeddiɣt.  
\v 36 Řami dd-igeɛɛed useynu zi sennej n Tzeddiɣt, fesyen ayt n Israil iqiḍan nsen uca \add ammu\add* muṭṭyen \add zeg wemcan ɣar wemcan\add*.  
\v 37 Mařa war dd-igeɛɛed useynu, war fesyen iqiḍan nsen ař ass i di tuɣa ittgeɛɛed.  
\v 38 Minzi aseynu n SIDI tuɣa yarsa x Tzeddiɣt s uziř uca di ǧiřet tuɣa timessi zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra taddart n Israil deg imuṭṭuyen nsen \add zeg wemcan ɣar wemcan\add*. \x ◘ \xo 40:38 \xt Uf. 13:21; Řxř. 14:14; Aɛwd. 1:33; Naḥ. 9:19; Izhd. 78:14; 105:39; 1 Kur. 10:1\x*   